NK050(wi)001:1: // ra t+na d+ai bam nu ni sa r+tha ga r+b+ha
NK050(wi)001:2: ma t+ma sam k+shi sta na ma bi ha ra
NK050(wi)001:4: nges don snying po'i gnad mdor bsdus pa rin po che'i sgron me zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK050(wi)001:5: na mo gu ru many+dzu sh+r+ai ye /
NK050(wi)001:6: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba //
NK050(wi)001:7: rang byung zag med bde ba che //
NK050(wi)001:8: bde gshegs snying po la btud nas //
NK050(wi)001:9: nges don snying po mdo tsam bshad //
NK050(wi)001:10: 'dir nges don snying po'i gnad mdor bsdu na //
NK050(wi)001:11: gdod ma'i 'od gsal bde gshegs snying po ni //
NK050(wi)001:12: 'khor 'das kun gyi spyi gzhir gnas te /
NK050(wi)001:13: rang gi ngo bo la grol 'khrul gang yang med mod //
NK050(wi)001:14: de nyid ngang ngam rtsal las rang ngo rang gis
NK050(wi)001:15: rig dang ma rig pa'i dbang gis 'khor 'das gnyis
NK050(wi)001:18: nga med pa yi sngon rol du //
NK050(wi)001:19: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med de //
NK050(wi)001:20: lam dang 'bras bu ga la yod //
NK050(wi)001:21: nga las ma byung gcig kyang med //
NK050(wi)001:22: nga ni stong pa chen po'o //
NK050(wi)001:24: pad+ma dbang chen bde gshegs spyi dril las //
NK050(wi)001:25: kun nas nyon mongs 'khor ba'i chos //
NK050(wi)001:26: rnam par byang ba mya ngan 'das //
NK050(wi)001:27: rtsa ba sems kyi chos nyid 'dus //
NK050(wi)001:28: sems ni rang bzhin 'od gsal ba //
NK050(wi)001:29: ma mdzad ma bcos lhun gyis grub //
NK050(wi)001:31: snying po rab tu bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK050(wi)001:32: thog ma med pa'i dus kyi dbyings //
NK050(wi)001:33: chos rnams kun gyi gnas yin te //
NK050(wi)001:35: mya ngan 'das pa thob pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:39: gnyis 'di glo bur byung ba ste //
NK050(wi)001:41: dbu ma chos dbyings bstod pa las //
NK050(wi)001:42: gang zhig 'khor ba'i rgyur gyur pa //
NK050(wi)001:43: de nyid sbyang bar byas pa las //
NK050(wi)001:44: dag pa de nyid mya ngan 'das //
NK050(wi)001:45: chos kyi sku nyid de yin no //
NK050(wi)001:48: sems nyid gcig pu kun gyi sa bon te //
NK050(wi)001:49: gang las srid dang mya ngan 'das 'phro ba //
NK050(wi)001:55: snang cha nas gzugs sku mtshan dpe'i 'byung khung dang /
NK050(wi)001:56: stong cha nas chos sku spros mtshan gyi mtha' kun bral bar ye nas gnas pa nyid /
NK050(wi)001:57: yon tan lhun gyis grub pas nor bu dang /
NK050(wi)001:58: gzhan du mi 'gyur bas nam mkha' dang /
NK050(wi)001:59: ye nas rlan zhing khyab pas chu'i dpe sogs rgyud bla mar gsungs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:60: rdzogs chen du gzhi'i mtshon dpe /
NK050(wi)001:61: stong la khyab pas nam mkha' /
NK050(wi)001:62: dri ma med pas man shel /
NK050(wi)001:65: gsal la mi 'gags pas nyi ma lta bu sogs rgyud nas gsungs pa don gyi gnad gcig pas /
NK050(wi)001:66: 'di'i rang rtsal las phyir ma g.yos pa'i tshe 'khrul
NK050(wi)001:67: pa'ang min la grol ba'ang min pas gzhi tsam du
NK050(wi)001:68: gnas so // de'i rang rtsal phyir g.yos pa'i tshe
NK050(wi)001:69: rang ngo rang gis ma rig pas gzhi'i gnas tshul
NK050(wi)001:70: dang mi mthun par thag pa la sbrul du 'khrul
NK050(wi)001:71: pa bzhin blo gzung 'dzin can du shar dus sems
NK050(wi)001:72: sam rnam shes zhes bya ste 'khrul pa yin zhing
NK050(wi)001:73: gnas so // / des 'khor ba'i bag chags thams cad 'dzin zhing sdud pa'i gzhi byed la /
NK050(wi)001:74: rtsal des rang ngo rang gis rig ste /
NK050(wi)001:75: thag pa la thag par mthong ba bzhin phyin ci
NK050(wi)001:76: ma log par chos nyid kyi gnas tshul ji lta
NK050(wi)001:77: ba dang mthun par shar dus rig pa'am ye shes
NK050(wi)001:78: zhes bya ste / des ma rig pa dang 'khor
NK050(wi)001:79: ba'i bag chags thams cad 'jom par byed cing rnam
NK050(wi)001:80: par grol bar byed pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:82: 'di na sna tshogs snang ba kun //
NK050(wi)001:83: thag pa la ni sbrul mthong bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:84: de ma yin ga der bzung bas //
NK050(wi)001:85: phyi nang snod bcud gnyis su chags //
NK050(wi)001:86: de yang brtags na thag pa nyid //
NK050(wi)001:87: snod bcud ye nas stong pa nyid //
NK050(wi)001:88: don dam kun rdzob gzugs can no //
NK050(wi)001:89: sbrul mthong de nyid mthong bas bden //
NK050(wi)001:90: thag mthong yang dag nyid du bden //
NK050(wi)001:91: dper na tho la bya gnas bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:92: bden pa gnyis kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK050(wi)001:93: 'jig rten kun rdzob tsam du ste //
NK050(wi)001:94: yang dag nyid la 'brel ba med //
NK050(wi)001:95: stong pa nyid kyi dbyings la ni //
NK050(wi)001:96: de yi ngo bor thams cad grol //
NK050(wi)001:99: 'khrul ma myong pa'i ma rig rtsad //
NK050(wi)001:100: ma rtags ye nas chod nas 'dug /
NK050(wi)001:101: gang du 'di kun sus ma tshor //
NK050(wi)001:104: 'khor ba rnam rtog tsam nyid de //
NK050(wi)001:105: rnam rtog med pa thar pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:107: des na sems rnam shes tshogs brgyad chos can dang /
NK050(wi)001:108: de'i rang bzhin nam chos nyid kyi ye shes nyid tha snyad du gcig ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:109: sems rtogs pa tsam gyis sems kyi ye shes chos nyid mi rtogs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:111: gzung 'dzin yod med sogs kyi khyad par yod pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:112: don dam par tha dad pa ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:113: sems kyi rang bzhin ye shes yin pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:114: ye shes rtogs dus sems kyang de las tha dad du ma dmigs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:115: ye shes rtogs tshe sems rang grol du 'char ba sogs kyi phyir /
NK050(wi)001:116: des na de gnyis gcig tha dad gang du'ang khas len par mi bya ste /
NK050(wi)001:118: sems dang ye shes rnam pa gnyis //
NK050(wi)001:119: gcig min tha dad ma yin te //
NK050(wi)001:120: dbye ba rab tu dka' ba'i chos //
NK050(wi)001:121: sems ni ye shes rtsal yin te //
NK050(wi)001:122: sems kyi gzhi ma ye shes yin //
NK050(wi)001:125: sems kyi rang bzhin shes pas ni //
NK050(wi)001:128: sa chen gyis mdzad pa'i dbang bzhi ngo sprod las /
NK050(wi)001:129: rang byung ye shes skyes pa la //
NK050(wi)001:130: rtog pa kun kyang ye shes su //
NK050(wi)001:131: ngo bo nyid kyis 'char ba yin //
NK050(wi)001:132: bsgom dang ma sgom gnyis su med //
NK050(wi)001:133: rnam rtog chos kyi dbyings su thim //
NK050(wi)001:134: rtog pa'i dbang du 'gro mi srid //
NK050(wi)001:137: de ltar rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK050(wi)001:138: rnam shes ma mthong ye shes mthong //
NK050(wi)001:140: gzhan yang dgongs pa nges 'grel las /
NK050(wi)001:141: 'du byed khams dang don dam mtshan nyid ni //
NK050(wi)001:142: gcig dang tha dad bral ba'i mtshan nyid de //
NK050(wi)001:143: gcig dang tha dad nyid du gang rtog pa //
NK050(wi)001:144: de dag tshul min lta la yang zhugs pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:145: zhes bden gnyis gcig pa dang tha dad pa la skyon bzhi bzhi gsungs pa lta bu ste /
NK050(wi)001:146: gzhi 'di la ye shes su bzhag pa'ang /
NK050(wi)001:147: chos dbyings snang stong zung 'jug yin pas na stong
NK050(wi)001:148: rkyang tsam min par rig gdangs kyi cha yod pa
NK050(wi)001:149: dang / rang gi ngo bo 'khrul grol las 'das
NK050(wi)001:150: pa de las ma g.yos pa na ma 'khrul tsam
NK050(wi)001:152: gzhi las rtsal shar zin pa'i ye shes kyis ji
NK050(wi)001:153: bzhin par rtogs nas grol zin pa'i ye shes dang
NK050(wi)001:155: de bzhin du gdod ma'i gzhi dbyings dang /
NK050(wi)001:156: mthar thug gi ka dag grol sa gnyis kyang dbyings
NK050(wi)001:157: snang stong zung 'jug rang bzhin 'gyur med kyi cha
NK050(wi)001:159: tha snyad du slar 'khrul gzhi byed mi byed dang /
NK050(wi)001:160: rang rtsal shes rab rdzogs ma rdzogs dang /
NK050(wi)001:161: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'i sa bon spangs ma spang sogs kyi khyad par che'o //
NK050(wi)001:162: de'i phyir gzhi gnas kyi ye shes ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum dang /
NK050(wi)001:163: de las shar ba'i ye shes slob lam gyis bsdus pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:164: mthar phyin 'bras bu'i ye shes sangs rgyas kyi mkhyen
NK050(wi)001:165: pa gsum yang tha snyad du gcig ma yin la
NK050(wi)001:166: / don dam par tha dad ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:167: rtsa ba spros bral rang byung gi ye shes su gcig pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:168: des na lam gyi skabs lta ba 'khor 'das sam
NK050(wi)001:169: gzhi 'bras dbyer med du khas len pa'ang thog ma'i
NK050(wi)001:170: spyi gzhi tsam gyi ngos nas ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:171: de'i tshe grol 'khrul gnyis ka med pa'i phyir su zhig la ltos nas dbyer med brjod /
NK050(wi)001:173: rtsal las shar zin ma dag 'khrul pa'i phung khams
NK050(wi)001:174: skye mched sogs kyi chos 'di rnams gnas tshul dag
NK050(wi)001:175: par rab 'byams sangs rgyas kyis ji ltar gzigs pa
NK050(wi)001:176: bzhin bden gnyis dbyer med mnyam pa chen por ye
NK050(wi)001:177: nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du gtan la phab
NK050(wi)001:178: nas ngo bo dbyer med du khas len pa yin
NK050(wi)001:179: pas de ltar shan phyed pa gal che'o //
NK050(wi)001:180: mdor na sgyu 'phrul gsang snying las /
NK050(wi)001:181: e ma ho bde gshegs snying po las /
NK050(wi)001:182: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK050(wi)001:183: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK050(wi)001:184: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK050(wi)001:185: bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
NK050(wi)001:186: sus kyang ma bcings bcing med de //
NK050(wi)001:187: bcing bar bya bar yod ma yin //
NK050(wi)001:188: rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa yi //
NK050(wi)001:189: nan gyis mkha' la mdud pa 'dor //
NK050(wi)001:190: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:191: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK050(wi)001:192: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzod //
NK050(wi)001:195: ma rig rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK050(wi)001:197: mi mthun bde sdug myong bar 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:198: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK050(wi)001:199: ces gsungs pa bzhin gzhi ye nas 'ching grol med
NK050(wi)001:200: pa'i gnas lugs zab mo nyid gtan la ma phebs
NK050(wi)001:201: na rnam grol mthar thug gi 'bras bu mngon du
NK050(wi)001:203: don gyi gnas 'di la nges don gyi mdo rgyud
NK050(wi)001:204: bstan bcos thams cad dgongs pa mthun pas de'i tshul
NK050(wi)001:205: ni da lta rtsal las shar zin gyi 'khrul pa'i
NK050(wi)001:206: skabs dri mas bsgribs pa'i dus nyid na'ang gzhi rang
NK050(wi)001:207: gi ngo bo la ni dri ma med pas rang
NK050(wi)001:208: bzhin rnam dag chen po'am sems kyi rang bzhin 'od
NK050(wi)001:210: ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK050(wi)001:212: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo la //
NK050(wi)001:213: gzung 'dzin dri ma gzhi la med //
NK050(wi)001:214: de phyir rang byung snying po 'di //
NK050(wi)001:215: sus kyang ma byas bzo bcos min //
NK050(wi)001:216: rang byung rig pa'i rgyal po yin //
NK050(wi)001:219: 'gyur med byang chub sems la 'khrul ba ga la yod //
NK050(wi)001:220: 'khrul med byang chub sems ni 'gro ba yongs la khyab //
NK050(wi)001:221: byang chub snying po sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK050(wi)001:223: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK050(wi)001:224: ci ste nam mkha' nyon mongs bya bar nus //
NK050(wi)001:225: de la rjes kyang bstan par nus srid kyi //
NK050(wi)001:226: rang bzhin 'od gsal rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems //
NK050(wi)001:227: de ni nam yang nyon mongs bya mi nus //
NK050(wi)001:230: sems ni rtag tu rang bzhin 'od gsal 'dod //
NK050(wi)001:231: de ni glo bur nyes pas ma rung byas //
NK050(wi)001:232: chos nyid sems las gzhan pa'i sems gzhan ni //
NK050(wi)001:233: 'od gsal ma yin rang bzhin la brjod do //
NK050(wi)001:236: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal gang yin pa //
NK050(wi)001:237: de ni nam mkha' bzhin du 'gyur med de //
NK050(wi)001:238: yang dag min rtog las byung 'dod chags sogs //
NK050(wi)001:239: glo bur dri mas de nyon mongs mi 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:242: sa yi dkyil na yod pa'i chu //
NK050(wi)001:243: dri ma med par gnas pa ltar //
NK050(wi)001:244: nyon mongs nang na ye shes kyang //
NK050(wi)001:245: de bzhin dri ma med par gnas //
NK050(wi)001:247: 'di'i snang cha nas gzugs sku'i yon tan dang /
NK050(wi)001:248: stong cha nas chos sku'i yon tan rdzogs par ldan yang /
NK050(wi)001:249: da lta sems can gyi skabs dri mas bsgribs te
NK050(wi)001:250: mngon sum mi snang ba'i cha nas khams sam rigs
NK050(wi)001:251: dang / sangs rgyas pa'i tshe dri ma mtha' dag dang bral dus byang chub ces brjod kyang /
NK050(wi)001:252: ngo bo sems nyid kyi nus pa rdzogs par snang
NK050(wi)001:253: mi snang tsam las sngar med gsar skyer 'dod pa
NK050(wi)001:254: ni min te / rgyud bla ma las /
NK050(wi)001:255: 'dus ma byas shing lhun gyis grub //
NK050(wi)001:257: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:258: 'gyur ba med pa chos nyid do //
NK050(wi)001:260: spros bral don gsal chen po'i rgyud las /
NK050(wi)001:261: chos sku rang byung ye shes la //
NK050(wi)001:262: rgyu rkyen med pas 'dus byas med //
NK050(wi)001:265: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa la //
NK050(wi)001:266: rgyu dang rkyen gyis bskyed pa 'khrul //
NK050(wi)001:268: de la 'khor chos las dang nyon mongs pa rnams rten pa med pa'i tshul gyis brten pa ni /
NK050(wi)001:269: nyi mkha'i ngos sprin brten pa ltar //
NK050(wi)001:270: gzhi la ma reg ma 'byar la de'i ngang du gnas pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:271: don la rang bzhin med pas rten brten par ma grub bzhin brten par btags pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:273: sa ni chu la chu rlung la //
NK050(wi)001:274: rlung ni mkha' la rab tu gnas //
NK050(wi)001:275: mkha' ni rlung dang chu dag dang //
NK050(wi)001:276: sa yi khams la gnas ma yin //
NK050(wi)001:277: de bzhin phung po khams dbang rnams //
NK050(wi)001:278: las dang nyon mongs dag la brten //
NK050(wi)001:279: las dang nyon mongs tshul bzhin min //
NK050(wi)001:280: yid la byed la rtag tu gnas //
NK050(wi)001:281: tshul bzhin ma yin yid byed ni //
NK050(wi)001:282: sems kyi dag pa la rab gnas //
NK050(wi)001:283: sems kyi rang bzhin chos rnams ni //
NK050(wi)001:284: thams cad la yang gnas ma yin //
NK050(wi)001:287: dri med nyi ma zla ba yang //
NK050(wi)001:288: sprin dang khug sna du ba dang //
NK050(wi)001:289: sgra gcan gdong dang rdul la sogs //
NK050(wi)001:290: sgrib pa lnga yis bsgribs par 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:291: de bzhin 'od gsal ba yi sems //
NK050(wi)001:292: 'dod dang gnod sems le lo dang //
NK050(wi)001:293: rgod pa dang ni the tshom ste //
NK050(wi)001:294: sgrib pa lnga yis bsgribs par 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:297: las dang nyon mongs rnam rtog las //
NK050(wi)001:298: de dag spros las spros pa ni //
NK050(wi)001:300: zhes gsungs pa bzhin don du med snang glo bur
NK050(wi)001:301: ba zag bcas las nyon sogs 'khor ba'i chos 'di
NK050(wi)001:303: thog med nas gzung 'dzin rnam rtog gi spros pa'i bag chags las byung zhing /
NK050(wi)001:304: spros pa de gang las byung na sems las byung /
NK050(wi)001:305: sems ni da lta'i sems gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par shar ba 'di yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:306: 'di gang las byung na gdod ma'i 'od gsal chen
NK050(wi)001:307: po'i rtsal la bdag tu zhen pa las byung zhing
NK050(wi)001:308: / gdod ma'i 'od gsal chen po ni zung 'jug
NK050(wi)001:309: spros pa dang bral bas gang la'ang mi gnas shing
NK050(wi)001:310: gang yang phyogs su lhung ba med pas /
NK050(wi)001:311: chos thams cad de'i ngang las byung /
NK050(wi)001:313: de'i ngang du thim pas 'khrul pa'i phu thag chod
NK050(wi)001:314: pa 'di rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i khyad chos
NK050(wi)001:315: yin la / de nyid shin tu gsal bar go bder brjod na /
NK050(wi)001:316: ye thog gzhi yi gnas lugs sam 'od gsal ni
NK050(wi)001:317: rtogs zin 'khrul zin gnyis ka min pas gzhi dbyings
NK050(wi)001:318: lung ma bstan zhes bya ste dpe 'chi ba'i 'od
NK050(wi)001:319: gsal bzhin no // de yang sems can rnams 'chi
NK050(wi)001:320: ba'i tshe snang gsum mtha'i nyer thob 'od gsal la
NK050(wi)001:321: thim pa'i skabs su shar ba'i 'od gsal de'i rang
NK050(wi)001:322: gi ngo bo ni dwangs gsal sgrib g.yog dang bral
NK050(wi)001:323: ba bston gnam dwangs ba lta bu ste /
NK050(wi)001:324: de'i tshe 'khrul sems gzung 'dzin gyi kun rtog rags
NK050(wi)001:325: phra rnams ni chos nyid kyi rtsal gzhi thim du
NK050(wi)001:326: song bas de'i dus na med pa'i phyir ro //
NK050(wi)001:327: 'on kyang phal pa rnams la lam rkyen med pas
NK050(wi)001:328: 'od gsal de'i rang rtsal ye shes ni ma shar
NK050(wi)001:329: bas / yul 'od gsal yod kyang yul can med pas su zhig gis ngos zin /
NK050(wi)001:330: de ltar ngos ma zin pa'i cha nas sems med
NK050(wi)001:331: mun pa'i gnas skabs sam brgyal ba zhes bya ste
NK050(wi)001:332: / 'od gsal rang gi ngo bo ni nag thom lung ma bstan brgyal ba lta bu min no //
NK050(wi)001:333: de las rim pa sngon gyi bag chags kyi dbang
NK050(wi)001:334: gis snang gsum phra ba nas je rags su shar
NK050(wi)001:335: nas bar do'i yid lus rmi lam gyi snang ba
NK050(wi)001:336: ltar 'char te / 'dis sems can rnams gdod ma'i gzhi las 'khrul tshul mtshon nus /
NK050(wi)001:337: yang da ltar 'od gsal zin pa rnams sngar bla
NK050(wi)001:338: mas ngo sprod pa'i sems kyi chos nyid rig stong
NK050(wi)001:339: rjen pa la yang yang goms par byas pa'i lam
NK050(wi)001:341: de dus shar ba'i gzhi'i 'od gsal ma lta bu
NK050(wi)001:342: de ngos zin nas bar do med par yar gyi
NK050(wi)001:343: zang thal du grol bar byed pa de 'dis gdod
NK050(wi)001:344: ma'i gzhi las gzhi snang g.yos tshe kun tu bzang
NK050(wi)001:345: po'i shes rab rang byung gi ye shes kyis rang
NK050(wi)001:346: ngo rang gis rig ste gzhi gnas lhan skyes kyi
NK050(wi)001:347: ma rig pa bcom nas nang dbyings 'od gsal chen
NK050(wi)001:348: po ka dag gi grol sar mngon par byang chub
NK050(wi)001:349: ste 'gro ba rnams la thog ma'i lam ston pa
NK050(wi)001:350: por byung tshul yang mtshon nus shing /
NK050(wi)001:351: de ltar sems ye shes su gnas gyur pa'am sems
NK050(wi)001:352: 'gag pa'i spangs pa de slar mi ldog pa ni
NK050(wi)001:353: blo gnyen po'i ngang tshul dang bral mi rung ba'i
NK050(wi)001:354: phyir dang / de la zlog byed kyi rkyen gzhan med pa'i phyir te /
NK050(wi)001:356: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal te //
NK050(wi)001:357: dri ma rnams ni glo bur ba //
NK050(wi)001:359: 'tshe ba med dang yang dag don //
NK050(wi)001:360: rang bzhin la ni phyin log gis //
NK050(wi)001:361: 'bad du zin kyang mi zlog ste //
NK050(wi)001:362: blo ni de phyogs 'dzin phyir ro //
NK050(wi)001:364: gdod ma'i dbyings las thugs rje'i rtsal g.yo tshul yang /
NK050(wi)001:365: da lta'i rang sems kyi 'char sgo sna tshogs pa
NK050(wi)001:366: 'di la byung gnas 'gro gsum gyi mtha' legs par
NK050(wi)001:367: brtags na gang nas kyang ma byung /
NK050(wi)001:369: gang du'ang mi 'gro ste sems kyi chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i dbyings las byung zhing /
NK050(wi)001:371: der thim pa'i tshul 'dis shes te /
NK050(wi)001:372: sems kyi chos nyid ni ye nas 'ching grol las
NK050(wi)001:373: 'das pa'i rang bzhin mnyam pa nyid ngo bo dus
NK050(wi)001:374: gsum 'pho 'gyur dang bral ba'i zag med 'dus ma
NK050(wi)001:376: da lta'i rang sems skad cig ma 'di'i steng nas
NK050(wi)001:377: 'khor 'das grol 'khrul thams cad kyi phug chod dgos
NK050(wi)001:378: kyi de las gzhan du chod thabs med do //
NK050(wi)001:379: des na da lta nas sems nyid rdzogs pa chen
NK050(wi)001:380: po rig stong mnyam pa nyid kyi don ngos zin
NK050(wi)001:381: par byas nas yang yang goms par bya ba ni
NK050(wi)001:382: cis kyang gal che zhing 'di nyid rdzogs rim kun
NK050(wi)001:383: gyi bla mar gyur pa'i gnad kyang de yin no
NK050(wi)001:384: // mdor na kun bzang smon lam las /
NK050(wi)001:385: snang srid 'khor 'das thams cad kun gzhi gcig lam
NK050(wi)001:386: gnyis 'bras bu gnyis rig dang ma rig cho 'phrul
NK050(wi)001:387: te zhes dang / kun gyi gzhi ni 'dus ma
NK050(wi)001:388: byas rang byung klong yangs brjod du med 'khor 'das
NK050(wi)001:389: gnyis ka'i ming med do de nyid rig nas sangs
NK050(wi)001:390: rgyas te ma rig sems can 'khor bar 'khyams zhes
NK050(wi)001:391: te zhes dang / dang / kun tu bzang po
NK050(wi)001:392: nga yis kyang rgyu rkyen med par gzhi yi don
NK050(wi)001:393: de nyid gzhi la rang byung rig phyi nang sgro
NK050(wi)001:394: skur skyon ma btags dran med mun pa'i sgrib ma
NK050(wi)001:395: gos de phyir rang snang skyon ma gos zhes dang
NK050(wi)001:396: te zhes dang / dang / / dang po sems
NK050(wi)001:397: can 'khrul pa kun gzhi la rig pa ma shar
NK050(wi)001:398: bas ci yang dran med thom me ba de ka
NK050(wi)001:399: ma rig 'khrul pa'i rgyu de la had kyis brgyal
NK050(wi)001:400: ba las dngangs skrag shes pa za zi 'byung de
NK050(wi)001:401: las bdag gzhan dgra 'dzin skyes bag chags rim bzhin
NK050(wi)001:402: brtas pa las 'khor ba lugs su 'jug pa 'byung
NK050(wi)001:403: zhes sogs rgyas par gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:404: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos sku ye shes sogs ni nam mkha' go 'byed dang /
NK050(wi)001:405: nyi ma la zer bzhin 'od gsal ba'i dbyings la
NK050(wi)001:406: nam yang 'bral mi shes pa'i chos nyid kyi tshul
NK050(wi)001:407: du dbyer med par brten te /
NK050(wi)001:409: rnam dbyer bcas pa'i mtshan nyid can //
NK050(wi)001:410: bla med chos kyi stong ma yin //
NK050(wi)001:413: rang rig sgron ma rang snang 'od kyi yul //
NK050(wi)001:414: rang la gnas te rang gsang thabs kyis chod //
NK050(wi)001:415: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa'i mchog don yin //
NK050(wi)001:416: sangs rgyas kun dang mi g.yo mnyam par gnas //
NK050(wi)001:419: rig pa'i gsal cha ma 'gags pa ngo bo gcig
NK050(wi)001:420: la ye shes lnga ye shes lnga po smin pa
NK050(wi)001:421: las thog ma'i sangs rgyas rigs lnga 'byung de las
NK050(wi)001:422: ye shes mtha' rgyas pas sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa
NK050(wi)001:423: gnyis byung ye shes lnga yi rtsal shar bas khrag
NK050(wi)001:424: 'thung drug cu tham pa byung de phyir gzhi rig
NK050(wi)001:426: ye shes klong gi rgyud las /
NK050(wi)001:427: rig pa ma bslad chos sku yin //
NK050(wi)001:428: rang bzhin ngo bo nyid kyi sku //
NK050(wi)001:429: rgyu rkyen ma skyes 'gyur ba med //
NK050(wi)001:433: sangs rgyas sku dang ye shes zhing khams dang //
NK050(wi)001:434: ye shes yon tan phrin las ji snyed pa //
NK050(wi)001:435: ye shes de nyid de ltar snang ba yin //
NK050(wi)001:436: gzhan nas ma yin de ltar lhun gyis grub //
NK050(wi)001:438: mdor na 'phags pa 'da' dka' ye shes las /
NK050(wi)001:439: sems rtogs na sangs rgyas yin pas sangs rgyas gzhan
NK050(wi)001:440: du mi 'tshol ba'i 'du shes rab tu bskyed par
NK050(wi)001:443: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK050(wi)001:444: 'on kyang glo bur dri mas bsgribs //
NK050(wi)001:445: de bsal na ni sangs rgyas dngos //
NK050(wi)001:448: rin chen sems las phyir gyur pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:449: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med //
NK050(wi)001:452: dus bzhi phyogs bcu gang nas kyang //
NK050(wi)001:453: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:454: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas pas //
NK050(wi)001:455: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma 'tshol cig /
NK050(wi)001:458: byang chub byang chub nga yi rang bzhin las //
NK050(wi)001:459: ma bcol rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa ni //
NK050(wi)001:460: rgyal ba kun gyi snying po sku gsum ste //
NK050(wi)001:461: nga yi rang bzhin ma bcos chos skur grub //
NK050(wi)001:462: nga yi ngo bo ma bcos longs spyod rdzogs //
NK050(wi)001:463: nga yi thugs rje mngon phyung sprul sku gsum //
NK050(wi)001:464: btsal nas grub pa'i 'bras bur bstan pa min //
NK050(wi)001:465: ma btsal ye nas lhun gyis grub pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:466: zhes gsungs pa ltar sangs rgyas sku gsum yang rang
NK050(wi)001:467: rig pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du ye
NK050(wi)001:468: nas ma btsal lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid du
NK050(wi)001:469: bzhugs pa ste / gnas lugs yang dag pa'i don la de ltar yin no //
NK050(wi)001:470: 'on kyang gang zag blo dman pa rnams la dang
NK050(wi)001:471: po nas bstan na bdag tu lta ba sogs kyi
NK050(wi)001:473: rgyal bas bka' 'khor dang por bden bzhi spang gnyen
NK050(wi)001:474: du lta bas gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa'i
NK050(wi)001:475: sgo tsam las kun gzhi dang bde gshegs snying po'i
NK050(wi)001:476: rang bzhin sogs dngos su ma bstan te dgongs 'grel
NK050(wi)001:477: las / len pa'i rnam par shes par zab cing phra //
NK050(wi)001:478: sa bon thams cad chu bo'i rgyun bzhin 'bab //
NK050(wi)001:479: bdag tu rtog par gyur na mi rung bas //
NK050(wi)001:480: ngas 'di byis pa rnams la yongs ma bstan //
NK050(wi)001:483: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po las
NK050(wi)001:484: phyi rol du gyur pa byis pa so so'i skye
NK050(wi)001:487: las dang po pa stong pa nyid kyis sems rnam
NK050(wi)001:488: par g.yengs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams lags so
NK050(wi)001:492: bshad na nyan thos rang sangs rgyas //
NK050(wi)001:493: rab tu skrag ste brgyal bar 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:494: des na mchog tu gsang bar bya //
NK050(wi)001:496: bar par rnam thar gsum ldan gyi chos dbyings ngo
NK050(wi)001:497: bo stong phyogs nas ji lta bzhin ston par mdzad
NK050(wi)001:498: de / de yang gnas skabs su 'khor 'das kyi
NK050(wi)001:499: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis ma grub pa nyid
NK050(wi)001:500: de / don dam dang / de'i snang cha rten
NK050(wi)001:501: 'byung sgyu ma lta bu'i chos la kun rdzob tu
NK050(wi)001:502: bzhag ste 'phags slob kyi rjes thob kyi gzigs dang
NK050(wi)001:503: mthun par bden pa gnyis su dbye bar mdzad kyang
NK050(wi)001:504: de / don dam dang / / mthar thug sher
NK050(wi)001:505: mdo nas stong nyid bzhi sbyor du gsungs pa sogs
NK050(wi)001:506: kyi dgongs pa snang stong zung 'jug chos dbyings sgro
NK050(wi)001:508: dam pa'i don gyi bden gcig rnam grangs ma yin
NK050(wi)001:509: pa'i don dam 'phags slob kyi mnyam bzhag gi gzigs
NK050(wi)001:510: pa mthun par gtan la phabs nas /
NK050(wi)001:511: de'i don la gzung 'dzin med pa'i sems kyis mnyam par 'jog par gsungs te /
NK050(wi)001:513: gzugs kyi rang bzhin gang yin pa //
NK050(wi)001:514: de ni stong pa nyid bzhin du //
NK050(wi)001:515: stong pa nyid kyang gzugs su brjod //
NK050(wi)001:516: rang bzhin gdod nas ma skyes pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:518: tshig bral ngag gi lam gyis mi mtshon pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:519: de bzhin nyid chos rang bzhin nam mkha' 'dra //
NK050(wi)001:520: sems dang yid kyi rgyu ba rnams spangs pa //
NK050(wi)001:521: mchog rab ngo mtshar che ba dam pa shes //
NK050(wi)001:524: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK050(wi)001:525: ma skyes mi 'gag nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK050(wi)001:526: so so rang rig ye shes spyod yul ba //
NK050(wi)001:527: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK050(wi)001:530: tshu rol pha rol mtha' la min //
NK050(wi)001:531: de dag par na mi gnas pa //
NK050(wi)001:532: dus rnams mnyam pa nyid shes phyir //
NK050(wi)001:533: shes rab pha rol phyin par 'dod //
NK050(wi)001:536: bzhag par bya ba cung zad med //
NK050(wi)001:537: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK050(wi)001:538: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK050(wi)001:541: kun rdzob dang ni don dam dag /
NK050(wi)001:542: so so'i char ni shes gyur te //
NK050(wi)001:543: gang du yang dag 'dres gyur pa //
NK050(wi)001:544: zung du 'jug par de bshad do //
NK050(wi)001:546: brjod par bya ba ldog pa ste //
NK050(wi)001:547: sems kyi spyod yul ldog pas so //
NK050(wi)001:548: ma skyes pa dang mi 'gag pa //
NK050(wi)001:549: chos nyid mya ngan 'das dang mtshungs //
NK050(wi)001:551: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK050(wi)001:552: blo ni kun rdzob yin par 'dod //
NK050(wi)001:554: gang tshe dngos dang dngos med dag /
NK050(wi)001:555: blo yi mdun na mi gnas pa //
NK050(wi)001:556: de tshe rnam pa gzhan med pas //
NK050(wi)001:557: dmigs pa med par rab tu zhi //
NK050(wi)001:559: de yang chos nyid kyi rang mtshan ji lta ba
NK050(wi)001:560: mngon du gzigs pa 'phags pa'i sa na yin kyang
NK050(wi)001:561: / de'i don spyi bsgom pa tshogs sbyor gyi skabs su'ang med pa ni ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:562: chos nyid rang gi ngo bo spros bral gnyis snang med pa'i mtshan nyid can yin pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:563: de gsar byung min par ye nas sems kyi chos nyid du gnas pa'i gnad kyis /
NK050(wi)001:564: de'i don spyi blo la snang ba dpe nam mkha'i
NK050(wi)001:565: gzugs brnyan chu la shar ba lta bu yin pas
NK050(wi)001:566: / blo yang spros bral gnyis snang med pa'i rnam par 'char ba ste /
NK050(wi)001:567: de'ang ri mor bris pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:568: chu zla dang gnam zla'i dpes go myong rtogs gsum
NK050(wi)001:569: gyi khyad par gsungs pa bzhin snga ma gnyis ci
NK050(wi)001:570: rigs so skye'i sar yod de /
NK050(wi)001:571: 'di la mdo las stong nyid don spyi'i tshul du
NK050(wi)001:572: rtogs pa dang sngags su dpe yi ye shes zhes
NK050(wi)001:574: de tsam gyis so skye'i gang zag de 'phags par thal ba'i nyes pa'ang med de /
NK050(wi)001:575: da dung mthong spang gi sgrib pa las ma grol ba'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:576: dper na sa dang po'i 'phags pa de sangs rgyas su mi 'gyur ba yin no //
NK050(wi)001:577: de ltar byang sems blo che ba rnams kyis legs par rtogs shing goms pas /
NK050(wi)001:578: gnyen po'i ye shes de nyid kyis /
NK050(wi)001:579: spang bya glo bur dri ma rnams kyis spang ba'am
NK050(wi)001:580: bral ba'i stobs kyis chos dbyings kun tu 'gro ba'i
NK050(wi)001:581: don rtogs shing / chos dbyings de stong rkyang min
NK050(wi)001:582: par ye nas snang stong zung du 'jug pa'i gnad
NK050(wi)001:583: kyi yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis sogs rigs khams
NK050(wi)001:584: kyi yon tan rnams gong 'phel gyi tshul du dag
NK050(wi)001:585: sar zhing dag sbyor dang srid zhi mnyam nyid mthar
NK050(wi)001:586: thug sangs rgyas kyi sa'i sku dang zhing khams kyi
NK050(wi)001:587: bar du snang ba yin na'ang /
NK050(wi)001:588: blo chung ba rnams kyis de ltar ma rtogs shing
NK050(wi)001:589: snying po'i rang bzhin rang la yod par ma thos
NK050(wi)001:590: nas / stong rkyang rnam grangs pa tsam la don dam mthar thug tu bzung ba'i dbang gis /
NK050(wi)001:591: sems zhums sems can dman la brnyas pa sogs kyi
NK050(wi)001:592: skyon lnga po 'jug pas mnyam pa chen po'i don
NK050(wi)001:594: skyon de rnams spangs pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:595: 'khor lo tha mar rang bzhin sku dang ye shes
NK050(wi)001:596: sogs sangs rgyas kyi chos gang+ga'i klung gi bye ma
NK050(wi)001:597: snyed kyi grangs las brgal ba'i gzhal med bsam mi
NK050(wi)001:598: khyab pa'i tshogs rnams 'bral mi shes pa'i chos nyid
NK050(wi)001:599: kyi tshul du rigs khams la da lta sems can
NK050(wi)001:600: gyi dus nas 'phel 'bri med par sa 'og gi
NK050(wi)001:601: gter dang bum nang gi sgron me sogs kyi dpes
NK050(wi)001:602: gnas tshul mthar thug pa ji bzhin par ston par
NK050(wi)001:605: sprin dang rmi lam sgyu bzhin de dang der //
NK050(wi)001:606: shes bya thams cad rnam kun stong pa zhes //
NK050(wi)001:607: gsungs nas yang 'dir rgyal rnams sems can la //
NK050(wi)001:608: sangs rgyas snying po yod ces ci ste gsungs //
NK050(wi)001:610: sems zhums sems can dman pa brnyas pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:611: yang dag min 'dzin yang dag chos la bskur //
NK050(wi)001:612: bdag chags lhag pa'i skyon lnga gang dag la //
NK050(wi)001:613: yod pa de dag de spangs don du gsungs //
NK050(wi)001:615: de ltar spangs pas yon tan ci zhig thob na /
NK050(wi)001:616: rang gzhan gyi rgyud la sangs rgyas kyi snying po
NK050(wi)001:617: yod pa shes pas rang sems zhums pa bzlog nas
NK050(wi)001:618: thar pa sgrub pa la dka' ba med par shes
NK050(wi)001:620: sems can gzhan la brnyas pa bzlog nas ston pa
NK050(wi)001:621: bzhin du thams cad sangs rgyas su mnyam pa'i gus
NK050(wi)001:623: yang dag pa'i don sku dang ye shes kyi dgongs
NK050(wi)001:624: pa rang la gnas pa mi shes pa bzlog nas
NK050(wi)001:625: don dam pa'i dbyings rtogs pa'i shes rab dang /
NK050(wi)001:626: gnas lugs de ltar shes pa yod med rtag chad
NK050(wi)001:627: kyi sgro skur bzlog nas don dam pa'i don rtogs
NK050(wi)001:629: bdag nyid la mchog tu rlom pa'i lhag par chags
NK050(wi)001:630: pa bzlog nas bdag gzhan mtshungs par rtogs te gzhan
NK050(wi)001:631: la byams pa chen po skye bar 'gyur te /
NK050(wi)001:633: spro dang ston pa bzhin gus dang //
NK050(wi)001:634: shes rab ye shes byams chen te //
NK050(wi)001:635: chos lnga skye phyir de las ni //
NK050(wi)001:636: kha na ma tho med mtshungs lta //
NK050(wi)001:637: skyon med yon tan ldan pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:638: bdag dang sems can mtshungs byams las //
NK050(wi)001:639: sangs rgyas nyid ni myur du thob //
NK050(wi)001:641: de lta'i yon tan gyi chos rgyud la skyes te
NK050(wi)001:642: mnyam pa chen po'i don rtogs pas rdzogs smin sbyang
NK050(wi)001:643: ba rgya mtsho lta bu la 'jug nus pa'i phyir
NK050(wi)001:644: / bde gshegs snying po'i sgra thos pa tsam gyis
NK050(wi)001:645: kyang byang chub las phyir mi ldog par mdo las
NK050(wi)001:646: / gsungs so // 'di la kha cig drang don du 'dod pa ni rnam par 'khyams te /
NK050(wi)001:648: sems zhums pa sogs lnga po skyon du mi 'gyur zhing spang mi nus shing /
NK050(wi)001:649: gnyen po'i 'dzin stang lnga po 'chang ba'ang don la mi gnas pas dgos pa med pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:650: rgyud bla'i rang tshig dang yang dngos su 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK050(wi)001:651: des na snying po'i rang bzhin ma bstan pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:652: gsal bar mi bstan pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:653: rdzogs par bstan pa'i cha nas bka' 'khor snga ma gnyis la bla na mchis pa /
NK050(wi)001:655: drangs pa'i don rtsod pa'i gzhir gyur pa sogs dang /
NK050(wi)001:656: phyi ma de las ldog ste /
NK050(wi)001:659: nges pa'i don rtsod pa'i gzhir ma gyur pa sogs kyi basngagasa pa rgya cher gsungs pa yin no //
NK050(wi)001:660: tshul de ltar ma shes par bka' 'khor gsum go bzlog dang /
NK050(wi)001:661: drang nges kyi 'chad tshul sna tshogs pa zhig byung mod /
NK050(wi)001:662: 'o skol ni sangs rgyas rang nyid kyis ji ltar
NK050(wi)001:663: bzhag pa las 'gongs te smra bar mi nus pas
NK050(wi)001:665: mdo sde dgongs pa nges 'grel las /
NK050(wi)001:666: bcom ldan 'das kyis dang por yul w+aa ra na
NK050(wi)001:667: si drang srong smra ba'i ri dwags kyi nags su
NK050(wi)001:668: nyan thos kyi theg pa la yongs su zhugs pa
NK050(wi)001:669: rnams la 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi'i rnam par bstan
NK050(wi)001:670: pas chos kyi 'khor lo ngo mtshar rmad du byung
NK050(wi)001:671: ba / sngon lhar gyur pa'am mir gyur pa sus
NK050(wi)001:672: kyang chos dang mthun par 'jig rten du ma bskor
NK050(wi)001:673: ba gcig rab tu bskor te zhes dang /
NK050(wi)001:674: bcom ldan 'das kyis chos kyi ngo bo nyid ma mchis pa nyid las brtsams /
NK050(wi)001:675: skye ba ma mchis pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:677: gzod ma nas zhi ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:678: rang bzhin gyis mya ngan las 'das pa nyid las brtsams nas /
NK050(wi)001:679: theg pa chen po la yang dag par zhugs pa
NK050(wi)001:680: rnams la stong pa nyid smos pa'i rnam pas ngo
NK050(wi)001:681: mtshar rmad du byung ba'i chos kyi 'khor lo gnyis
NK050(wi)001:683: bcom ldan 'das kyis chos rnams kyi ngo bo nyid ma mchis pa nyid las brtsams /
NK050(wi)001:684: skye ba ma mchis pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:686: gzod ma nas zhi ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:687: rang bzhin gyis mya ngan las 'das pa nyid las brtsams nas /
NK050(wi)001:688: theg pa thams cad la yang dag par zhugs par
NK050(wi)001:689: rnams la legs par rnam par phye ba dang ldan
NK050(wi)001:690: pa / shin tu ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i
NK050(wi)001:691: chos kyi 'khor lo gsum pa bskor te zhes dang
NK050(wi)001:692: pa / / snga ma gnyis kyi skabs su bla na ma mchis pa sogs bzhi dang /
NK050(wi)001:693: phyi ma la bla na ma mchis pa sogs kyi basngagasa par mdzad do //
NK050(wi)001:694: de ltar basngagasa pa'ang 'khor tha ma'i mdo yin tshad la ni ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:695: snying po'i rang bzhin gsal bar bstan pa'i mdo rnams
NK050(wi)001:696: yin par kun mkhyen mi pham rin po ches bzhed
NK050(wi)001:697: do // de lta bu'i chos 'khor rim pa gsum
NK050(wi)001:698: po dag gis gang du sgrib byed glo bur pa'i
NK050(wi)001:701: shin tu phra ba'i tshul rnams sbyong byed kyi thabs rgya che chung las /
NK050(wi)001:702: don du gshegs snying gcig pu'i steng gi dri ma sbyong ba la gsum ka mthun zhing /
NK050(wi)001:703: 'di ltar dang pos mi rtag pa sogs kyis 'khor
NK050(wi)001:704: ba las yid 'byung zhing mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK050(wi)001:708: 'bras bu smon med de rnam par thar pa'i sgo
NK050(wi)001:709: gsum gyi 'jig rten pa'i mtshan 'dzin gyi gnyen por
NK050(wi)001:710: 'gyur zhing / gsum pa phyir mi ldog pa'i gtam
NK050(wi)001:711: gyis bde bar gshegs pa'i tshul rgya chen po khong
NK050(wi)001:712: du chud par byed pa dgongs pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:713: gzungs kyi dbang phyug rgyal pos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK050(wi)001:714: rigs kyi bu 'di ltar dper na nor bu mkhan
NK050(wi)001:715: mkhas pas nor bu sbyong ba'i tshul legs par shes
NK050(wi)001:716: pa des / nor bu rin po che'i rigs nas yongs su ma dag pa'i nor bu blangs te /
NK050(wi)001:717: lan tsh+wa'i chu rnyog por spangs nas skra'i re bas yongs su sbyong bar byed do //
NK050(wi)001:718: de bzhin de'i 'og tu sman bzang po'i khu bas spangs te ras srab mo /
NK050(wi)001:719: yongs su sbyong bar byed do //
NK050(wi)001:720: yongs su sbyongs te dri ma dang bral ba ni beed+aur+ya'i rigs chen po zhes brjod do //
NK050(wi)001:721: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa yang /
NK050(wi)001:722: yongs su ma dag pa'i sems can la dang po mi rtags pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:723: sdug bsngal ba sogs yid 'byung ba'i gtam gyis 'dul ba la 'dzud par mdzad pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:724: de'i 'og tu rnam par thar pa gsum gyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i tshul rtogs par mdzad pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:725: de'i 'og tu phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo'i gtam
NK050(wi)001:726: gyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i yul la 'jug par mdzad
NK050(wi)001:727: do // zhugs par gyur cing chos nyid rtogs na ni bla na med pa'i yon gnas so //
NK050(wi)001:730: mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdo las /
NK050(wi)001:731: bud med bu chung ngu kha nyags pa gso ba'i sman btang ba'i dpe sngon du btang nas /
NK050(wi)001:733: de bzhin gshegs pa yang sems can thams cad bsgral ba'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:734: sems can thams cad la bdag med pa'i nan tan ston te /
NK050(wi)001:735: de la nan tan du byas pa'i bdag ces bya ba'i sems med de /
NK050(wi)001:736: yongs su mya ngan las bazla'o //
NK050(wi)001:737: de la'ang 'jig rten rgyang 'phan pa'i ngan par blta ba bsal ba'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:738: bdag med pa'i chos bsgoms pas yongs su dag pa'i
NK050(wi)001:739: lus su 'byung ba'i phyir ji ltar bud med de
NK050(wi)001:740: la bu'i phyir mkhris pas nu ma la bskus pa
NK050(wi)001:741: bzhin du / de bzhin gshegs pa yang de dang 'dra ste /
NK050(wi)001:742: stong pa nyid bsgom pa'i phyir chos thams cad la bdag med ces gsungs so //
NK050(wi)001:743: ji ltar bud med des nu ma phyis bkrus nas bu bos te /
NK050(wi)001:744: nu zho blud do zhes bya ba ji bzhin du /
NK050(wi)001:745: ngas de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po bstan pa yang de dang 'dra ste /
NK050(wi)001:746: dge slong khyod ma skrag par /
NK050(wi)001:747: ji ltar bu la mas bos te /
NK050(wi)001:748: nu zho blud do zhes bya ba ji bzhin du /
NK050(wi)001:749: ngas de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po bstan pa yang de dang 'dra ste /
NK050(wi)001:750: dge slong khyod ma skrag par /
NK050(wi)001:751: ji ltar bu la mas bos te /
NK050(wi)001:752: nu zho bgas kyis 'thung ba bzhin du /
NK050(wi)001:753: dge slong khyod kyang bye brag phyed par gyis shig /
NK050(wi)001:754: gzhan du ci yang med pa'i stong pa nyid bsgoms pa las ni /
NK050(wi)001:755: sangs rgyas kyi sku dang ye shes 'byung bar mi 'gyur te /
NK050(wi)001:756: 'bras bu ni rgyu'i rjes su byed pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:758: ngas shes rab kya pha rol tu phyin par chos thams cad stong pa nyid du bstan pa ni /
NK050(wi)001:759: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dang theg pa la
NK050(wi)001:760: gsar du zhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang
NK050(wi)001:761: / gzhan mu stegs can rnams kyis dngos po la mngon par zhen pa /
NK050(wi)001:762: bdag tu lta ba can 'du shes kyi 'dzin pas
NK050(wi)001:763: bcings pa rnams la phan gdags pa'i phyir gsungs kyi
NK050(wi)001:764: / de kho na nyid du na /
NK050(wi)001:765: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba ste /
NK050(wi)001:766: de bzhin nyid kyi don lhun gyis grub pa'i ngo bo nyid du rigs par bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:769: dper na sos ka'i dus la babs pa na /
NK050(wi)001:770: skye bo dag khrus ras bcings te /
NK050(wi)001:771: rang gi rgyan dang nye bar spyod pa dag gis tshul rtse'o //
NK050(wi)001:773: der gcig gis rigs dang ldan pa'i nor bu beed+aur+ya chu'i nang du bzhag pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:774: de nas bee d+aur+ya'i don du de dag thams cad rgyan bzhag nas chu la zhugs par gyur to //
NK050(wi)001:775: de nas de na yod pa'i gseg ma'am gyo mo de dag la nor bu'o snyam nas dbyung ngo //
NK050(wi)001:776: phyung nas rdzing bu'i 'gram du bltas pa ni 'di
NK050(wi)001:777: ni nor bu yin no snyam pa'i 'du shes rab
NK050(wi)001:778: tu 'jug go // rdzing gi chu de yang nor bu'i 'od dang 'dra bar snang ngo //
NK050(wi)001:779: de dag de ltar snang ba'i tshul mthong nas /
NK050(wi)001:780: e ma ho nor bu'o snyam pa'i 'du shes rab tu zhugs so //
NK050(wi)001:781: de nas de rnams la thabs mkhas shing yid gzhungs
NK050(wi)001:782: pa gcig gis nor bu de yang dag par rnyed
NK050(wi)001:783: par gyur to // dge slong dag de bzhin du
NK050(wi)001:784: nor bu ltar chos kyi de kho na nyid mi
NK050(wi)001:785: shes pa khyed rnams kyi thams cad mi rtag pa
NK050(wi)001:786: par gyur to // dang / thams cad sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:787: thams cad bdag med pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:789: zhes 'dzin pa thams cad kyis bsgom pa'i bya ba mang du byas shing /
NK050(wi)001:790: mang du byas pa la blo nye bar bzhag pa de dag thams cad ni don med do //
NK050(wi)001:791: dge slong dag de'i phyir rdzing gi gseg ma dang
NK050(wi)001:792: gyo mo rnam par gnas pa len pa ltar mi
NK050(wi)001:793: 'gyur bar khyed cag thabs la mkhas par gyis shig
NK050(wi)001:796: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba'i snying po sangs rgyas
NK050(wi)001:797: kyi rang bzhin yongs su dag pa mi 'gyur mi
NK050(wi)001:799: gal te yod par smra na mkhas pa shes rab can dag chags par mi rigs /
NK050(wi)001:800: gal te med par smra na brdzun du smra bar 'gyur ro //
NK050(wi)001:801: bus pa ma rabs ni chad par smra zhing /
NK050(wi)001:802: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba'i snying po mi shes so //
NK050(wi)001:803: gal te sdug bsngal bar smra na lus la bde ba'i rang bzhin yod pa mi shes so //
NK050(wi)001:804: bus pa glen pa dag lus thams cad mi rtag
NK050(wi)001:805: go snyam ste rdza so ma btang ba dang 'dra
NK050(wi)001:806: bar 'dzin to // de la mkhas pa shes rab
NK050(wi)001:807: can dag ni rnam par phye ste thams cad kyis
NK050(wi)001:808: thams cad du mi rtag par mi smra'o //
NK050(wi)001:810: bdag gi lus 'di la sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin kho na yod pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:811: bus pa glen pa dag sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad bdag med do snyam du 'dzin te /
NK050(wi)001:812: mkhas pa shes rab can dag ni bdag med pa bla dwags btags par zad de /
NK050(wi)001:813: bden pa med pas rnam par phye'o //
NK050(wi)001:814: de ltar shes nas the tshom mi bskyed do //
NK050(wi)001:815: yang de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po stong par smra na /
NK050(wi)001:816: bus pa glen pa dag gis thos nas chad pa'am med par lta ba skye'o //
NK050(wi)001:817: mkhas pa shes rab can dag ni de bzhin gshegs
NK050(wi)001:818: pa'i rigs mi 'gyur mi 'pho bar bye brag dabye'o
NK050(wi)001:819: // gang rnam par grol ba sgyu ma lta bur
NK050(wi)001:820: smra na bus pa glen pa dag rnam par grol
NK050(wi)001:821: ba rnams kyi chos yin no snyam du 'dzin to
NK050(wi)001:822: // // mkhas pa shes rab can rnam par phye
NK050(wi)001:823: ste mi'i nang na seng ge lta bur de lta
NK050(wi)001:824: bur de bzhin gshegs pa nyag gcig ni rtogs gnas
NK050(wi)001:825: pa mi 'gyur mi 'pho bar byed do //
NK050(wi)001:827: chos thams cad bdag med de de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po yang bdag med do zhes smras na /
NK050(wi)001:828: bus pa glen pa dag gnyis su 'dzin to //
NK050(wi)001:829: mkhas pa shes rab can dag ni rang bzhin gnyis su med par rtogs so //
NK050(wi)001:830: bdag dang bdag med par rang bzhin gyis gnyis su med do //
NK050(wi)001:831: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdo 'di de ltar dpag tu
NK050(wi)001:832: med cing tshad med mtha' yas par sangs rgyas bcom
NK050(wi)001:833: ldan 'das rnams kyis yongs su basngagasa pas /
NK050(wi)001:834: ngas kyang yon tan dang ldan pa'i mdo sde thams cad las rgyas par gsungs so //
NK050(wi)001:836: gzhan yang de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'i mdo las /
NK050(wi)001:837: stong gsum dar yug gi dpe sogs kyis bstan pas
NK050(wi)001:838: mtshon nges don gyi mdo sde rnams rgya cher gsungs
NK050(wi)001:839: shing / phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo'i mdo las /
NK050(wi)001:840: byang chub sems dpal sgra dbyangs snyan pas gsol ba /
NK050(wi)001:841: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis chos bstan pa mthun lags sam /
NK050(wi)001:842: rigs kyi bu sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis chos bstan pa ni mthun no //
NK050(wi)001:843: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi chos bstan pa ji tsam zhig mthun /
NK050(wi)001:845: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis chos bstan pa ni phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lor mthun no //
NK050(wi)001:849: ji ltar mdog ngan pad+ma'i khong gnas pa //
NK050(wi)001:850: mtshan stong gis 'bar de bzhin gshegs pa ni //
NK050(wi)001:851: dri med lha yi mig ldan mis mthong nas //
NK050(wi)001:852: chu skyes 'dab ma'i sbubs nas 'byin byed pa //
NK050(wi)001:853: de bzhin bde gshegs mnar med gnas la yang //
NK050(wi)001:854: sangs rgyas spyan gyi rang chos nyer gzigs te //
NK050(wi)001:855: sgrib med phyi ma'i mur gnas snying rje yi //
NK050(wi)001:856: bdag can sgrib pa las ni grol bar mdzad //
NK050(wi)001:857: ces sogs dpe dgus rgyas par gsungs pa'i don shing
NK050(wi)001:858: rta chen po 'phags pa thog med kyis rgyas par
NK050(wi)001:859: bkral ba dang / dpal mgon 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis //
NK050(wi)001:860: ji ltar spun pas g.yog gyur pa //
NK050(wi)001:862: de bzhin nyon mongs kyis g.yog pa /
NK050(wi)001:863: de ni sangs rgyas zhes mi btags //
NK050(wi)001:864: ji ltar spun pa las grol nas //
NK050(wi)001:866: de bzhin nyon mongs las grol na //
NK050(wi)001:867: chos kyi sku nyid rab tu gsal //
NK050(wi)001:868: chu shing snying po med do zhes //
NK050(wi)001:869: de yi 'bras bu sangs rgyas nyid //
NK050(wi)001:870: lus can kun la bdud rtsir 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:871: zhes sogs bstod tshogs rnams nas gsal bar bstan pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:872: de'i phyir rang lugs kun mkhyen chen po'i bzhed pa ni /
NK050(wi)001:873: bka' 'khor phyi ma gnyis ka'i nges don mthar thug
NK050(wi)001:874: gi zab gnad gcig par blo gnyis snang gi spyod
NK050(wi)001:875: yul las 'das pa'i dri ma med 'phags pa'i ye
NK050(wi)001:876: shes lam bden zag med nyid sgra ji bzhin par
NK050(wi)001:879: drang don dang nges don gyi rnam par bzhag pa ni /
NK050(wi)001:880: chos thams cad kyi chos nyid de bzhin nyid dbyings
NK050(wi)001:881: rang bzhin gyis dag pa sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i
NK050(wi)001:882: dgongs pa ni rang bzhin gyis dag cing 'pho 'gyur
NK050(wi)001:883: med pa skye 'gag gnas gsum las 'das pa nam
NK050(wi)001:884: mkha'i ngo bo ni nges pa'i don yin la /
NK050(wi)001:885: de ston pa'i bka' dang bstan bcos ma lus pa nges pa'i don gyi khongs su bsdu'o //
NK050(wi)001:886: chos spyan snang tshad la skye ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:894: skye mched la sogs pa'i rim pa rnam pa sna
NK050(wi)001:895: tshogs par snang ba rmi lam lta bu smra bsam
NK050(wi)001:896: brjod pa'i rim pas gzhal zhing sgro btags nas bstan
NK050(wi)001:897: pa thams cad drang pa'i don zhes bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:898: de ston pa'i bka' dang bstan bcos thams cad kun rdzob kyi nang du bsdu'o //
NK050(wi)001:899: dper na sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu zhes smra
NK050(wi)001:900: brjod dang bsam pas rloms pa ni kun rdzob la
NK050(wi)001:901: / don dam pa'i gshis gang yin pa de ni nges pa'i don te yang dag pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:903: ting rgyal sogs kyi lung gis sgrub par mdzad pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:904: 'o na khyi phag sogs sems can rnams kyi sems
NK050(wi)001:905: kyi rgyud la stobs bcu'i ye shes yod dam snyam
NK050(wi)001:906: na / stobs bcu'i yon tan de'i rgyud kyi gshegs snying la ye nas yod de /
NK050(wi)001:907: khams rang gi chos nyid kyi yon tan yin pas
NK050(wi)001:908: khams yod na yon tan yod mod kyis de mngon
NK050(wi)001:910: ral gri la gcod pa'i bya ba yod kyang shub
NK050(wi)001:911: tu chud pas gcod pa'i bya ba mngon gyur du
NK050(wi)001:912: med pa dang / me long la gzugs brnyan 'char
NK050(wi)001:913: rung gi yon tan yod kyang sgrom du bcug pa
NK050(wi)001:914: la mngon du mi 'char ba dang 'dra ste /
NK050(wi)001:915: rang gzhan gyi gang zag de'i rgyud la yod pa'i
NK050(wi)001:916: sgrib pas khams kyi yon tan mngon du mi snang
NK050(wi)001:917: te / der ma zad de'i rang sems kyi chos
NK050(wi)001:918: nyid rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong nyid yod kyang
NK050(wi)001:919: mngon du mi 'gyur yon tan ci la mngon /
NK050(wi)001:920: de'i phyir mngon gyur du med pa 'di la bsam nas /
NK050(wi)001:921: stobs bcu skye rung gi rgyu tsam yod kyis dngos
NK050(wi)001:922: su med zer ba yod pa'ang dpyad tshul de'i dbang
NK050(wi)001:924: skye rung gi rgyu de 'dus byas kyi sems skad
NK050(wi)001:925: cig ma'i phreng ba 'di yin na sems yin tshad
NK050(wi)001:926: stobs bcu skye rung du sgrub dka' la /
NK050(wi)001:927: sgrib gnyis bag chags sbyang stobs kyis sems nyid rang gis byed pa yin na /
NK050(wi)001:928: 'di 'dus ma byas kyi dbyings kyi yon tan yin pas smin pa'i rgyur mi rung ngo //
NK050(wi)001:929: 'di lta bu'i khams de sngags kyi skabs su gnyug sems gsungs pa de yin te /
NK050(wi)001:930: glang chen rab 'bog gi rgyud las /
NK050(wi)001:931: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK050(wi)001:932: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas 'od gsal zhing //
NK050(wi)001:933: rnal 'byor nyid dbyings smra bsam las 'das pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:934: mnyam nyid byang chub sems la rtag tu 'dud //
NK050(wi)001:936: mnyam sbyor gyi 'grel pa rong zom chos bzang gis mdzad pa las /
NK050(wi)001:937: byang chub sems ni rdo rje ste //
NK050(wi)001:938: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid yin //
NK050(wi)001:940: rang gi sems nyid gdod nas rnam par dag pa
NK050(wi)001:941: gang yin pa de ni dus thams cad du brtan
NK050(wi)001:943: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid de yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:944: de bas na de nyid du sbyar na de nyid
NK050(wi)001:945: yin pa'i phyir de grub par 'gyur ro zhes pa'i
NK050(wi)001:946: don to // yin pa la sgrub ci dgos zhe na /
NK050(wi)001:947: 'di ltar ma shes shing goms par ma gyur pa rnams /
NK050(wi)001:948: shes shing goms pa klong du gyur pa tsam la
NK050(wi)001:949: dngos grub thob ces tha snyad du 'jog pa ma
NK050(wi)001:950: gtogs par / ma thob par byar med do zhes shes par bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:951: byang chub kyi sems ni 'gyur ba med pa'i de bzhin nyid do //
NK050(wi)001:954: kun khyab 'gyur med rtag brtan rdo rje'i sems //
NK050(wi)001:955: mtha' yas dngos po kun gyi ngo bo nyid //
NK050(wi)001:957: chos rje zhe chen pa d+harma r+aa dzas /
NK050(wi)001:958: 'khor 'das chos kun byed po rang gi sems //
NK050(wi)001:959: gnyis 'dzin 'ching ba'i 'khrul snang sbubs rgya las /
NK050(wi)001:960: ye grol bde gshegs snying po 'dus ma byas //
NK050(wi)001:961: lhun rdzogs don gyi sangs rgyas /
NK050(wi)001:963: 'di rang gi ngo bo ye nas rnam par shes pa'i chos las 'das pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:964: sgrib pa kun las nges par grol ba'i gnyis med
NK050(wi)001:965: ye shes kyi mtshan nyid can yin pas 'di mngon
NK050(wi)001:966: du gyur na 'od gsal mngon du gyur pa yin
NK050(wi)001:967: pas dbu ma'i rig dpyad dang thabs lam sogs mtshan
NK050(wi)001:968: bcas kyi lam gzhan gsar du snon mi dgos te
NK050(wi)001:969: sbyor rdzogs kyi nyams len bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:970: de'i phyir dbang rnon in+d+ra b+ho d+hi lta bu gang
NK050(wi)001:971: zag cig car ba dbang dus su grol ba'ang yod
NK050(wi)001:972: pa yin la / so sor rtog pa'i shes rab
NK050(wi)001:973: ces pa'ang so so rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis
NK050(wi)001:974: yul dang yul can gnyis su med par rtogs pa
NK050(wi)001:975: pa yin la / la bya yi / rigs dpyad
NK050(wi)001:976: med dgag tsam dang sems tsam pa'i rnam shes rang
NK050(wi)001:977: rig rang gsal tsam ni ma yin te don dam
NK050(wi)001:978: blo'i yul du byar med par gsungs pa'i phyir ro
NK050(wi)001:979: pa yin la / la bya yi / // des
NK050(wi)001:980: na gnyug sems 'od gsal de nam yang rgyun chad
NK050(wi)001:981: pa yin la / la bya yi / // pa
NK050(wi)001:982: med la / ngo bo stong pas dmigs mtshon gang
NK050(wi)001:983: pa yin la / la bya yi / // pa
NK050(wi)001:984: med la / yang med kyang / stong yang min
NK050(wi)001:985: te mtshan ma med pa'i rang 'od gsal ba yin
NK050(wi)001:986: pa yin la / la bya yi / // pa
NK050(wi)001:987: med la / yang med kyang / / sgrib pa
NK050(wi)001:988: ma zad pa'i sems rgyud kyi gshegs snying la stobs
NK050(wi)001:989: bcu'i ye shes mngon gyur du med pa ni bdag
NK050(wi)001:991: bla med chos kyi yon tan dbyings de la med pa min kyang /
NK050(wi)001:992: mngon du 'gyur pa ni sgrib pa yod pa'i phyir te /
NK050(wi)001:993: thog med gyur pa tha ma dang ldan pa /
NK050(wi)001:994: rang bzhin gyis dag rtag pa'i chos can ni //
NK050(wi)001:995: thog med sbubs kyis bsgribs phyir mi mthong ste //
NK050(wi)001:996: ji ltar gser gyi gzugs ni sgrib pa bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:999: ji ltar rin chen bee d+aur+yara //
NK050(wi)001:1000: dus rnams kun tu 'od gsal yang //
NK050(wi)001:1001: rdo yi nang du gnas gyur pa //
NK050(wi)001:1002: de yi 'od ni gsal ma yin //
NK050(wi)001:1003: de bzhin nyon mongs kyis bsgribs pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:1004: chos dbyings shin tu dri med pa'ang //
NK050(wi)001:1008: 'dis khyi rgya la mtshan dpe yod med sogs kyi log rtog thams cad kyang sel nus te /
NK050(wi)001:1009: de sgrib dag zin dang yon tan mngon gyur gyis sangs rgyas dngos ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK050(wi)001:1010: gnas tshul dbang btsan du byas na /
NK050(wi)001:1011: khams rang gi ngo bo la sangs rgyas kyi yon
NK050(wi)001:1012: tan drug cu rtsa bzhi po sogs ye ldan min
NK050(wi)001:1013: na / de 'dra'i khams de yod kyang sangs rgyas kyi rigs su mi 'grub ste stong rkyang bzhin /
NK050(wi)001:1015: khams yod na ni las byas pas //
NK050(wi)001:1016: sa le sbram dag mthob par 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:1017: khams med na ni las byas kyang //
NK050(wi)001:1018: nyon mongs 'ba' zhig skyed par byed //
NK050(wi)001:1021: sngon rnal 'byor bsgom par 'dod pa zhig gis slob dpon la lung nod du phyin pa'i tshe /
NK050(wi)001:1022: slob dpon gyis sgom nus mi nus sad pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:1023: khyod kyi mgo la ma he'i rwa gnyis bsgoms shig gsungs pas /
NK050(wi)001:1024: des de bzhin nyan te rang gnas su bsgoms pas /
NK050(wi)001:1025: ting nge 'dzin grub ste thog mar kun brtags pa'i gzugs yid ngor dngos su gsal ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:1026: mthar dbang 'byor ba'i gzugs thog reg gi rnam pa dngos su byung bas /
NK050(wi)001:1027: gzhan la sbran nas spong khang gi sgo bshig ste
NK050(wi)001:1028: 'gro dgos par byung ba bzhin don la med kyang
NK050(wi)001:1029: bskyed rim bsgom pa sogs kyis mngon du 'gyur rung
NK050(wi)001:1030: ba dang / rang gi rtogs pa ma yin yang
NK050(wi)001:1031: gzhan gyi smon lam gyis kyang grub ste thag mkhan
NK050(wi)001:1032: rgan po la shing gi lha mos dngos grub byin
NK050(wi)001:1033: pas lus mdun rgyab gnyis kar byad bzhin dang rkang
NK050(wi)001:1034: lag yod par gyur pa'i lo rgyus bzhin /
NK050(wi)001:1035: lhag pa'i lhas byin gyis brlab pa las kyang de ltar snang du rung ba sogs kyi phyir /
NK050(wi)001:1036: rten cing 'brel 'byung gi nus pa'i mthu tsam las don la yod mi dgos so snyam na /
NK050(wi)001:1037: rten cing 'brel 'byung gi dbang gis de ltar 'byung
NK050(wi)001:1038: ba ni mi 'gal zhing sngags phyi rgyud rnams su
NK050(wi)001:1039: lha bskyed tshul de dang phyogs mthun lta bur gsungs
NK050(wi)001:1040: pa yod cing / der ma zad kun brtag goms
NK050(wi)001:1041: pa'i bskyed rim 'jig rten pa'i lam de 'dra phyi
NK050(wi)001:1043: mu stegs kha cig gis nam mkha' 'di dngos por
NK050(wi)001:1044: bsgom pas dbyug pa sogs kyis brdung du rung ba
NK050(wi)001:1045: dang / bskyed rim la goms pa dang rigs sngags kyi mthus gzugs gzhan du bsgyur ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:1046: dngos po sprul bsgyur byed pa sogs dang /
NK050(wi)001:1047: dka' bzlog ma sogs kyis byin gyis brlabs pas mig
NK050(wi)001:1048: 'phrul sogs thun mong gi grub pa thob pa dang
NK050(wi)001:1049: / rlung sems tsam gyi sgyu lus dang grong 'jug byed pa sogs ji snyed pa yod mod /
NK050(wi)001:1050: de tsam ni thar pa'i rgyur 'gro ba'ang ma yin la /
NK050(wi)001:1051: sngags phyi rgyud rnams su zhugs pas kyang rang lam
NK050(wi)001:1052: des 'dod gzugs kyi rig 'dzin mngon du byas te
NK050(wi)001:1053: / rten der sngags bla med la zhugs nas gzod
NK050(wi)001:1054: phyag rgya chen po mchog la sbyor dgos par gsungs
NK050(wi)001:1055: pa'i gnad kyang der thug pas /
NK050(wi)001:1056: 'dis sngags bla med nas gsungs pa'i rdzogs rim gyi
NK050(wi)001:1057: lha sku ngang sgyu 'od sogs rtsol med du 'char
NK050(wi)001:1058: ba'i gnad la ci'ang gnod mi nus te /
NK050(wi)001:1059: 'di ni chos nyid kyi rang gdangs 'ba' zhig las shar dgos pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:1061: mthar thug rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhi ka dag lhun grub zung 'jug kyang mi 'grub la /
NK050(wi)001:1062: kun tu bzang po ye thog gdod ma'i grol gzhir
NK050(wi)001:1063: mngon par byang chub pa'i tshe nang gsal phra ba'i
NK050(wi)001:1064: ye shes gting gsal 'gag pa med pa las phyir
NK050(wi)001:1065: gsal rang snang longs sku'i zhing sku sogs kyang 'char
NK050(wi)001:1067: kun tu bzang pos de'i sngon du bskyed rim kun
NK050(wi)001:1068: brtags kyi lam sogs gang yang bsgom par ma gsungs
NK050(wi)001:1069: shing / gzhan gyis byin gyis brlab pa sogs kyang ma gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:1070: de bzhin sems can rnams 'chi ba'i tshe 'chi ba'i
NK050(wi)001:1071: 'od gsal dang chos nyid bar do'i snang ba rnams
NK050(wi)001:1072: 'char bar gsar rnying gi rgyud sder gsungs na /
NK050(wi)001:1073: de ni de dag gis sngar goms pa'i stobs kyis ni ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:1074: gal te yin na lam ma bsgom pa'i sems can mi srid par 'gyur la /
NK050(wi)001:1075: yi dam gyi lha'i byin brlabs las shar ba yang min te /
NK050(wi)001:1076: yin na de dag de'i tshe cis mi grol //
NK050(wi)001:1077: des na sngags bla med thun mong ba phra thig sogs dang /
NK050(wi)001:1078: thun min sbyor rdzogs kyi nyams len skabs ka dag
NK050(wi)001:1079: stong chen 'od gsal gyi don la mnyam par bzhag
NK050(wi)001:1080: pas mkha' snang du ba me khyer sogs dang 'ja'
NK050(wi)001:1081: thig lha skur sogs rtsol med du 'char ba 'di
NK050(wi)001:1082: thams cad chos nyid kyi rtsal 'ba' zhig las shar
NK050(wi)001:1083: ba yin pa la smyon med la /
NK050(wi)001:1084: de lta na chos nyid de stong rkyang min par
NK050(wi)001:1085: sku dang ye shes kyi snang ba dang ye nas
NK050(wi)001:1086: 'du 'bral med pa 'dis chos nyid kyi rig pas
NK050(wi)001:1087: grub pa yin pas sus kyang gzhig par mi nus
NK050(wi)001:1088: so // de'i phyir kun gzigs rong pas rang byung ye shes chen por /
NK050(wi)001:1089: gsang sngags kyi tshul las snang ba thams cad rang
NK050(wi)001:1090: byung ye shes rang snang ba'i dkyil 'khor du 'dod
NK050(wi)001:1091: pa 'di la / rang gi grub mtha' 'dzin pa la la dag /
NK050(wi)001:1092: 'di dag ni gnyen po'i don du gsungs pa yin te /
NK050(wi)001:1093: mtshan nyid pa ma yin no zhe'am /
NK050(wi)001:1094: kun brtags pa dang dbang 'byor ba'i gzugs yin te mtshan nyid pa ma yin no zhe'am /
NK050(wi)001:1095: lung de'ang dgongs pa'i dbang gis gsungs pa yin te /
NK050(wi)001:1096: gzu bor gsungs pa yin no zhes de skad ma zer cig ces dang /
NK050(wi)001:1097: gsang sngags kyi tshul las ji skad gsungs pa 'di dag ni /
NK050(wi)001:1098: mtshan nyid par grub pa yin te yongs su brtags pa ma yin no //
NK050(wi)001:1099: de'i dbang gis bka' 'di yang gzu bor gsungs pa nyid yin te /
NK050(wi)001:1100: dgongs pa'i tshig ma yin no //
NK050(wi)001:1103: thig le chen po drug bshad pa'i skabs su /
NK050(wi)001:1104: chos nyid ni 'gyur ba med pa /
NK050(wi)001:1105: thig le ni spros pa dang bral ba'i don te /
NK050(wi)001:1106: sna tshogs pa'i chos kyis rang bzhin gzhan du 'gyur ba'ang med la /
NK050(wi)001:1107: mtshan ma'i spros pas zin pa'ang med /
NK050(wi)001:1108: mtshan ma gsal zhing dor pa yang ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:1109: mtshan ma nyid kyi ngo bo nyid de lta bu yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:1110: chos nyid kyi thig le zhes bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:1111: de nyid sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas dbyings kyi thig le'o //
NK050(wi)001:1112: de bzhin du dri ma thams cad gdod nas dag pas dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le /
NK050(wi)001:1113: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal te rang byung gi ye shes chen po'i thig le /
NK050(wi)001:1114: de las kun tu bzang po'i rol pa'i rgyan mi 'gog pas kun tu bzang po'i thig le /
NK050(wi)001:1115: de lta bu'i don de yang da gzod bgrod cing
NK050(wi)001:1116: sbyang ba la mi ltos te ye nas lhun gyis
NK050(wi)001:1117: grub pas / lhun gyis gnas pa'i thig le'o //
NK050(wi)001:1118: de la dang po gnyis ni sems can gyi 'khrul pas ma bslad pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1119: bar ma gsum ni gnyen po'i thabs kyis ma bcos pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1120: tha ma ni rtsol ba las 'das par la bzla ba'o //
NK050(wi)001:1121: 'di dag gis kyang byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK050(wi)001:1123: gol sa bcad pa rnams bstan pa yin la /
NK050(wi)001:1124: byang chub sems kyi bzhag thabs kyang rtsol ba dang
NK050(wi)001:1125: bral bar la bzla ba dang gdeng chod pa nyid
NK050(wi)001:1126: yin no // zhes gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:1127: de'i phyir gzhung kha cig tu 'khor lo bar ba
NK050(wi)001:1128: nas gsungs pa'i chos dbyings stong nyid la snying po'i
NK050(wi)001:1129: rang bzhin gsungs kyi zag med kyi yon tan rnams
NK050(wi)001:1130: drang ba'i don tsam las don la med ces gsungs
NK050(wi)001:1131: pa'ang yod mod / de ni mdo phyogs kyi gzhung
NK050(wi)001:1132: kha cig 'chad pa'i tshe bshad du rung tsam yin
NK050(wi)001:1133: yang 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa dang mtshams
NK050(wi)001:1134: sbyor pa'i skabs 'dir ni de ltar sbyar nas bshad
NK050(wi)001:1135: pa'ang yod mod / mi rung ste / sngags kyi
NK050(wi)001:1136: sgyu 'od sogs thabs zab mo la brten nas ye
NK050(wi)001:1137: shes 'char ba'i gnad rnams srog dang bral bar byas
NK050(wi)001:1138: pa'ang yod mod / mi rung ste / pa'i phyir ro // des na chos dbyings 'od gsal lam /
NK050(wi)001:1141: bde gshegs snying po zhes pa rnams don gcig pas 'di sangs rgyas kyi rigs mtshan nyid pa yin /
NK050(wi)001:1142: de yang sgrib bcas kyi rgyud la yod tshe 'tshang rgya rung gi rigs dang /
NK050(wi)001:1143: sangs rgyas tshe mngon gyur yin yang /
NK050(wi)001:1144: rang gi ngo bo 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid
NK050(wi)001:1145: yin pas snga phyi sogs kyi khyad par gnas tshul
NK050(wi)001:1146: la med de ngo bo 'gyur med yin pas so
NK050(wi)001:1147: // snang tshul gyi dbang du byas na glo bur
NK050(wi)001:1148: gyi dri ma yod med kyis gnas skabs gsum du
NK050(wi)001:1150: ma dag ma dag dag pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:1151: shin tu rnam dag go rim bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:1152: sems can byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK050(wi)001:1153: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes brjod do //
NK050(wi)001:1156: ji ltar so ga'i dus su chu //
NK050(wi)001:1157: dro'o zhes ni brjod par byed //
NK050(wi)001:1158: de nyid grang ba'i dus su ni //
NK050(wi)001:1159: grang ngo zhes ni brjod pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:1160: nyon mongs d+r+wa bas g.yogs pa la //
NK050(wi)001:1161: sems can zhes ni brjod pa ste //
NK050(wi)001:1162: de nyid nyon mongs bral gyur na //
NK050(wi)001:1163: sangs rgyas zhes ni brjod par byed //
NK050(wi)001:1165: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir nges don bka' 'khor phyi ma
NK050(wi)001:1166: 'di nyid gsungs pa'i rjes thob de ma thag par
NK050(wi)001:1167: 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'ang 'byung ma
NK050(wi)001:1168: rag pa'i phyir / ji ltar ma yi sngon du drod 'byung ba ltar /
NK050(wi)001:1169: chos dbyings 'od gsal bsam mi khyab pa'i gnas lugs ji lta ba bzhin bstan te /
NK050(wi)001:1172: bral 'bras tsam las chos nyid rang gi ngo bo
NK050(wi)001:1173: dbang btsan du byas na bskyed byed kyi rgyu 'bras
NK050(wi)001:1174: mtshan nyid pa min par bstan pas /
NK050(wi)001:1175: 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa dang yang lam gyi mtshams sbyor bla na med pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:1176: gong bshad bral gzhi sogs gsum po dang /
NK050(wi)001:1177: rdo rje theg pa'i lugs kyi rgyud gsum thabs shes
NK050(wi)001:1178: kyis khyad par du phye ba tsam las ngo bo
NK050(wi)001:1179: gzhi 'bras dbyer med chen por gnad gcig pas na
NK050(wi)001:1180: / sngon gyi gsar rnying gi mkhas grub dam pa
NK050(wi)001:1181: rnams kyis mdo sngags phyi nang sbyar te bshad pa
NK050(wi)001:1184: gdod nas dag pa'i rig pa ni //
NK050(wi)001:1185: ye nas chos skur gnas pa la //
NK050(wi)001:1186: dbul po'i khyim gyi sa 'og na //
NK050(wi)001:1187: gnas pa'i nor bu rin chen bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:1189: ngo sprod de ngo shes pa ni //
NK050(wi)001:1190: chos dbyings ye shes rtogs pa ste //
NK050(wi)001:1191: sangs rgyas zhes su grags pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1193: sa chen grags rgyal gyi lam bzang tshigs bcad mar /
NK050(wi)001:1194: rang sems gdod nas spros bral rgyu rgyud dang //
NK050(wi)001:1195: dbang gi ye shes lam gyi lta ba dang //
NK050(wi)001:1196: nyams myong sangs rgyas sa la khyad par med //
NK050(wi)001:1197: rtogs pa'i khyad par zla ba'i dpe yis bstan //
NK050(wi)001:1200: rang bzhin rgyu la bsam na lhun grub ste //
NK050(wi)001:1201: mtha' yas yon tan tshogs ni gnas gyur yin //
NK050(wi)001:1202: des na lhun grub gnas gyur mi 'gal ba //
NK050(wi)001:1205: lam 'bras gzhung rdo rje'i tshig rkang gi 'brel par //
NK050(wi)001:1206: kun gzhi zhes pa ni thabs kyis zin pa dang
NK050(wi)001:1207: ma zin pa'i bye brag gis 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i
NK050(wi)001:1208: gzhir gyur pa'o // rgyu ni 'bras bu skye rung gi nus pa'i mthu la bya /
NK050(wi)001:1209: rgyud ni sems can nas rdo rje 'dzin pa'i bar du sems nyid rigs pa rgyun mi 'chad pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1211: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad mtshan nyid kyi tshul du tshang /
NK050(wi)001:1212: mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam thams cad yon tan gyi tshul du tshang /
NK050(wi)001:1213: 'bras bu'i chos thams cad nus mthu'i tshul du tshang ngo //
NK050(wi)001:1214: 'di nyid la rtsa rgyud ces bya ste /
NK050(wi)001:1215: lus la rten 'brel bsgrigs pas rtogs par bya rgyu sems kun gzhi yin pas so //
NK050(wi)001:1216: zhes kun gzhi rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK050(wi)001:1218: phyag rgya chen po 'bras bu'i rgyud de rgyud gsum du rnam par bzhag ste gsungs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1219: rgyal dbang rang byung zhabs kyi zab mo nang don rang 'grel du /
NK050(wi)001:1220: dri med rgyal ba'i snying po dang //
NK050(wi)001:1221: ma dag ma dag dag pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:1222: shin tu rnam dag go rim bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:1223: sems can lam la gnas pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:1224: de bzhin gshegs rnams rim pa bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:1225: gsungs phyir de don rtogs par bya //
NK050(wi)001:1226: zhes bya ba smos te 'di mchog tu rtogs par
NK050(wi)001:1227: dka' ba'i rdo rje theg pa'i brjod bya ste bsam
NK050(wi)001:1228: gyis mi khyab pa'i gnas bzhis 'khyud pa'i sangs rgyas
NK050(wi)001:1229: kyi byang chub la brten pa yin no //
NK050(wi)001:1230: de la rdo rje ni 'gyur ba med pa sangs rgyas yin la /
NK050(wi)001:1231: de'i lam du 'gro ba ni theg pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:1232: rgyal ba'i sras rnams der phyin par byed pa'am /
NK050(wi)001:1233: yang na mi shigs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi snying po
NK050(wi)001:1234: ni 'khor 'das thams cad de las mi g.yo ba'i
NK050(wi)001:1235: gzhi yin pas rdo rje theg pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1236: gnas lugs 'di la dri ma thams cad kyis gos pa med pas dri ma med pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1237: de nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo yin pas sangs rgyas kyi snying po zhes bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:1238: 'di la gnas skabs gsum du 'gyur te ma dag
NK050(wi)001:1239: pa dang bcas pa sems can gyi gnas skabs dang
NK050(wi)001:1240: / ma dag pa dang dag pa gnyis ldan pa'i byang chub sems dpa' lam pa'i gnas skabs dang /
NK050(wi)001:1241: shin tu rnam par dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i gnas skabs te /
NK050(wi)001:1242: de ltar rnam pa gsum po 'di la ming gi
NK050(wi)001:1243: tha snyad kyi rnam grangs gzhi dang lam dang 'bras
NK050(wi)001:1247: gzhi dngos po'i gnas lugs dang /
NK050(wi)001:1249: 'bras bu skye ba'i rim pa zhes bya ba la
NK050(wi)001:1250: sogs pa sngon gyi mkhas grub rnams kyis gsungs so
NK050(wi)001:1251: // zhes sogs gnas bzhi dam pa'i yul du gyur
NK050(wi)001:1252: pa phal gyis bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i tshul nor
NK050(wi)001:1253: bu'i dpe dang bcas te rgyas par gsungs pa dang
NK050(wi)001:1254: // / kun mkhyen chos rjes nges don shing rta chen mor /
NK050(wi)001:1255: 'dir bka' tha ma la khams rang bzhin gyis dag pa yon tan ye ldan du yod la /
NK050(wi)001:1256: lam nyams su blang dus yon tan skye ba ltar snang ba khas len pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1257: sngags las rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor 'gro ba kun
NK050(wi)001:1258: la gnas par bstan pa gnyis khyad med pas gzhi
NK050(wi)001:1259: gcig la / lam yang thabs shes tshogs gnyis su gcig pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1260: 'bras bu'ang sku dang ye shes su gcig pas sngon
NK050(wi)001:1261: gyi slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas la sogs
NK050(wi)001:1262: pas phyi nang du bshad pa mdzad pa yin no
NK050(wi)001:1265: gzhi rgyud bde gshegs snying po'i khams //
NK050(wi)001:1266: thabs rgyud lam gyi yongs sbyong nas //
NK050(wi)001:1267: 'bras rgyud sku bzhir mtshams sbyar ba'i //
NK050(wi)001:1268: bla ma de la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK050(wi)001:1270: 'on kyang 'khor lo tha mar chos dbyings sam snying
NK050(wi)001:1271: po'i rang bzhin ji lta bar gtan la phabs nas
NK050(wi)001:1272: bstan kyang / de mngon du byed pa'i thabs thun
NK050(wi)001:1273: mong ba rgyu tshogs gnyis la goms stobs kyis dus
NK050(wi)001:1274: ring mo zhig nas mngon du byed par bstan gyi
NK050(wi)001:1275: da lta nas mngon du byed pa'i thabs thun min
NK050(wi)001:1276: rnams ma bstan pas thabs la rmongs pa'i cha yod
NK050(wi)001:1277: bstan kyang / de / +aar+ya de was bdag byin rlabs las /
NK050(wi)001:1278: bskal pa bye ba mtha' yas su //
NK050(wi)001:1279: thos pa'i pha rol son gyur kyang //
NK050(wi)001:1280: bdag byin brlab las phyir phyogs pas //
NK050(wi)001:1281: de yis de nyid mthong mi 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:1283: dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i rim pa gnyis te gsang sher gyi lam rang lus thabs ldan dang /
NK050(wi)001:1284: gzhan lus pho nya'i lam ste mtshan bcas kyi rdzogs rim yin la /
NK050(wi)001:1285: de'i rten du bskyed rim dgos shing /
NK050(wi)001:1286: de thams cad kyang smin byed dbang dang dam tshig
NK050(wi)001:1287: la ma brten par sgom du mi rung bas na
NK050(wi)001:1288: / don la smin byed kyi dbang dang /
NK050(wi)001:1289: grol byed kyi lam rim pa gnyis la ma brten par /
NK050(wi)001:1290: dbang bzhi pa'i ye shes lhan cig skyes pa nyid rtogs mi nus par gsungs so //
NK050(wi)001:1291: rgyu mtshan des byang sems blo chen brtson ldan rnams
NK050(wi)001:1292: kyang grangs med gsum gyi dus la ltos dgos shing
NK050(wi)001:1293: / de yang sangs rgyas kho na'i spyod yul las
NK050(wi)001:1294: sa bcu'i byang sems chen po rnams kyis kyang khams
NK050(wi)001:1295: kyi yon tan ye ldan yin par gzigs kyi mtha'
NK050(wi)001:1296: dag mngon gyur du ni gzigs pa min par gsungs
NK050(wi)001:1298: sprin mthong mkha' la nyi bzhin phyogs gcig blo gros can /
NK050(wi)001:1299: blo mig dag pa'i 'phags rnams kyis kyang thams cad mthong ma lags //
NK050(wi)001:1300: bcom ldan 'das khyod chos sku rnam dag blo gros mtha' yas pa //
NK050(wi)001:1301: shes bya mtha' med mkha' dbyings khyab pa de dag gis kun mthong //
NK050(wi)001:1303: spang bya'i dri ma las nyon rnam smin gyi phra
NK050(wi)001:1304: ba gang zad phan chad spang bya gtan med pa
NK050(wi)001:1305: ni / ma rig bag chags kyi sa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1306: zag pa med pa'i las dang /
NK050(wi)001:1307: yid kyi rang bzhin gyi phung po dang /
NK050(wi)001:1308: bsam mi khyab 'gyur gyi 'chi 'pho ba ste de bzhi po yin la /
NK050(wi)001:1309: de thams cad spangs pa ni sangs rgyas kyi sa
NK050(wi)001:1310: kho na yin te nyan rang sogs la mi srid
NK050(wi)001:1311: do // de bzhi po spangs na mthar thug gi
NK050(wi)001:1312: yon tan stobs sogs sangs rgyas kyi tsho lta bu
NK050(wi)001:1313: mngon du gyur pa ni dbyings kyi yon tan nyid
NK050(wi)001:1314: mngon du gyur pa yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:1315: 'di sangs rgyas kyi rigs kho na yin gyi nyan rang sogs kyi ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:1316: sangs rgyas kyi sa'i yon tan dang rnam dbyer med pa'i phyir ro //
NK050(wi)001:1317: gal te nyan rang sogs kyis kyang 'di lta bu'i
NK050(wi)001:1318: khams yod par thos shing rtogs na ni de dag
NK050(wi)001:1319: kyang rim gyis sangs rgyas su 'gyur te mdo sde
NK050(wi)001:1320: pad dkar sogs nas gsungs pa bzhin mthar thug theg
NK050(wi)001:1321: gcig tu sgrub pa'i gnad 'di la thug pa'i phyir
NK050(wi)001:1322: ro // mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sar rig par
NK050(wi)001:1323: ye shes kyi stobs las sgrib gnyis bag chags bcas
NK050(wi)001:1324: zad pa'i rjes su ye shes nyid 'gag pa ma
NK050(wi)001:1325: ro // yin te / snang bas mun pa log kyang snang ba mi ldog pa bzhin du /
NK050(wi)001:1326: sgrib gnyis dang bral ba'i ye shes nam mkha' dang
NK050(wi)001:1327: mnyam pa'i gnas gyur mthar thug ste nam yang zad
NK050(wi)001:1328: mi shes so // 'o na rong zom sogs kyis ye shes med par ma gsungs sam snyam na /
NK050(wi)001:1329: de ni gzhan byung gi ye shes slob lam du
NK050(wi)001:1330: zag med gsar thob 'dus byas kyi cha rnams de'i
NK050(wi)001:1331: tshe 'gag zin pa'am yul yul can tha dad du
NK050(wi)001:1332: 'dzin pa'i spros pa nye bar zhi ba'i cha tsam
NK050(wi)001:1333: la dgongs kyi rang byung gi ye shes ni me
NK050(wi)001:1336: de bas na sangs rgyas rang gi ngo bo ni
NK050(wi)001:1337: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa nyid yin par
NK050(wi)001:1338: lung dang rig pa gnyis kas mngon no //
NK050(wi)001:1339: de lta na sems can dang sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin mnyam ste /
NK050(wi)001:1340: chos thams cad ni ngo bo nyid kyis stong pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1341: chos thams cad ni rang bzhin gyis mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1342: chos thams cad ni rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'o //
NK050(wi)001:1343: chos thams cad ni ye nas mngon par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1344: gang gis don 'di lta bu rtogs te /
NK050(wi)001:1345: bdag dang sangs rgyas dbyer med pa'i blo dang ldan
NK050(wi)001:1346: zhing phung po lnga sgyu ma tsam du snang ba'ang
NK050(wi)001:1347: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid yin pa'i blo dang ldan
NK050(wi)001:1348: na / lam gyi mchog yin te /
NK050(wi)001:1349: gang gis khyad par yod par mthong ba ni lam gyi mchog ma yin no //
NK050(wi)001:1351: de yang 'di ltar mngon du sangs rgyas pa de mtshan nyid ji ltar sangs rgyas zhe na /
NK050(wi)001:1352: thams cad snying po byang chub kyi rang bzhin gzhan
NK050(wi)001:1353: la ltos pa med par rang byung gi ye shes
NK050(wi)001:1355: ye shes de nyid kyang mtshan ma thams cad las 'das pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:1356: bsnyad pa thams cad dang bral ba'i mtshan nyid do //
NK050(wi)001:1358: de'i rang bzhin de yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK050(wi)001:1362: ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1363: de la ma byas pa ni sems can 'khrul pas ji ltar bslad kyang /
NK050(wi)001:1364: sems kyi rang bzhin 'gyur ba med pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1366: rgyal ba rnams kyi thabs kyis ji ltar bcos kyang /
NK050(wi)001:1367: byang chub sems kyi yon tan bog dbyung du med pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1368: lhun gyis grub pa ni de lta bas na bgrod cing sbyang ba las 'das pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1369: 'dis rdzogs pa chen po'i don mtha' dag bsdus so //
NK050(wi)001:1371: man ngag rtsa ba gsum ni /
NK050(wi)001:1372: lung la ma brten pa'i man ngag /
NK050(wi)001:1373: rgyu las ma byung ba'i 'bras bu /
NK050(wi)001:1374: sems las ma byung ba'i chos so //
NK050(wi)001:1375: de la byang chub kyi sems ni chos thams cad kyi snying po yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:1376: blo la bcang ba'i man ngag dam pa yin yang /
NK050(wi)001:1377: lung gi sgra la brten pa'ang ma yin no //
NK050(wi)001:1378: byang chub kyi sems ni rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba yin yang /
NK050(wi)001:1379: sems las byung ba'i chos shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin dang snying rjes bsdus pa'ang ma yin no //
NK050(wi)001:1380: byang chub kyi sems ni mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa yin yang /
NK050(wi)001:1381: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs kyi rgyu las bsgrub pa'ang ma yin no //
NK050(wi)001:1383: byang chub kyi sems dang rang byung gi ye shes don gcig /
NK050(wi)001:1385: sems ye shes su bskyed pa'i skabs lnga ka'ang gnas
NK050(wi)001:1386: gyur pa med pa'i bral 'bras rang byung gi ye
NK050(wi)001:1387: shes 'ba' zhig tu gsungs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1388: dam tshig mdo rgyas las kyang /
NK050(wi)001:1389: ye shes kyi dam tshig skabs su //
NK050(wi)001:1390: sa chu me rlung snod bcud bcas //
NK050(wi)001:1391: kun kyang rang bzhin chos nyid don //
NK050(wi)001:1392: chos nyid don las gzhan med pas //
NK050(wi)001:1393: rang byung ye shes gsal ba'o //
NK050(wi)001:1395: sgrib pa gdod nas dag pas rang byung gi ye shes su 'od gsal ba ste /
NK050(wi)001:1396: 'di lta bu ni nges don gyi mdo sde las kyang gsungs te /
NK050(wi)001:1397: dri ma med par grags pa'i mdo las /
NK050(wi)001:1400: snying po med pa yin yang /
NK050(wi)001:1401: bsod nams gsog ma yin pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1402: ye shes gsob ma yin pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1403: rang byung gi ye shes su dbang bskur ba'i snying po med pa ma yin par gsungs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1404: gzhan yang sdong po bkod pa sogs mdo du ma nas /
NK050(wi)001:1405: nam mkha' bzhin du rang byung gi ye shes 'pho 'gyur med pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1406: so so'i skye bo'i shes pa'ang rang bzhin gyis rnam par byang ba can dang /
NK050(wi)001:1407: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po can dang /
NK050(wi)001:1408: zag pa med pa'i sems can no //
NK050(wi)001:1409: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs mod kyi /
NK050(wi)001:1410: de dag tu ni mtshan ma'i chos kyang shas cher 'dod la /
NK050(wi)001:1411: 'dir sangs rgyas ma rgyas pa'i chos rdul tsam yang mi 'dod do //
NK050(wi)001:1412: zhes chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang
NK050(wi)001:1413: bzhin rang byung gi ye shes nyag gcig tu bstan
NK050(wi)001:1414: pas shes so // des na mdo las /
NK050(wi)001:1415: de bzhin gshegs pa chos kyi sku //
NK050(wi)001:1416: ye shes nam mkha' lta bu ste //
NK050(wi)001:1417: de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes sku //
NK050(wi)001:1418: gzung du med cing reg tu med //
NK050(wi)001:1420: ji ltar nam mkha' mu med cing //
NK050(wi)001:1421: tshad yod ma yin mtha' yas ltar //
NK050(wi)001:1422: de bzhin ye shes chen po yi //
NK050(wi)001:1423: mtha' ni dmigs par mi 'gyur ro //
NK050(wi)001:1426: sems 'gag pa ste sku yis mngon sum mdzad //
NK050(wi)001:1427: zhes gsungs te de'i tshe sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK050(wi)001:1428: sgrib bral mngon 'gyur mthar thug par grub pa'i phyir
NK050(wi)001:1429: ro // des na bde gshegs snying po'i rang bzhin
NK050(wi)001:1430: ni tshogs sogs slob lam du dad pas don spyi
NK050(wi)001:1431: phyogs re tsam 'jal ba las thams cad rtogs nus
NK050(wi)001:1433: snying po'i mdor gang so so skye bo dang /
NK050(wi)001:1436: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis kyang ji lta ba
NK050(wi)001:1437: bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi snying po mthong ba ma
NK050(wi)001:1438: yin no // zhes sogs dmus long gis mar gyi
NK050(wi)001:1439: kha dog dris pa dang glang po che'i mtshan nyid
NK050(wi)001:1440: gzhal ba sogs kyi dpes bstan pas mtshon te /
NK050(wi)001:1441: mdor na rgyud bla ma las /
NK050(wi)001:1442: rang byung rnams kyi don dam ni //
NK050(wi)001:1443: dad pa nyid kyis rtogs bya yis //
NK050(wi)001:1445: mig med pas ni mthong ba med //
NK050(wi)001:1447: de lta na'ang 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg par ni /
NK050(wi)001:1449: grol byed kyi lam bdag byin rlabs bsgom pa sogs
NK050(wi)001:1450: bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i thabs mkhas kyi myur lam la
NK050(wi)001:1451: brten nas / da lta so skye'i sa nas kyang
NK050(wi)001:1452: yid ches skye zhing mngon du byar yod pa ni
NK050(wi)001:1453: sngags kyi khyad chos thun min te /
NK050(wi)001:1455: gzhan gyis brjod min lhan cig skyes //
NK050(wi)001:1456: gang du yang ni mi snyed de //
NK050(wi)001:1457: bla mas dus thabs bstan pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:1458: rang gi bsod nams las shes bya //
NK050(wi)001:1460: rgyu mtshan des thabs kyi theg pa dang 'bras bu'i theg par grub pa yin te /
NK050(wi)001:1462: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK050(wi)001:1463: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:1464: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas te //
NK050(wi)001:1465: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK050(wi)001:1467: de ltar thabs kyis khyad par du 'phags pa bzhin du lta bas kyang 'phags te /
NK050(wi)001:1468: kha cig gis yul chos dbyings spros bral tsam gyi
NK050(wi)001:1469: cha la dgongs nas khyad par med du brjod kyang
NK050(wi)001:1470: / lta ba ni de gtan la 'bebs byed yul can gyi ngos nas 'jog dgos pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:1471: don dam bde ba chen po dang /
NK050(wi)001:1472: kun rdzob sku dang ye shes su blta ba sogs kyis khyad par du 'phags te /
