NK050(wi)001:1474: sngags dang mtshan nyid kyi grub mtha' mthun pa ni /
NK050(wi)001:1476: kun rdzob sgyu mar 'dod pa spyi mthun /
NK050(wi)001:1477: sgyu ma tsam nyid sems snang yin pa rnal 'byor spyod pa dang mthun /
NK050(wi)001:1478: sems kyi tshul ji ltar 'dod pa byang sems gcig pur smra ba dang mthun /
NK050(wi)001:1479: spyod pas gzhan don la nyams su len pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1480: 'bras bu bla med ye shes kyang mthun /
NK050(wi)001:1481: sngags su sangs rgyas kyi sa gsum dang bdud rtsi 'od sogs gsungs pa yang /
NK050(wi)001:1482: mtshan nyid la chos sku mdzad pa bcas dang /
NK050(wi)001:1483: sangs rgyas kyi chos lnga zhes gsungs pa mtshungs par shes par bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:1484: cung zad mi mthun pa ni /
NK050(wi)001:1486: kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'dod pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1487: sems kyi rang bzhin rang byung ye shes su 'dod pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1488: chos thams cad sangs rgyas par 'dod par mi mthun no //
NK050(wi)001:1490: so so'i skye bo'i shes pa zag pa med pa'i sems dang ldan pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1491: rang byung ye shes mi 'jig pa yod par gsungs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1492: sh+aakya thub pa'i zhing dag par gsungs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1493: rtag tu skye med chos ni de bzhin nyid /
NK050(wi)001:1494: sogs kyi mdo sde las kyang bden gnyis dbyer med dang /
NK050(wi)001:1496: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis sangs rgyas su gsungs pas khyad par mi rigs snyam na /
NK050(wi)001:1497: de ltar gsungs pa bden te /
NK050(wi)001:1498: khyad par 'di dag nyan thos dang thun mong du
NK050(wi)001:1499: grags pa'i gzhung las bye brag phye ste gsungs pa
NK050(wi)001:1500: yin la / 'di dang sngags cung zad sgo mthun
NK050(wi)001:1501: pa ni 'dod pa nyid de theg pa'i bye brag
NK050(wi)001:1502: thams cad tha dad du med de byang sems kyi
NK050(wi)001:1503: spyod pa rlab po che dang /
NK050(wi)001:1504: kun gzhi'i rnam shes lta bu theg chen du gsungs
NK050(wi)001:1505: pa'i khyad chos dag kyang nyan thos lung las sa
NK050(wi)001:1506: bon tsam grags pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:1508: gsang sngags kyi gzhung la grags pa'i lta ba ni /
NK050(wi)001:1509: don dam par skye 'gags med par 'dod pa dbu ma dang mthun la /
NK050(wi)001:1510: kun rdzob tu phung khams skye mched sgyu ma tsam du lta ba'ang mthun no //
NK050(wi)001:1512: sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid de dag kyang /
NK050(wi)001:1513: yongs su dag pa'i lha'i mtshan nyid du lta ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:1514: bden pa gnyis kyang dbyer med par lta bas khyad par du byas pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1515: zhes gsungs pas mtshon zhib par lta ba'i brjed byang du gsal bar bstan pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:1516: sngags thun min gyi lta ba mdo tsam ni 'og tu 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK050(wi)001:1517: de lta bu'i bla na med pa'am theg pa chen po sangs rgyas kyi rigs de la dbye na /
NK050(wi)001:1519: gter dang 'bras bu'i shing bzhin du //
NK050(wi)001:1520: rigs de rnam gnyis shes bya ste //
NK050(wi)001:1521: thog med rang bzhin gnas pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:1522: yang dag blang ba mchog yin no //
NK050(wi)001:1524: rang bzhin gnas pa'i rigs dang /
NK050(wi)001:1529: de la sems kyi chos nyid rang bzhin gyis 'od
NK050(wi)001:1530: gsal ba rang bzhin gyis ngo bo nyid med pa
NK050(wi)001:1531: ni / rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i sems ji ltar
NK050(wi)001:1532: snang ba mtshan dang dpe byad 'bar ba'i yon tan
NK050(wi)001:1533: gyis bgos pa dang tha dad par ma yin te
NK050(wi)001:1534: ni / / 'on kyang snang ba dang stong pa'i rang bzhin gyis rnam par phye'o //
NK050(wi)001:1537: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i rigs dbyings zag
NK050(wi)001:1538: med ngo bo nyid sku'i bral rgyu'am bral gzhi lhun
NK050(wi)001:1539: gyis grub pas rin po che'i sku lta bu dang
NK050(wi)001:1540: / chos can rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i rigs longs
NK050(wi)001:1541: spyod rdzogs sku'i bral rgyu 'khor los bsgyur ba lta
NK050(wi)001:1542: / bu dang / de'i gzugs brnyan snang ba sprul
NK050(wi)001:1543: sku'i bral rgyu gser gyi gzugs brnyan lta bu ste
NK050(wi)001:1544: / bu dang / / mthar phyin 'bras bu'i sku
NK050(wi)001:1545: gsum gyi 'char gzhir gyur pa'i cha nas ldog pas
NK050(wi)001:1547: don la de gsum ngo bo dbyer med pa'i chos
NK050(wi)001:1548: nyid snang stong zung 'jug spros bral mnyam pa chen
NK050(wi)001:1549: po'i ye shes chos kyi sku rang byung 'dus ma
NK050(wi)001:1551: snang stong tha dad du dbye gzhi zad pa'i dbyer med chen po yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:1552: gong bshad kyi dpe rnams kyis kyang phyogs re tsam
NK050(wi)001:1553: las rdzogs par mtshon mi nus pas de bzhin gshegs
NK050(wi)001:1554: pa nyid dang dpe mtshungs par /
NK050(wi)001:1557: 'di la dpe ni ma dmigs pas //
NK050(wi)001:1558: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid dang khams //
NK050(wi)001:1559: 'dra ba nyid du bstan pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:1561: 'di nyid sgrib bral mngon du gyur dus theg chen
NK050(wi)001:1562: gyi 'gog bden mthar thug pa dag pa gnyis ldan
NK050(wi)001:1563: ngo bo nyid sku yin la /
NK050(wi)001:1564: sgrub pa'i rigs ni dbyings ye'am chos nyid dang chos
NK050(wi)001:1565: can rang bzhin gyi gnas pa'i rigs de gnyis pos
NK050(wi)001:1566: sad pa la brten nas de'i steng gi dri ma
NK050(wi)001:1567: glo bur ba rnams sel byed sems bskyed pa sogs
NK050(wi)001:1568: gnas skabs slob lam gyis bsdus pa'i thabs shes tshogs
NK050(wi)001:1569: gnyis zung 'brel la slob pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:1572: byang chub kyi rigs zhes bya ba 'di ni chos kyi dbyings lhur len pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:1573: nam mkha' ltar yangs pa rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal
NK050(wi)001:1574: ba mthong nas bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs
NK050(wi)001:1575: chen po la rjes su slob pa dag go //
NK050(wi)001:1577: des na snga ma ni bral gzhi dang /
NK050(wi)001:1578: phyi ma ni de'i steng gi dri ma sel byed kyi lam mo //
NK050(wi)001:1579: lam bden bral rgyus bsdus pa kun gzhi la brten
NK050(wi)001:1580: yang des thob pa'i cha bral 'bras rigs sam snying
NK050(wi)001:1581: po la brten pas 'gyur ba med pa'i thar pa
NK050(wi)001:1582: dam pa'i rgyu byed par gsungs so //
NK050(wi)001:1583: de lta bu'i rang bzhin gnas rigs de yod par gang gis shes na /
NK050(wi)001:1584: spyir du ba las me bzhin rigs sad pa'i rtags kyis rigs nyid yod par rjes su dpog ste /
NK050(wi)001:1585: rang bzhin chos sku'i rigs sad pa'i rtags ni /
NK050(wi)001:1587: so so skye bo'i dus na'ang stong pa nyid thos nas //
NK050(wi)001:1588: nang du rab tu dga' ba yang dang yang du 'byung //
NK050(wi)001:1589: rab tu dga' ba las byung mchi mas mig brlan zhing //
NK050(wi)001:1590: lus kyi ba spu ldang bar 'gyur ba gang yin pa //
NK050(wi)001:1591: de la rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob blo'i sa bon yod //
NK050(wi)001:1592: de nyid nye bar bstan pa'i snod ni de yin te //
NK050(wi)001:1593: de la dam pa'i don gyi bden pa bstan par bya //
NK050(wi)001:1595: gzugs sku chos can gyi rigs sad pa'i rtags ni /
NK050(wi)001:1597: sbyor ba'i sngon du snying rje dang //
NK050(wi)001:1598: mos pa dang ni bzod pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:1599: dge la yang dag spyod pa ni //
NK050(wi)001:1600: rigs kyi rtags su nges par bshad //
NK050(wi)001:1602: rigs de sad pa'i phan yon yang //
NK050(wi)001:1604: ring mo zhig nas ngan song du //
NK050(wi)001:1605: song yang myur du thar bar 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:1606: de na'ang sdug bsngal chung ngu myong //
NK050(wi)001:1607: skyo byas sems can smin par byed //
NK050(wi)001:1609: rigs de lan gcig sad phan chad ngan song du mi skye ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:1610: gal te song yang dar gyi pho longs brdab pa'i yun tsam gyis thar zhing /
NK050(wi)001:1611: der yang sdug bsngal chung ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:1612: skyo shas drag pos sems can yang smin par byed de /
NK050(wi)001:1613: ston pa nyid dmyal bar shing rta 'dren pa'i gyad du gyur pa'i tshe /
NK050(wi)001:1614: snying rje chen po'i rigs sad pa'i rkyen gyis mod
NK050(wi)001:1615: la thar te sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lhar skyes
NK050(wi)001:1616: shing / de nas 'phos te 'dzam gling du rdza mkhan gyi bu khye'u snang byed du gyur te /
NK050(wi)001:1617: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa'i spyan sngar byang chub tu thugs bskyed par gsungs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1618: gzhan yang 'dza' bo'i bu mo sogs kyi skyes rabs gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:1619: de lta bu'i rigs 'di 'gro la med na gang
NK050(wi)001:1620: dag la sdug bsngal byung bas de dag skyo bar
NK050(wi)001:1622: 'ga' zhig 'khor 'das la blang dor byed pa'i blo yang mi 'byung bar rigs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1623: thar pa 'dod pa'ang sems la 'char mi srid pa las /
NK050(wi)001:1624: sus kyang ma bstan par skye bo 'ga' la /
NK050(wi)001:1625: gzhan sdug bsngal 'byung ba la snying rje skye ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:1626: sdug bsngal myong bas yid 'byung ba sogs kyang thog
NK050(wi)001:1627: med nas chos khams dge ba'i mthur shes par bya
NK050(wi)001:1629: gal te sangs rgyas khams med na //
NK050(wi)001:1630: sdug bsngal skyo bar mi 'gyur zhing //
NK050(wi)001:1632: don gnyer smon pa'ang med par 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:1633: srid dang mya ngan 'das la de'i //
NK050(wi)001:1634: sdug bde'i skyon yon mthong ba 'di //
NK050(wi)001:1635: rigs yod las yin gang phyir 'di //
NK050(wi)001:1636: rigs med dag la med phyir ro //
NK050(wi)001:1638: khyad par rgyud sde rnams su sbas don /
NK050(wi)001:1639: rtsa ba spros bral gyi thig le sems nyid lhan
NK050(wi)001:1640: cig skyes pa'i ye shes stong gsal 'gags med sku
NK050(wi)001:1641: gsum gyi rang bzhin du gnas pa'i /
NK050(wi)001:1642: chos sku'i rtags chos thams cad rang bzhin stong par snang ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:1643: longs sku'i rtags mig yul du dbyings rig gi rtags bcu 'char ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:1644: sprul sku'i rtags tshogs drug gi yul snang gi nus
NK050(wi)001:1645: pa so so rang 'byin pa gsum bslu ba med
NK050(wi)001:1646: pa'i rtags su rang byung zhabs kyis gsungs pa dang
NK050(wi)001:1648: nga yi rang bzhin shes 'dod pas //
NK050(wi)001:1649: dpe ni nam mkha' lta bur ltos //
NK050(wi)001:1650: don ni sems nyid skye ba med //
NK050(wi)001:1651: rtags ni rig pa byang chub sems //
NK050(wi)001:1652: zhes dpe nam mkha' dag pa /
NK050(wi)001:1654: rtags dran rig sna tshogs su gsal ba sogs //
NK050(wi)001:1655: dpe don rtags gsum gyis mtshon nas chos nyid yid
NK050(wi)001:1656: dpyod du ma lus par mngon sum du ngo sprad
NK050(wi)001:1657: nas rtsol med kyi lam la da lta nas goms
NK050(wi)001:1659: thun min man ngag rdzogs pa chen po'i khyad chos so //
NK050(wi)001:1660: gang du rigs med pa'am rigs chad gsungs pa ni
NK050(wi)001:1661: rigs mdangs pa rnams la dman pa la dgag sgra
NK050(wi)001:1663: rang bzhin gnas rigs med pa'i 'gro ba ni 'ga' yang med de /
NK050(wi)001:1664: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'i mdor /
NK050(wi)001:1666: 'di ni chos thams cad kyi chos nyid de bzhin gshegs pa rnams byung yang rung /
NK050(wi)001:1668: sems can 'di dag ni rtag tu de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po can no //
NK050(wi)001:1671: bde gshegs snying pos 'gro ba yongs la khyab //
NK050(wi)001:1673: in+d+ra b+hu tis ye shes su grub pa las /
NK050(wi)001:1674: sems can kun gyi yid khyab par //
NK050(wi)001:1675: rdo rje sems dpa' rtag par bzhugs //
NK050(wi)001:1676: de ltar shes pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK050(wi)001:1677: dbang po gang la yang brnyas mi bya //
NK050(wi)001:1680: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po kun tu
NK050(wi)001:1681: bzang po ni thams cad kyi rang bzhin yin pa'i
NK050(wi)001:1682: phyir / sems can thams cad ni de bzhin yin pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:1683: sems can thams cad ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po can no //
NK050(wi)001:1686: sangs rgyas rnams ni byon gyur tam /
NK050(wi)001:1687: ma byon na yang rnam kun tu //
NK050(wi)001:1688: rgyun chad med pa'i chos nyid ni //
NK050(wi)001:1692: khams gsum sems can thams cad kyang //
NK050(wi)001:1693: kun gzhi sangs rgyas nga dang mnyam //
NK050(wi)001:1695: 'di'i kun gzhi ni sbyor ba don gyi kun gazhi'am
NK050(wi)001:1696: kun gzhi'i ye shes bde gshegs snying po nyid yin
NK050(wi)001:1698: sa rnams sna tshogs kun gzhi ste //
NK050(wi)001:1699: bde gshegs snying po dge ba'ang de //
NK050(wi)001:1700: snying po de la kun gzhi'i sgras //
NK050(wi)001:1701: de bzhin gshegs rnams ston par mdzad //
NK050(wi)001:1703: ji ltar zla ba skye 'bri ba //
NK050(wi)001:1704: mi shes 'gro ba rnam rtog kyang //
NK050(wi)001:1705: zla ba skye 'bri med pa bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:1706: gling dang gling du rab tu snang //
NK050(wi)001:1707: de bzhin kun gzhi'i rnam shes la //
NK050(wi)001:1708: byis pa mi shes 'gro rnams kyis //
NK050(wi)001:1709: rtag tu skye 'brir rnam rtog ste //
NK050(wi)001:1710: de ni zag med sangs rgyas so //
NK050(wi)001:1712: zag med rang lugs rang thob na //
NK050(wi)001:1713: de dag brtan cing rtag par 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:1715: des na mthar gyis rnam grol gyi 'bras bu mi thob pa ni ma yin no //
NK050(wi)001:1716: des na rgyu rigs de gnyis sad pa la brten
NK050(wi)001:1717: nas theg pa chen po'i byang chub tu sems bskyed
NK050(wi)001:1718: nas / gtso bor mnyam bzhag tu rnam par mi
NK050(wi)001:1719: rtog pa'i ye shes la goms pas chos sku la
NK050(wi)001:1720: sgrib pa'i dri ma sel zhing /
NK050(wi)001:1721: rjes thob tu snying rje sgyu ma lta bu dang 'grogs te /
NK050(wi)001:1722: thabs la mkhas pas tshogs gnyis la spyod pas gzugs sku gnyis la sgrib pa'i dri ma bsal nas /
NK050(wi)001:1723: mthar thug bral 'bras zag med kyi yon tan bsam
NK050(wi)001:1724: mi khyab pas 'khyud pa'i dbyings kyi ngo bo nyid
NK050(wi)001:1725: sku'am gzhan snang gzugs sku'i 'char gzhi nam mkha'i zla
NK050(wi)001:1726: ba lta bu sangs rgyas rang snang gi sku gsum
NK050(wi)001:1727: po gzhan nas btsal ba med par ye shes rang
NK050(wi)001:1728: la snang bar byed pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:1730: rang bzhin 'od gsal zhes brjod gang yin nyid dang mkha' bzhin glo bur gyi //
NK050(wi)001:1731: nyon mongs shes bya'i sprin tshogs stug pos bsgribs pa las ni bral gyur pa //
NK050(wi)001:1732: dri med sangs rgyas yon tan kun ldan rtag brtan g.yung drung sangs rgyas nyid //
NK050(wi)001:1733: de ni chos la mi rtog rnam 'byed ye shes dag la brten nas 'thob //
NK050(wi)001:1735: thog ma dbus mtha' med cing rnam dbyer med //
NK050(wi)001:1736: gnyis med gsum bral dri med rnam rtog med //
NK050(wi)001:1737: chos dbyings rang bzhin gang yin de rtogs pa //
NK050(wi)001:1738: mnyam par bzhag pa'i rnal 'byor pa yis mthong //
NK050(wi)001:1739: gzhal med gang+ga'i bye ma las 'das pa //
NK050(wi)001:1740: dpag med mnyam med yon tan rnams dang ldan //
NK050(wi)001:1741: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dri med dbyings de ni //
NK050(wi)001:1742: bag chags bcas pa'i nyes kun gtan spangs pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1745: gcig dang du mar bral ba yi //
NK050(wi)001:1746: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK050(wi)001:1747: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs te //
NK050(wi)001:1748: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK050(wi)001:1750: de las shar ba'i gzugs sku gnyis po ni rgyu gdul bya'i snod dag pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1751: rkyen sngon gyi thugs bskyed dang tshogs gnyis la goms
NK050(wi)001:1752: pa'i lhan cig byed rgyus rang byung zag med kyi
NK050(wi)001:1753: ye shes nyid / dpe chu zla'i tshul du gdul
NK050(wi)001:1754: bya gzhan snang du ston pa'i cha nas smin 'bras
NK050(wi)001:1757: sna tshogs dam chos 'od zer snang ba'i skus //
NK050(wi)001:1758: 'gro ba'i rnam grol don sgrub la brtson pa //
NK050(wi)001:1759: mdzad pa yid bzhin nor bu rgyal bzhin te //
NK050(wi)001:1760: sna tshogs dngos kyang de yi rang bzhin min //
NK050(wi)001:1761: 'jig rten zhi ba'i lam du 'jug pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:1762: rab tu smin dang lung ston rgya ma gzugs //
NK050(wi)001:1763: gang yin de yang 'dir ni rtag gnas te //
NK050(wi)001:1764: nam mkha'i khams su gzugs kyi khams bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:1767: log par rtog brtag rnam dag cing //
NK050(wi)001:1768: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK050(wi)001:1769: thugs rje chen pos 'brel pa las //
NK050(wi)001:1770: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK050(wi)001:1773: dri ma med pa'i chos sku la //
NK050(wi)001:1774: ye shes rgya mtsho gnas gyur pas //
NK050(wi)001:1775: sna tshogs nor bu ji bzhin du //
NK050(wi)001:1776: de las sems can don 'byung ngo //
NK050(wi)001:1777: zhes gsungs mdor na shing rta chen mor /
NK050(wi)001:1778: skabs 'dir sangs rgyas kho na'i spyod yul las gdul
NK050(wi)001:1779: bya la mi snang ba dbyings kyi sku gsum chos
NK050(wi)001:1780: sku nyag gcig tu ro gcig pa nang dbyings phra
NK050(wi)001:1781: ba'i ye shes su yod pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1782: de'i byin rlabs dang gdul bya'i smon lam las phyir
NK050(wi)001:1783: gsal gzhan snang du shar ba ye shes phrin las
NK050(wi)001:1784: dag pa'i gzugs sku gnyis snang ba ni nam mkha'i
NK050(wi)001:1785: zla ba dang chu zla ltar shes par bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:1788: rigs gnyis la sangs rgyas sku gsum ye ldan du yod pas /
NK050(wi)001:1789: sangs rgyas kyi sa'i rgyas 'gyur snang cha longs sku dang /
NK050(wi)001:1790: de'i stong cha chos sku rang bzhin gnas rigs gnyis dbyer med pa'i byin rlabs las /
NK050(wi)001:1791: sprul sku gdul bya gzhan snang du ston pa 'khor
NK050(wi)001:1792: bsgyur gyi gzugs brnyan gser rir shar ba'i dpes gsungs
NK050(wi)001:1793: pa bzhin no // de ltar ma shes pa rang
NK050(wi)001:1794: bzhin gnas rigs med dgag stong rkyang 'dus ma byas
NK050(wi)001:1795: pa bzhin no // dang / rgyas 'gyur lam gyi gsar skye 'dus byas kho nar zhen pas ni /
NK050(wi)001:1796: mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i skabs su slob lam gyi
NK050(wi)001:1797: rtogs pa rgyun chad pas nyan thos kyi 'gog pa
NK050(wi)001:1798: mar me shi ba'i dpe ltar sku dang ye shes
NK050(wi)001:1799: sogs gang yang bzhag tu med pa'i lugs 'dzin pa
NK050(wi)001:1801: de lta na theg chen 'gog bden gyi dri tsam yang mi bro ste /
NK050(wi)001:1802: gzhi spros pa'i mthar lhung ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:1803: lam theg chen gyi tshogs gnyis la dgos pa med pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1804: 'bras bu theg gsum gyi myang 'das la khyad par med pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1805: mthar thug 'bras chad kyi g.yang las brgal mi nus
NK050(wi)001:1806: pas don dam pa'i skyabs kyang rnyed par mi 'gyur
NK050(wi)001:1807: bas na / tshul de la dgongs te kun mkhyen chos rjes yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod du /
NK050(wi)001:1808: tshul 'di mi shes stong pa phyang chad pa /
NK050(wi)001:1809: tshig tu yod med mtha' bral zhes smra yang //
NK050(wi)001:1810: bral gzhi mi shes srid rtse'i lta ba can //
NK050(wi)001:1811: bstan pa 'di las phyi rol gyur pas na //
NK050(wi)001:1812: nam mkha'i yid can thal bas byug na rung //
NK050(wi)001:1813: zhes log par lta ba phur bu pa'i khongs su bsdu bar mdzad pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1815: mda' bsnun na re nam mkha'i yid can la //
NK050(wi)001:1816: thar pa nam yang yod pa ma yin no //
NK050(wi)001:1818: gal te slob lam du rgyu tshogs gnyis kyis sngar med gsar du bskyed do snyam na /
NK050(wi)001:1819: sangs rgyas chos sku'am ngo bo nyid sku dang longs
NK050(wi)001:1820: sku 'dus byas dang mi rtag par 'gyur bas de
NK050(wi)001:1821: lta na / rgyud nyi tshe bas bsdus pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1822: 'gyur bcas kyi zug rngu ma spangs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1823: mkha' khyab ye shes rdo rje'i sku can ma yin pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1824: rdo rje'i sku la mi rtag par bltas pa'i nyes
NK050(wi)001:1825: pa tshad med par gsungs pas mtshon skyon mtha' yas
NK050(wi)001:1826: pa'i phyir theg pa chen po'i don las gzhan du
NK050(wi)001:1827: gyur pa'o // de'i phyir chos kyi dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK050(wi)001:1828: gang gi tshe dag pa gnyis ldan gyi byang chub brnyes pa de'i tshe /
NK050(wi)001:1831: sprul pa'i sku'i ye shes dang snang ba thams cad kyang /
NK050(wi)001:1832: sangs rgyas nyid kyi rig pa klong du phebs pa'i
NK050(wi)001:1833: rang snang tsam las gzhan du grub pa med de
NK050(wi)001:1834: / sku dang ye shes kyi snang ba de dag
NK050(wi)001:1835: rang la yod pa de'i tshe mngon du gyur pa
NK050(wi)001:1836: las gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK050(wi)001:1837: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs las byung ba ma yin nam zhe na /
NK050(wi)001:1839: tshogs gnyis ni ye nas snang ba dang stong pa'i
NK050(wi)001:1840: yon tan du rdzogs zin pa la lhun grub ces
NK050(wi)001:1841: brjod de / glo bur du bsags pa de ni
NK050(wi)001:1842: dri ma sel byed kyi rkyen gyis cha tsam la
NK050(wi)001:1843: rgyu tshogs gnyis zhes btags pa tsam ste /
NK050(wi)001:1844: nor bu dri mas gos pa khrus ras dang 'dag
NK050(wi)001:1845: chal gyis phyi ba la nor bu mthong ba'i rgyur
NK050(wi)001:1847: de'i phyir sku gsum rang byung ye shes kyi snang bar 'dus la /
NK050(wi)001:1848: rang byung gi ye shes sku gsum la sogs pa'i chos rnams kyi 'char gazhi'am ston par gnas te /
NK050(wi)001:1850: rang byung ye shes kun gyi ston pa gcig /
NK050(wi)001:1851: nga yi rang bzhin rnam gsum snang ba las //
NK050(wi)001:1852: ston pa'i grangs ni rnam pa gsum du byung //
NK050(wi)001:1855: de bzhin du rong zom pa'i mnyam sbyor 'grel ba las /
NK050(wi)001:1856: de nyid rang byung yin te /
NK050(wi)001:1857: rgyu dang rkyen las ma bskyed pa'i bcom ldan 'das so //
NK050(wi)001:1859: byang chub kyi sems ni rigs dang bshes gnyen gyi stobs kyis bskyed pa yin /
NK050(wi)001:1860: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs kyis mngon par bsgrub pa ma yin /
NK050(wi)001:1861: 'bras bu'i ngo bo bla na med pa'i sems dang /
NK050(wi)001:1862: thog ma med pa'i rigs kyi sems dag kyang rang bzhin bye brag tu gyur pa med de /
NK050(wi)001:1863: thams cad du mi phyed pa'i phyir rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:1864: kun tu bzang po zhes bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:1865: gang yang de'i dbang du mdzad pa'i gzugs kyi sku rnams la'ang de skad ces bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:1868: sems can kun gyi sems gang ni //
NK050(wi)001:1869: rdo rje zhes su bshad pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:1870: brtan pa'i phyir ni sems dpar brjod //
NK050(wi)001:1871: ces sogs gsungs pa lta bu ste /
NK050(wi)001:1872: sems nyid theg pa spyi la grags pa'i dang po rigs kyi sems kyi bdag nyid dang /
NK050(wi)001:1873: rigs dang bshes gshen gyi stobs la brten nas byang chub tu sems bskyed pa nas bzung ste /
NK050(wi)001:1874: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la thug pa'i rgyu yi gnas skabs kyi sems dang /
NK050(wi)001:1875: 'bras bu'i ngo bo bla na med pa sangs rgyas
NK050(wi)001:1876: kyi sa yis bsdus pa rnams gnas yongs su bsgyur
NK050(wi)001:1877: ba med pa ni rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya
NK050(wi)001:1878: / rdo rje sems dpa' ni rang gi bde ba'o //
NK050(wi)001:1879: rang gi bde ba ni sems kyi mtshan nyid do //
NK050(wi)001:1880: sems kyi mtshan nyid ni sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis su med pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:1881: zhes gsungs pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:1882: des na rigs gnyis kyang dbyings gcig gi snang stong
NK050(wi)001:1883: gi ldog chas phye ba tsam las ngo bo'am rang
NK050(wi)001:1884: bzhin dbyer med zag med 'dus ma byas chen la
NK050(wi)001:1885: bzhag pa 'di kun mkhyen chos rje'i dgongs pa rma
NK050(wi)001:1888: de'ang rang bzhin gyis dag cing ngo bo nyid dri
NK050(wi)001:1889: ma med pa'i sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK050(wi)001:1890: dam pa ye nas gnas pa'i sems kyi rang bzhin
NK050(wi)001:1891: 'od gsal ba'i snang cha las sangs rgyas gzugs sku'i
NK050(wi)001:1892: yon tan lhun grub tu yod pa dpe dgus bstan
NK050(wi)001:1893: cing / stong cha la chos sku'i yon tan nam
NK050(wi)001:1894: mkha' lta bu'i dpe mdo dang rgyud thams cad nas
NK050(wi)001:1895: cing / bshad la / de gnyis dbyer mi phyed
NK050(wi)001:1896: pa ni thog ma med pa'i chos khams dge ba
NK050(wi)001:1897: cing / bshad la / ste / 'gyur ba med pas rang bzhin gnas pa'i rigs dang /
NK050(wi)001:1898: dri ma sbyangs nas yon tan rgyas par mngon pas rgyas 'gyur gyi rigs zhes btags kyang /
NK050(wi)001:1899: rtsa ba rang rig pa'i ye shes 'od gsal ba'o //
NK050(wi)001:1901: de bzhin kun gzigs rong zom pa'i gsungs /
NK050(wi)001:1902: mnyam sbyor 'brel ba'i lung gong du drangs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:1904: 'di ltar rdo rje ltar mi shigs pa ni /
NK050(wi)001:1905: thog ma med pa'i dus can gyi byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK050(wi)001:1906: rigs dang bshes gnyen gyi stobs la bsten nas byang
NK050(wi)001:1907: chub kyi sems bskyed pa nas bzung ste rdo rje
NK050(wi)001:1908: lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la thug gi bar du
NK050(wi)001:1909: de'i rgyu'i gnas skabs kyi sems dang 'bras bu'i ngo
NK050(wi)001:1910: bo dpag bsam gyi shing dang yid bzhin gyi nor
NK050(wi)001:1911: bu rin po che lta bu'i chos kyi sku mdzad
NK050(wi)001:1912: pa dang bcas pa'i sems rnams rang bzhin bye brag
NK050(wi)001:1913: med pas rdo rje ltar mi phyed pa kun tu
NK050(wi)001:1914: bzang po'i sems zhes gzhi lam 'bras gsum dbyer med
NK050(wi)001:1915: pa'i rang byung gi ye shes la byang chub kyi
NK050(wi)001:1916: sems sam rigs su gsungs pas mtshon /
NK050(wi)001:1917: chos kyi rgyal po smin gling pa sku mched sogs
NK050(wi)001:1918: snga 'gyur gyi pan grub thams cad kyis tshul de
NK050(wi)001:1919: dang mthun par zhal gyis bzhes pa sha stag ste
NK050(wi)001:1920: / zhib par rje thams cad mkhyen pa 'jam dpal
NK050(wi)001:1921: dgyes pa'i gsung bde gshegs snying po'i stong thun dang
NK050(wi)001:1922: gzhan stong khas len seng ge'i nga ro /
NK050(wi)001:1923: gnyug sems sgrub pa yan lag dang bcas pa las shes par bya la /
NK050(wi)001:1924: de dang mthun par 'gro ba'i mgon po a ti shas kyang /
NK050(wi)001:1925: chos kyi dbyings la lta ba'i glu las /
NK050(wi)001:1926: ji ltar sbrum ma'i lto na bu //
NK050(wi)001:1927: yod kyang mthong ba ma yin pa //
NK050(wi)001:1928: de bzhin nyon mongs kyis g.yog pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:1929: chos kyi dbyings kyang mthong ba yin //
NK050(wi)001:1930: chos dbyings gang phyir bdag ma yin //
NK050(wi)001:1931: bud med ma yin skyes ma yin //
NK050(wi)001:1932: gzung ba kun las rnam grol ba //
NK050(wi)001:1933: ji ltar 'dzin par brtag par bya //
NK050(wi)001:1934: mi gtsang mi rtag sdug bsngal zhes //
NK050(wi)001:1935: bya ba gsum pos sems sbyong byed //
NK050(wi)001:1936: stong pa nyid ni ston pa'i mdo //
NK050(wi)001:1937: rgyal bas ji skad gsungs pa ste //
NK050(wi)001:1938: de dag kun gyis nyon mongs ldog /
NK050(wi)001:1939: khams de nyams par byed ma yin //
NK050(wi)001:1941: chos dbyings rang bzhin nam mkha' yi //
NK050(wi)001:1942: khams ltar rgyu med rkyen med de //
NK050(wi)001:1943: skye dang rga dang gnas pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:1945: sangs rgyas chos dbyer med pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:1946: de rigs de bzhin thob pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:1947: brdzun med bslu med 'tshe med pa //
NK050(wi)001:1948: gdod nas rang bzhin zhi nyid do //
NK050(wi)001:1949: zhes kun brtag las nyon gyis stong zhing zag med
NK050(wi)001:1950: kyi yon tan dang rnam dbyer med pa'i chos dbyings
NK050(wi)001:1951: snang stong zung 'jug 'dus ma byas la rigs su
NK050(wi)001:1953: til+li pas 'og min nas spyan drangs pa'i bka' yang
NK050(wi)001:1954: dag pa'i tshad ma zhes mkha' 'gro ma'i man ngag
NK050(wi)001:1955: las / ji ltar mar me bum nang gnas //
NK050(wi)001:1956: phyi rol du ni snang mi 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:1957: bum pa de nyid bcag gyur na //
NK050(wi)001:1959: de bzhin bum pa rang lus nyid //
NK050(wi)001:1960: 'od gsal mar me lta bu yin //
NK050(wi)001:1961: bla ma'i zhal gyis legs bcag na //
NK050(wi)001:1962: sangs rgyas ye shes gsal bar 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:1964: ti los na ro la gnang ba'i phyag chen gang+ga mar /
NK050(wi)001:1965: dper na nam mkha'i rang bzhin kha dog dbyibs las 'das /
NK050(wi)001:1966: dkar nag dag gis gos shing 'gyur ba med //
NK050(wi)001:1967: de bzhin rang sems snying po kha dog dbyibs las 'das //
NK050(wi)001:1968: dge sdig dkar nag chos kyis gos pa med //
NK050(wi)001:1969: bskal pa'i 'khor bas sgrib par mi nus so //
NK050(wi)001:1971: slob dpon gnyis med rdo rjes mdzad pa'i de kho
NK050(wi)001:1972: na nyid bcu pa zhes mnga' bdag mee tri pa'i
NK050(wi)001:1973: gdams skor las / de bzhin nyid ni shes 'dod pas //
NK050(wi)001:1974: rnam bcas ma yin rnam med min //
NK050(wi)001:1975: bla ma'i ngag gis ma brgyan pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:1976: dbu ma'ang 'bring po tsam du gnas //
NK050(wi)001:1978: bram ze chen pos mnga' bdag mar pa la gdams pa'i mgur las kyang /
NK050(wi)001:1979: stong nyid snying rje dbyer med pa //
NK050(wi)001:1980: rgyun chad med pa gnyug ma'i sems //
NK050(wi)001:1981: gdod nas dag pa'i de bzhin nyid //
NK050(wi)001:1982: nam mkha' nam mkha' sbyor ba mthong //
NK050(wi)001:1984: rje mi las snyi ba rin chen la gnang ba'i snyan brgyud dngos po gsal byed las /
NK050(wi)001:1985: lus can dag ni kun la yang //
NK050(wi)001:1986: snying po'i don 'di gdod nas gnas //
NK050(wi)001:1987: des na sems can sangs rgyas rgyu //
NK050(wi)001:1988: rgyu las 'bras bu thebs pa la //
NK050(wi)001:1989: gdod nas thebs kyis da ltar min //
NK050(wi)001:1991: bye brag ngoms rdzong snyan brgyud rtsa ba tshe ring skor gsum gyi zhus lan rdo rje'i mgur las /
NK050(wi)001:1992: don dam bden pa'i dbang du ni /
NK050(wi)001:1993: bgegs bas sangs rgyas nyid du med //
NK050(wi)001:1995: kun rdzob bden pa'i dbang du ni //
NK050(wi)001:1997: thams cad yod ces thub pas gsungs //
NK050(wi)001:1998: zhes gnas skabs su rnam grangs pa'i bden gnyis so sor phyes nas /
NK050(wi)001:2000: yod pa dngos por snang ba dang //
NK050(wi)001:2001: med pa stong pa'i chos nyid gnyis //
NK050(wi)001:2002: ngo bo dbyer med ro gcig pas //
NK050(wi)001:2003: rang rig gzhan rig yod min te //
NK050(wi)001:2004: thams cad zung 'jug yangs pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:2005: zhes rnam grangs min pa'i don dam nyid rtsal 'don du mdzad nas /
NK050(wi)001:2006: de ltar rtogs pa'i mkhas pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:2007: rnam shes ma mthong ye shes mthong //
NK050(wi)001:2008: de las snying rje shugs 'byung ste //
NK050(wi)001:2009: stobs dang mi 'jigs gzungs la sogs //
NK050(wi)001:2010: sangs rgyas yon tan gang yin pa //
NK050(wi)001:2011: nor bu rin chen tshul du byung //
NK050(wi)001:2012: de rnal 'byor bdag gi rtogs tshad yin //
NK050(wi)001:2013: zhes dri med 'phags pa'i ye shes kyis gzigs tshul
NK050(wi)001:2014: sgra ji bzhin par drang thad du ston par mdzad
NK050(wi)001:2015: pa dang / zhang rin po ches lam mchog mthar thug tu /
NK050(wi)001:2016: nges don mthar thug snying po chos kyi sku //
NK050(wi)001:2017: ngo bo nyid kyis rnam dag 'od gsal dbyings //
NK050(wi)001:2018: dus gsum rgyal ba byon rung ma byon rung //
NK050(wi)001:2019: 'phags pa'i tshogs kyis rtogs rung ma rtogs rung //
NK050(wi)001:2020: thub pa rnams kyis gsungs rung ma gsungs rung //
NK050(wi)001:2021: dgongs 'grel mkhan pos dkrol rung ma dkrol rung //
NK050(wi)001:2022: chos nyid 'od gsal spros bral rnam dag 'di //
NK050(wi)001:2023: ye nas lhun grub 'phel 'grib med par gnas //
NK050(wi)001:2024: nam mkha' dag la 'jig rten chags 'jig gi //
NK050(wi)001:2025: me yis bsregs dang rlung gis gtor la sogs //
NK050(wi)001:2026: bskal pa dpag med mang por gnod byas kyang //
NK050(wi)001:2027: mkha' la mi gnod 'phel 'grib med pa ltar //
NK050(wi)001:2028: nyi 'od rab gsal sprin gyis rab bsgribs pas //
NK050(wi)001:2029: mun pa 'thibs dang sprin tshogs yal ba'i tshe //
NK050(wi)001:2030: gsal bar 'gyur ba'i 'phel 'grib ltar snang gi //
NK050(wi)001:2031: nyi ma'i snying po 'phel dang 'grib mi srid //
NK050(wi)001:2032: de ltar gnas pa'i 'gyur med chos sku 'di //
NK050(wi)001:2033: rang gi sems las ma gtogs gzhan na med //
NK050(wi)001:2034: sna tshogs 'khor ba ma lus sems las shar //
NK050(wi)001:2035: rang sems ma rtogs phyin log 'khrul snang gis //
NK050(wi)001:2036: dkrugs pas 'khor ba'i snod bcud sdug bsngal 'phel //
NK050(wi)001:2037: rang sems nges rtogs mya ngan 'das pa yi //
NK050(wi)001:2038: ye shes mtha' yas bde ba chen por shar //
NK050(wi)001:2039: de phyir ma lus rang gi sems nyid las //
NK050(wi)001:2040: 'phros phyir rang gi sems nyid ngo shes na //
NK050(wi)001:2041: sems can kun gyi chos nyid shes par 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:2042: de shes mya ngan 'das sogs chos kun shes //
NK050(wi)001:2043: chos kun yongs shes khams gsum kun las 'das //
NK050(wi)001:2044: gcig shes pas na chos kun mkhas par 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:2046: rgyal dbang rang byung zhabs kyis nang don rang 'brel du /
NK050(wi)001:2047: chos kun dang theg bsdus kyi lung gis rigs kyi dbye ba rgyas par bshad nas /
NK050(wi)001:2048: yang rgyas 'gyur gyi rigs de gsar du byung ba
NK050(wi)001:2049: snyam du kha cig sems na de lta ma yin
NK050(wi)001:2050: te zhes sogs kyi rang bzhin gnas rigs chos dbyings
NK050(wi)001:2051: dang / rgyas 'gyur tshogs brgyad dag pa'i ye shes
NK050(wi)001:2052: de dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su gsal bar bstan
NK050(wi)001:2054: chu khams gser dang nam mkha' rnams //
NK050(wi)001:2055: dag pa bzhin du rnam dag 'dod //
NK050(wi)001:2056: ces pa dbus mtha'i lung gis rang bzhin rnam dag tu sgrub cing /
NK050(wi)001:2057: gzhung chung gnyis nas kyang gsal bar bstan pa bzhin /
NK050(wi)001:2059: yon tan kyi chos drug cu rtsa bzhi dang rnam
NK050(wi)001:2060: dbyer med pa'i dbyings stong nyid la rnam mchog gi
NK050(wi)001:2061: stong nyid du bzhed pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2062: si tu kun mkhyen sogs kyi bzhed tshul bka' brgyud yongs la grags pa ltar dang /
NK050(wi)001:2064: nges par dngos po thams cad kyi //
NK050(wi)001:2065: dag pa de bzhin nyid du brjod //
NK050(wi)001:2066: phyes nas re re'i dbye ba yis //
NK050(wi)001:2067: lha rnams kyis ni brjod par bya //
NK050(wi)001:2068: phung po lnga dang dbang po drug /
NK050(wi)001:2069: skye mched drug dang 'byung chen lnga //
NK050(wi)001:2070: rang bzhin gyis ni rnam par dag /
NK050(wi)001:2071: nyon mongs shes bya'i sgrib sbyang bya //
NK050(wi)001:2072: rang nyid bdag nyid dag pa nyid //
NK050(wi)001:2073: dag pa gzhan gyis rnam grol min //
NK050(wi)001:2074: zhes gsungs pa'i don rgyud gsum la dag pa gsum
NK050(wi)001:2075: gsum sbyor te 'chad pa'i tshul yang don gyis 'di
NK050(wi)001:2077: rje btsun rtse mos mdzad pa'i rnam bshad nyi zer las /
NK050(wi)001:2078: de bzhin nyid las ni chos kyi sku'o //
NK050(wi)001:2079: rang rig pa las ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:2080: lha so so las ni sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK050(wi)001:2081: yang na de bzhin nyid ni dbyings yin la //
NK050(wi)001:2082: rang rig pa ni ye shes yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:2083: de gnyis las lha so so'i gzugs kyi sku 'byung ngo //
NK050(wi)001:2085: ci gal te de ltar 'bras bu'i chos sku dang gzugs sku dbyer med pa yin la /
NK050(wi)001:2086: lam gyi dus su'ang dbyer med yin mod /
NK050(wi)001:2087: rgyu'i rgyud rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa yin nam ma yin /
NK050(wi)001:2088: ma yin na grol bar mi 'gyur la /
NK050(wi)001:2089: yin na lam la don med par 'gyur ro snyam na /
NK050(wi)001:2090: de la rang bzhin gyis sangs rgyas kyi sku gnas so zhes ston pa ni /
NK050(wi)001:2091: zhal phyag rnam pa'i gzugs can nyid //
NK050(wi)001:2092: sogs kyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i gzugs sku dang /
NK050(wi)001:2093: mchog tu bde ba gzugs med pa //
NK050(wi)001:2094: sogs kyis chos kyi sku ste de gnyis ka'ang /
NK050(wi)001:2095: 'gro ba kun la lhan cig skyes //
NK050(wi)001:2096: zhes sems can la lhan skyes su gnas pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2097: 'on kyang bag chags phal las so //
NK050(wi)001:2098: zhes da lta glo bur gyi dri mas sgrib pa'i don du gsungs pa bzhin /
NK050(wi)001:2099: rgyu rgyud kyi dag pa gsum gyi dbyings de bzhin
NK050(wi)001:2100: nyid chos sku'i bral rgyu rang bzhin gnas rigs dngos
NK050(wi)001:2101: dang / rang rig pa ye shes longs sku dang /
NK050(wi)001:2102: lha sku'i dag pa sprul sku'i bral rgyu yin pas phyi ma gnyis rgyas 'gyur dang don gcig /
NK050(wi)001:2103: des na rgyu rgyud kyi gsum po rang bzhin gyis
NK050(wi)001:2104: dag pas sol ba la dkar po'i nus pa med
NK050(wi)001:2105: pa ltar sbyang du mi rung ba ma yin pa
NK050(wi)001:2106: dang / de bzhin nyid lta ba /
NK050(wi)001:2107: gzhan gnyis bskyed rdzogs bsgom pa ste lam rgyud kyi
NK050(wi)001:2108: gsum po'ang gnas tshul dang mthun par rang bzhin gyis
NK050(wi)001:2109: dag pas mu stegs byed kyi lam ltar dri ma
NK050(wi)001:2110: sbyong mi nus pa ma yin pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2111: 'bras rgyud kyi sku gsum rang bzhin gyis dag pas
NK050(wi)001:2112: spang ba slar mi ldog pa chu khams gser sogs
NK050(wi)001:2113: gong smos dbus mtha'i lung gis sgrub ste rje btsun
NK050(wi)001:2114: grags pas rnam 'grel dag ldan du gsungs pa dang
NK050(wi)001:2115: / sa pan gyis rang bzhed mthar thug bstod 'grel du /
NK050(wi)001:2116: sems kyi chos nyid rang bzhin gyis dag kyang sems
NK050(wi)001:2117: kyi mtshan nyid la glo bur gyi dri mas bsgribs
NK050(wi)001:2118: pa'i tshul dang / dri ma glo bur ba yin pas sbyang du rung ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:2119: de bsal bas sangs rgyas su 'gyur tshul /
NK050(wi)001:2120: de'i tshe chos nyid la ltos nas gnas 'gyur ba med pa rigs tshogs kyi dgongs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2121: yon tan snang tshul la ltos nas gnas gyur yod pa bstod tshogs kyi dgongs pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:2122: de gnyis gnad kyis mi 'gal ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:2123: sangs rgyas la ye shes med par 'dod pa phyogs sngar bzhag nas /
NK050(wi)001:2124: rang bzhed sangs rgyas la ye shes med pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2125: sku med pa ma yin pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2126: de gnyis dbyer med par gsungs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2127: snye mo sgom chen gyi dris lan du /
NK050(wi)001:2128: sems stong par rtogs pa la sde snod gsum dang
NK050(wi)001:2129: rgyud sde bzhir brtsi mi gtub nyan thos 'gog pa
NK050(wi)001:2130: dang mtshungs / zung 'jug tu rtogs pa la brtsi na bzhag tu rung /
NK050(wi)001:2131: sems stong cha rkyang bar dkon mchog gsum mi tshang /
NK050(wi)001:2132: rig stong zung 'jug la sa bon tshang /
NK050(wi)001:2133: zung 'jug gi don legs par rtogs na mngon gyur du tshang ba yin /
NK050(wi)001:2135: spros bral du gtan la phab nas zung 'jug nyams su len pa /
NK050(wi)001:2137: rgyu dus kyi lta ba dug can dang /
NK050(wi)001:2138: 'bras dus kyi lta ba dug med ces snga ma
NK050(wi)001:2139: thos bsam gyis gzhal ba'i dpyad stong spros bral tsam
NK050(wi)001:2140: ste des go mi chod par phyi ma bde stong
NK050(wi)001:2141: rig stong zung 'jug dbang dang rim gnyis las byung
NK050(wi)001:2142: ba sangs rgyas kyi sa'i yon tan ye shes dang
NK050(wi)001:2143: ngo bo gcig par bzhed pa sogs dpal ldan sa
NK050(wi)001:2144: skya pa rnams la yongs su grags pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2145: gzhan yang bdag nyid chen po tsong kha pas kyang sngags kyi tshul khrims rnam bshad sogs su /
NK050(wi)001:2146: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis dag pa rang bzhin med pa'i stong nyid spros bral dang /
NK050(wi)001:2147: chos can gzugs sogs phung lnga rnam snang sogs sangs
NK050(wi)001:2148: rgyas lnga'i bdag nyid de rang bzhin du gsungs pa
NK050(wi)001:2149: sogs dang / khyad par lam gyi gtso bo rnam gsum du /
NK050(wi)001:2150: gang zhig 'khor 'das chos rnams thams cad kyi //
NK050(wi)001:2151: rgyu 'bras nam yang bslu ba med mthong zhing //
NK050(wi)001:2152: dmigs pa'i gtad so gang yin kun zhig pa //
NK050(wi)001:2153: de tshe sangs rgyas dgyes pa'i lam la zhugs //
NK050(wi)001:2154: snang ba rten 'brel bslu ba med pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:2155: stong pa khas len bral ba'i go ba gnyis //
NK050(wi)001:2156: ji srid so sor gnas pa de srid du //
NK050(wi)001:2157: da dung thub pa'i dgongs pa rtogs pa med //
NK050(wi)001:2158: nam zhig res 'jog med par cig car du //
NK050(wi)001:2159: rten 'brel mi bslur mthong ba tsam nyid nas //
NK050(wi)001:2160: nges shes yul gyi 'dzin stangs kun 'jig na //
NK050(wi)001:2161: de tshe lta ba'i dpyad pa rdzogs pa lags //
NK050(wi)001:2162: zhes snang stong zug 'jug rnam grangs min pa'i don dam nyid rtsal 'don mdzad pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2163: kun mkhyen dol po sangs rgyas kyis ri chos nges don rgya mtshor gsungs pa sogs kyang /
NK050(wi)001:2164: gnas skabs su snang stong gnyis rtsal 'don che chung dang /
NK050(wi)001:2165: bden gnyis 'jog mtshams tha dad pa sogs grub mtha'i zhal bzhes phra mo'i khyad par tsam las /
NK050(wi)001:2166: don la bden gnyis ro mnyam rnam grangs min pa'i
NK050(wi)001:2167: don dam mthar thug blo bral ye shes chen po'i
NK050(wi)001:2168: klong du / chos nyid kyi bden pa gzigs pa'i
NK050(wi)001:2169: 'phags chen rnams kyi dgongs pa'i gsang mdzod chu dang
NK050(wi)001:2170: lan tsh+wa bzhin dbyer med ro mnyam pas mtshur mthong
NK050(wi)001:2171: byis blos gzhal bya'i yul min te /
NK050(wi)001:2173: gang phyir de ni rgya mtsho ltar //
NK050(wi)001:2174: sgra dang dpe dang blo rnams kyis //
NK050(wi)001:2175: gting dang pha rol mi rnyed pas //
NK050(wi)001:2176: de phyir rab tu zab pa nyid //
NK050(wi)001:2178: chos la skur pa mi 'debs shing //
NK050(wi)001:2179: gang mos de la 'dun par bya //
NK050(wi)001:2181: gzhan yang bde mchog nyung ngu'i rgyud dang byams gzhung dang /
NK050(wi)001:2182: rin chen phreng ba sogs las gsungs pa'i don rnams
NK050(wi)001:2183: dran par byas nas bdag nyid kyis bdag nyid srung
NK050(wi)001:2184: bar byed pa 'di shin tu gal che bar mngon
NK050(wi)001:2185: no // de'i phyir tshig spyi sbas mthar gang ltar bshad kyang mi 'gal bas /
NK050(wi)001:2186: don gnad mdo tsam smos na /
NK050(wi)001:2187: slob dpon legs ldan gyis mdzad pa'i dbu ma'i bstan bcos rin chen sgron mar /
NK050(wi)001:2188: dbu ma phra rags gnyis su gsungs pa ltar /
NK050(wi)001:2189: rags pa phyi'i dbu ma thal rang gi skabs su /
NK050(wi)001:2190: 'khor lo bar pa'i bstan bya'i gtso bo gnas skabs
NK050(wi)001:2191: su chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis ma grub pa
NK050(wi)001:2192: dang / kun rdzob rten 'byung gi snang ba gnyis mi 'gal bar gtan la phabs nas /
NK050(wi)001:2193: mthar thug rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam la sbyor bar mdzad pa yin la /
NK050(wi)001:2194: phra ba nang gi dbu ma'i skabs de nyid gzhir bzhag gi steng du /
NK050(wi)001:2195: 'khor lo tha ma'i bstan don rtogs bya lta bas
NK050(wi)001:2196: gtan la 'bebs pa'i yul chos dbyings de yang med
NK050(wi)001:2197: dgag phyogs gcig pa'i stong rkyang tsam min par sku
NK050(wi)001:2198: dang ye shes kyis brgyan pa'i snang ba dang tha
NK050(wi)001:2199: mi dad pa'i rang byung zag med 'dus ma byas
NK050(wi)001:2200: su sgrub pa'i khyad par tsam ste /
NK050(wi)001:2201: gnyis kas mnyam bzhag tu bsal bzhag dang bral ba'i
NK050(wi)001:2202: chos dbyings mnyam par 'jog pa ste de'i ngor gzung
NK050(wi)001:2203: 'dzin mtshan ma'i spros pa tha dag 'gog pa la
NK050(wi)001:2205: rjes thob tu snga mas stong nyid la don dam dang /
NK050(wi)001:2206: snang ba la kun rdzob tu bzhag ste bden gnyis dbye bar mdzad cing /
NK050(wi)001:2207: phyi mas gnas snang mthun mi mthun la bden gnyis 'jog pa'i khyad par ro //
NK050(wi)001:2208: de yang snga ma gtan la ma phebs na phyi ma nyid gtan la 'bebs mi nus pas /
NK050(wi)001:2209: thog mar dbu ma rigs tshogs kyi dgongs pa thal 'gyur ba ltar /
NK050(wi)001:2213: rang bzhin gyis mya ngan las 'das pa /
NK050(wi)001:2214: zung 'jug 'phags pa'i ye shes kyi spyod yul du
NK050(wi)001:2215: gyur pa'i mthar thug rnam grangs min pa'i don dam
NK050(wi)001:2216: nyid gtan la phebs par bya zhing /
NK050(wi)001:2217: de phebs pa na byams gzhung dang bstod tshogs sogs
NK050(wi)001:2218: kyi dgongs pa ltar sku dang ye shes sogs zag
NK050(wi)001:2219: pa med pa'i chos rnams kyang chos kyi dbyings de
NK050(wi)001:2220: dang ngo bo tha mi dad pa'i phyir rang byung
NK050(wi)001:2221: 'dus ma byas su mi 'grub pa'i gnas med la
NK050(wi)001:2222: / chos dbyings snang stong zung 'jug mi 'gal ba'ang
NK050(wi)001:2223: gong gis bden gnyis dpyod pa'i mthar thug dpyod rigs
NK050(wi)001:2224: / kyis grub / de ma grub na thal 'gyur rang yang mi 'grub /
NK050(wi)001:2225: de nyid da lta sems can la mi snang zhing
NK050(wi)001:2226: sangs rgyas kyi sar mngon gyur du snang ba dang
NK050(wi)001:2227: / da lta'i bag chags 'khrul snang 'di sems can
NK050(wi)001:2228: la snang sangs rgyas dus mi snang ba gnyis gnyid
NK050(wi)001:2229: du song ma song gi snang ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:2230: ma sad pa dang sad dus kyi rmi lam bzhin
NK050(wi)001:2231: tha snyad du tshad mas grub pas bden gnyis 'jog
NK050(wi)001:2232: mtshams phyi ma 'di yang bde blag tu shes nus
NK050(wi)001:2233: / de ltar bden mi bden sogs su bzhag pa
NK050(wi)001:2234: 'di tha dpyod ngor yin pas don dpyod ngor bden
NK050(wi)001:2235: grub tu sgrub pa min pa'i gnad gzhan stong khas
NK050(wi)001:2236: len du gsungs pa ltar shes par bya la /
NK050(wi)001:2237: de lta'i tshul gyis chos dbyings snang stong zung 'jug
NK050(wi)001:2238: rnam grangs min pa'i don dam 'di nyid mthar thug
NK050(wi)001:2239: theg gcig tu sgrub pa'i gzhi yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:2240: 'di nyid sngags su e wam dang /
NK050(wi)001:2246: rang byung gi ye shes sogs su gsungs pa yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:2247: de ltar shes na 'di nyid nges don mthar thug tu grub pa la smyon du med pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:2248: tshul 'di ni sngags phyi rgyud rnams su /
NK050(wi)001:2249: bdag gi de kho na nyid dang /
NK050(wi)001:2250: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i byin brlabs rdo rje dbyings kyi lha dang /
NK050(wi)001:2251: nang par ma h+aa'i bden pa dbyer med blo'i spyod yul dang bral ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:2252: a nu'i dbyings ye dbyer med dang /
NK050(wi)001:2253: mthar thug rdzogs chen gyi ka dag lhun grub zung
NK050(wi)001:2254: 'jug gdod ma gzhi yi bzhugs tshul gsungs pa rnams
NK050(wi)001:2256: thog mar 'di nyid gtan la phebs par mi 'gyur zhing /
NK050(wi)001:2257: 'di nyid legs par go na phyi ma rnams kyang
NK050(wi)001:2258: rim bzhin gtan la 'bebs pa la dka' ba med
NK050(wi)001:2259: pa'i dpyod kyi mthu thob par 'gyur bas /
NK050(wi)001:2260: tshul 'di ltar shes pa cis kyang gal che'o //
NK050(wi)001:2261: de'i phyir don gyi gnad 'di la /
NK050(wi)001:2262: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po dang /
NK050(wi)001:2264: kun mkhyen dol po gsum dgongs pa mthun par sngon
NK050(wi)001:2265: gyi dam pa rnams bzhed pa nyid don la gnas
NK050(wi)001:2266: par mthong ste / gsum kas 'khor lo tha ma nges don mthar thug tu bzhed cing /
NK050(wi)001:2267: snga ma gnyis kyi gsung ci rigs sngar drangs pas shes la /
NK050(wi)001:2268: kun mkhyen dol bos ri chos nges don rgya mtshor /
NK050(wi)001:2269: dri ma sbyang ba'i gzhi bde gshegs snying po /
NK050(wi)001:2270: dri ma sbyong ba'i lam rdo rje'i rnal 'byor /
NK050(wi)001:2271: dri ma dag pa'i gzhi bral 'bras chos sku zhes dang /
NK050(wi)001:2272: gang zhig chos rnams kun gyis dben yang zag med bgrang yas chos kyi sku /
NK050(wi)001:2273: chos dang gang zag bdag dang bral yang de bzhin nyid bdag dag pa'i bdag /
NK050(wi)001:2274: yod med rtag chad mtha' las 'das kyang brtag brtan g.yung drung nyid du bzhugs /
NK050(wi)001:2275: dngos rnams kun gyi rang bzhin med kyang rang bzhin 'od gsal la btud nas /
NK050(wi)001:2276: zhes mchod brjod du gsungs pa ltar /
NK050(wi)001:2277: don dam pa stong pa nyid dang bdag med pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2279: rang bzhin med pa'i spros bral mnyam pa chen por gtan la phab nas /
NK050(wi)001:2280: de nyid zag med kyi yon tan gyi chos rnams dang dbyer med pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2281: de las 'khor 'das kyi chos kun 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2282: rang bzhin 'gyur med kyi cha nas chos kyi sku
NK050(wi)001:2283: dang dag pa'i bdag sogs kyi sgras tha snyad du
NK050(wi)001:2284: bstan pa dang / khyad par rigs kyi skabs /
NK050(wi)001:2286: 'das pa'i de bzhin nyid gang ma byon de bzhin nyid //
NK050(wi)001:2287: da ltar de bzhin nyid gang dgra bcom de bzhin nyid //
NK050(wi)001:2288: chos kun de bzhin nyid gang rgyal ba'i de bzhin nyid //
NK050(wi)001:2289: chos kun de bzhin nyid 'di thams cad bye brag med //
NK050(wi)001:2291: 'di ni chos gter mchog dang chos mdzad dam pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:2292: sangs rgyas rigs yin 'gro ba'i bde dang skyid pa'i mdzod //
NK050(wi)001:2293: 'das dang ma byon phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten mgon po rnams //
NK050(wi)001:2294: de dag 'di las 'khrungs kyang chos dbyings zad mi 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:2295: zhes drangs te gzhi 'bras ngo bo dbyer med pa'i sher phyin dang /
NK050(wi)001:2296: 'khor lo mtha' mar rang bzhin gnas rigs su gsungs pa don gcig par bzhed pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2297: dpal ldan zla bas mdzad pa'i sgron gsal du /
NK050(wi)001:2298: rgyal ba kun gyi gnas ni sems can thams cad
NK050(wi)001:2299: de de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po yin pa'i phyir
NK050(wi)001:2300: ro // zhes gsungs pas mtshon mthar thug rgyud sde
NK050(wi)001:2301: rnams su gsungs pa'i stong nyid snying rje dbyer med
NK050(wi)001:2302: pa'i rdo rje'i rigs chen po ste de gnyis dbyer
NK050(wi)001:2303: med pa la sbyang gzhir bzhag nas /
NK050(wi)001:2304: de sbyong ba'i lam rgyal ba'i sa bon bzang po las byung bsod nams tshogs las gang 'khrungs pa /
NK050(wi)001:2306: blo bur gyi dri ma mtha' dag bsal ba'i ched
NK050(wi)001:2307: du rnam par dag pa'i ye shes kyi tshogs 'khor
NK050(wi)001:2308: dang bcas pa sgrub pa la brtson pa gang yin
NK050(wi)001:2309: pa zhes thun mong du sku gnyis la sgrib byed
NK050(wi)001:2310: kyi dri ma sel ba'i phyir lam tshogs gnyis la
NK050(wi)001:2313: rdo rje'i rnal 'byor sogs la brten nas zung 'jug
NK050(wi)001:2314: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes rtsal 'don du mdzad
NK050(wi)001:2315: de rang bzhin snying po dril te gsungs pa /
NK050(wi)001:2316: 'dir gnyis med ye shes zhes pa la /
NK050(wi)001:2317: gang dang gang gnyis su med na /
NK050(wi)001:2318: chos kyi dbyings dang rang byung gyi ye shes gcig tu 'dres shing ro mnyam pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:2319: de nyid mthar thug gi stong nyid snying rje dang /
NK050(wi)001:2321: bde stong dbyer med zung 'jug ro gcig pa yang yin la /
NK050(wi)001:2322: mthar thug gnas lugs kyi shes dang shes bya gcig pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2323: dbyings rig dbyer med ro gcig pa yang yin no //
NK050(wi)001:2324: de lta bu'i sher phyin mtshan nyid pa de ni /
NK050(wi)001:2326: 'bras bu'i sher phyin mthar thug pa ste ngo bo dbyer med pa'i de bzhin nyid do //
NK050(wi)001:2327: de mngon du byed pa'i lam dang /
NK050(wi)001:2328: de ston pa'i gzhung la ni btag pa tsam ste /
NK050(wi)001:2329: de bzhin du dbu ma chen po dang /
NK050(wi)001:2332: sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par sbyor ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:2338: de bzhin nyid kyi rnam grangs su gtogs pa ji
NK050(wi)001:2339: snyed gsungs pa rnams la yang gzhung lam gang yin
NK050(wi)001:2341: gzhi dang 'bras bu ngo bo dbyer med gang yin
NK050(wi)001:2342: pa thams cad mtshan nyid pa nyid du gsungs nas
NK050(wi)001:2343: te / 'di ni mdo rgyud zab mo mthar thug pa thams cad kyi spyi 'grel chen po dang /
NK050(wi)001:2344: rdo rje'i tshig tu gsungs pa thams cad kyi mdud 'grol chen mo dang /
NK050(wi)001:2345: dgongs te gsungs pa'am dgongs chen zab mo thams cad kyi don 'grel chen po yin /
NK050(wi)001:2346: 'on kyang de dag de ltar tshul bzhin du rtogs pa la /
NK050(wi)001:2347: skyo ma snga btsan gyi bag chags spangs nas ston pa bzhi dang /
NK050(wi)001:2348: sa bcu pa rnams kyi man ngag zab mo nyams
NK050(wi)001:2349: su myong ba'i sgron me bzang po la brten dgos
NK050(wi)001:2350: so // de'i phyir 'khor lo phyi ma gnyis dang /
NK050(wi)001:2351: rdo rje theg pa don gcig mod kyi nyams su len pa na /
NK050(wi)001:2352: la zlo ba chos nyid zab mo la 'khor lo
NK050(wi)001:2353: bar pa dang mthun par rtog med spros bral mnyam
NK050(wi)001:2354: par bzhag nas / rjes thob shan 'byed pa'i tshe /
NK050(wi)001:2355: chos rnams la yang dag par so sor rtog pa na 'khor lo tha ma dang /
NK050(wi)001:2356: rdo rje theg pa las gsungs pa bzhin legs par
NK050(wi)001:2357: rnam par phye ste ngo sprad na theg pa chen
NK050(wi)001:2358: po'i gsung rab thams cad kyi don zab mo nyams
NK050(wi)001:2359: su len pa tshang la ma nor zhing yongs su
NK050(wi)001:2362: don dam par chos dbyings zad 'phel med pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2363: kun rdzob glo bur gyi dri ma'ang don la yod
NK050(wi)001:2364: ma myong bas zad 'phel med pa'i chos nyid mnyam
NK050(wi)001:2365: pa chen po rgyal ba'i yum gyi dgongs don sgra
NK050(wi)001:2366: ji bzhin par bzhed pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2368: 'dir gzhi 'bras ngo bo dbyer med ces pa'ang don
NK050(wi)001:2369: dam chos sku'i dbang du byas kyi kun rdzob gzugs
NK050(wi)001:2371: lam mi dgos pa yang ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:2372: mnyam bzhag rnam par mi rtog pa'i shes rab gang
NK050(wi)001:2373: yin pa ye shes kyi tshogs kyis chos sku gdod
NK050(wi)001:2374: nas bzhugs pa'i dri ma bral bar byed cing /
NK050(wi)001:2375: rjes thob sgyu ma lta bur rtogs pa'i ye shes
NK050(wi)001:2376: dang ldan pa bsod nams kyi tshogs kyis gzhan don
NK050(wi)001:2377: brda'i sku bskyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK050(wi)001:2378: zhes gsungs te rgyud bla'i lung sogs drangs nas de ltar legs par shan phyes 'dug pas /
NK050(wi)001:2379: lta ba bka' rtags kyi phyag rgya dang 'gal min dang /
NK050(wi)001:2380: sbyong phyogs spangs pa'i ha shang gi lugs su 'gyur
NK050(wi)001:2381: min sogs dpyad pa ni gzhi med pa'i skur 'debs
NK050(wi)001:2382: tsam ste / blo dang ldan pa rnams kyis 'di'i
NK050(wi)001:2383: lung don la gzu bor dpyad pas shes nus so
NK050(wi)001:2384: tsam ste / // des na legs par brtag na /
NK050(wi)001:2385: rags pa phyi'am shes rab rgyu'i dbu ma la brten
NK050(wi)001:2386: nas bden gnyis kyi mtshan nyid legs par phyes te
NK050(wi)001:2387: bdag med gnyis kyi don gtan la phab nas nges
NK050(wi)001:2388: pa'i shes pa the tshom gyi smag dang bral ba
NK050(wi)001:2389: skyes pa na / mnyam bzhag sgom pa'i tshe phra
NK050(wi)001:2390: ba nang ngam zung 'jug 'bras bu'i dbu ma gnyis
NK050(wi)001:2391: med ye shes chen po'i don la rim gyis sbyor
NK050(wi)001:2392: zhing goms par byed pa la /
NK050(wi)001:2393: nges don gyi dbu ma rnam gnyis mthar thug gi dgongs par mi mthun pa ci'ang med de /
NK050(wi)001:2394: thal 'gyur bas blo gnyis snang ngam rnam shes kyi
NK050(wi)001:2395: spyod yul du gyur pa'i rnam grangs pa'i don dam
NK050(wi)001:2396: ni gnas skabs su 'jug pa'i sgo tsam las mthar
NK050(wi)001:2398: so so rang rig ye shes dam pa'i spyod yul
NK050(wi)001:2399: du gyur pa'i zung 'jug rnam grangs ma yin pa'i
NK050(wi)001:2400: don dam smra bsam brjod med shes rab phar phyin
NK050(wi)001:2402: dam pa'i don gyi bden pa gcig pur gsungs la /
NK050(wi)001:2403: de bzhin gzhan stong pas kyang tha dpyod ngor /
NK050(wi)001:2404: rnam shes yul dang bcas pa ni bslu ba brdzun
NK050(wi)001:2405: pa kun rdzob glog dang sprin lta bu ste de'i
NK050(wi)001:2407: ye shes yul dang bcas pa ni rtag pa brtan
NK050(wi)001:2408: pa 'pho 'gyur med pas bsal bzhag dang bral ba'i
NK050(wi)001:2409: chos nyid ni mthar thug mi bslu ba'i dbang gis
NK050(wi)001:2410: don dam par bzhag cing sgom pas na don gyis
NK050(wi)001:2411: gnad gcig cing / grub mtha'i khas len yod med kyang /
NK050(wi)001:2412: rang lugs kun mkhyen chen po'i bzhed pa /
NK050(wi)001:2413: theg chen 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag gi ye shes sam don dam nyid yul du byed pa'i tshe na /
NK050(wi)001:2414: de'i ngor med dgag dang ma yin dgag gi 'dzin
NK050(wi)001:2415: stangs sogs spros pa gang yang yod mi srid pa'i
NK050(wi)001:2416: phyir / zung 'jug spros bral mnyam pa chen por grub mtha'i khas len gang yang byar med la /
NK050(wi)001:2417: rjes thob tha snyad yul du byed pa'i tshe gzhi
NK050(wi)001:2418: lam 'bras bu'i rnam bzhag sogs tshad ma'i lung las
NK050(wi)001:2419: ji skad gsungs pa ltar shan phyes te gdon mi
NK050(wi)001:2420: za bar khas len par gsungs pa'i gnad kyang gnyis
NK050(wi)001:2422: gnyis kas don dpyod dam mnyam bzhag gi ngor yod
NK050(wi)001:2423: med sogs kyi spros pa'i mtshan rtogs mtha' dag bkag
NK050(wi)001:2424: nas bsal bzhag dang bral ba'i spros bral mnyam pa
NK050(wi)001:2425: chen por la bzla zhing mnyam par 'jog pa dang
NK050(wi)001:2426: / rjes thob kun rdzob tha dpyod ngor rang rang
NK050(wi)001:2427: gi grub mtha'i zhal bzhes kyi bden gnyis so sor
NK050(wi)001:2428: phyes te khas len pa'i phyir na'o //
NK050(wi)001:2429: de bas na don la rton par bya yi /
NK050(wi)001:2430: tshig tsam gyi rjes su 'brangs te /
NK050(wi)001:2431: dgag sgrub kyi spros pas ngal bar mi bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:2432: des na snang stong gang rung re'i phyogs su zhen
NK050(wi)001:2433: cing bzung bas ni mthar 'dzin gyi lta ba ngan
NK050(wi)001:2435: chos dbyings snang stong zung 'jug mthar thug rnam grangs
NK050(wi)001:2436: ma yin pa'i don dam srid zhi mnyam nyid du
NK050(wi)001:2437: legs par gtan la 'bebs dgos shing /
NK050(wi)001:2438: de nyid gtan la 'bebs pa'i tshul yang /
NK050(wi)001:2439: yid bzhin mdzod kyi le'u bco brgyad par gsungs pa ltar /
NK050(wi)001:2440: tha snyad du snang ba kun rdzob kyi chos kun
NK050(wi)001:2441: don la med kyang bag chags 'khrul pa'i dbang gis
NK050(wi)001:2442: sngon med phyis med par 'dir med bzhin snang ba'i
NK050(wi)001:2443: 'khrul snang stong gzugs d+ha du ras myos pa'i mig
NK050(wi)001:2444: la skra shad 'dzag pa sogs su snang ba bzhin
NK050(wi)001:2445: don la yod ma myong bas snang stong tha dad
NK050(wi)001:2446: du dbye ba'i gzhi thad la /
NK050(wi)001:2447: don dam rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i sku dang
NK050(wi)001:2448: ye shes sogs kyang zag pa med pa'i dbyings dang
NK050(wi)001:2449: so so ma yin tha mi dad par rang bzhin
NK050(wi)001:2450: ye nas mnyam pa nyid dus gsum 'pho 'gyur dang
NK050(wi)001:2451: bral bas na snang stong tha dad du dbyer med
NK050(wi)001:2452: pa'i phyir / blos btags pa'i bden pa gnyis kyang
NK050(wi)001:2453: ming tsam tshig tsam ste don la rang bzhin gyis
NK050(wi)001:2454: ma grub pa'i phyir dbyer med rnam dag chen po'i
NK050(wi)001:2455: srid zhi mnyam nyid du shes par bya ste /
NK050(wi)001:2456: kun rdzob rnam chad rnam dbye'i yul 'das pas //
NK050(wi)001:2457: btags pa'i bden gnyis 'das phyir spros kun zhi //
NK050(wi)001:2458: bden pa dbyer med grub dang ma grub med //
NK050(wi)001:2459: dbyings la snang stong rang bzhin gnyis med pas //
NK050(wi)001:2460: bden pa de yang dbyer med ces su brjod //
NK050(wi)001:2462: 'di la tha snyad pa'i kun tu tshad ma la
NK050(wi)001:2463: brten nas gnas snang gi dbang gis bden pa gnyis
NK050(wi)001:2464: su bzhag na / 'di ltar 'khrul snang 'khor ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK050(wi)001:2465: mi bden bslu phyir kun rdzob bden pa lags //
NK050(wi)001:2466: zab zhi 'od gsal mya ngan 'das pa'i chos //
NK050(wi)001:2467: 'gyur med rang bzhin don dam bden par 'dod //
NK050(wi)001:2469: gong du smos pa'i bden gnyis dbyer med spros bral
NK050(wi)001:2470: mnyam pa chen por gtan la 'bebs pa nyid sngon
NK050(wi)001:2471: du btang nas / de lta bu'i gnas tshul dang
NK050(wi)001:2472: snang tshul kun nas mthun par gyur pa'i yul dang
NK050(wi)001:2473: yul can gnyis ka don dam dang /
NK050(wi)001:2474: gnas snang ma mthun pa'i yul yul can gnyis ka kun rdzob tu bzhag ste /
NK050(wi)001:2475: 'di ni tha snyad du bslu mi slu'i dbang gis de ltar 'jog dgos te /
NK050(wi)001:2476: de ltar ma yin na dung dkar 'dzin dang ser
NK050(wi)001:2477: 'dzin gnyis la'ang bden rdzun du bzhag mi shes pas
NK050(wi)001:2478: tha snyad kyi rnam bzhag thams cad 'khrugs par 'gyur
NK050(wi)001:2479: bas so // des na gnas snang mthun pa'i stobs
NK050(wi)001:2480: kyis thob pa'i myang 'das kyi chos thams cad don
NK050(wi)001:2481: bas so // dam yin la / mi mthun pa'i
NK050(wi)001:2482: stobs kyis byung ba'i 'khor ba'i chos thams cad kun
NK050(wi)001:2483: rdzob tu bzhag tu rung ste /
NK050(wi)001:2484: tha dpyod kyis dpyad na sku dang ye shes kyi
NK050(wi)001:2485: snang ba thams cad las nyon 'khrul pas bskyed pa
NK050(wi)001:2486: min zhing / yang dag pa'i ye shes kyi dbang las byung ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:2487: sgrib pas bslad ma zhugs pa'i phyir bden zhing mi bslu bar grub bo //
NK050(wi)001:2488: 'khor ba'i chos rnams ni de las ldog pas bden par ma grub ces bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:2489: 'di'i bden mi bden ni mi bslu ba dang bslu
NK050(wi)001:2490: bar tha snyad dpyod byed kyi tshad mas grub pa
NK050(wi)001:2491: yin no // de lta na gnas snang mthun par
NK050(wi)001:2492: gyur pa'i yul can la ye shes zhes bya ste
NK050(wi)001:2494: mi mthun par 'dzin pa la rnam shes zhes bya ste gzung 'dzin can no //
NK050(wi)001:2495: gnas snang mthun pa'i yul la tshad ma'i gnod pa
NK050(wi)001:2496: bstan pas nam yang ldog byed med pas brtan pa
NK050(wi)001:2497: 'jig rten pa'i dper byas na thag pa la thag
NK050(wi)001:2499: gnas snang mi mthun pa'i yul la tshad mas gnod
NK050(wi)001:2500: pa mthong na ldog ste thag pa la sbrul 'dzin
NK050(wi)001:2501: gyi blo bzhin mi brtan no //
NK050(wi)001:2502: des na blo gros mi zad pa'i mdor /
NK050(wi)001:2504: rnam shes ni mi rtag gsungs pa'i don yang de yin no //
NK050(wi)001:2505: de'i phyir dbyings dang gnyis su med pa'i ye shes
NK050(wi)001:2506: 'di chos nyid dang tha dad med pa'i dbang gis
NK050(wi)001:2509: 'jig rten khams mang la la dag /
NK050(wi)001:2510: bsam gyis mi khyab tshig gyur kyang //
NK050(wi)001:2512: rang byung ye shes de yin no //
NK050(wi)001:2514: spros bral don gsal chen po'i rgyud las /
NK050(wi)001:2515: ngas bstan rgyud lung thams cad du //
NK050(wi)001:2517: rdo rje lta bu'i tshig brjod na //
NK050(wi)001:2518: rang byung ye shes chen por bshad //
NK050(wi)001:2521: ji ltar bum pa zhig gyur kyang //
NK050(wi)001:2522: nam mkha' la ni 'jig pa med //
NK050(wi)001:2523: de bzhin sems ni zhig gyur kyang //
NK050(wi)001:2524: ye shes la ni 'jig pa med //
NK050(wi)001:2527: ji ltar me yis dag pa'i gos //
NK050(wi)001:2528: sna tshogs dri mas dri ma can //
NK050(wi)001:2529: ji ltar me yi nang bcug na //
NK050(wi)001:2530: dri ma tshig gyur gos min ltar //
NK050(wi)001:2531: de bzhin 'od gsal ba yis sems //
NK050(wi)001:2532: 'dod chags la sogs dri ma can //
NK050(wi)001:2533: ye shes me yis dri ma bsreg /
NK050(wi)001:2534: de nyid 'od gsal ma yin no //
NK050(wi)001:2536: 'di chos can ltos nas skye 'gags ltar snang na yang /
NK050(wi)001:2537: de rnam shes 'khrul pa can la snang tshul yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:2538: des chos nyid ma 'khrul ba'i gshis lugs don dam pa'i gnod mi nus te /
NK050(wi)001:2539: dper na snod kyi dbang gis nam mkha' 'phel 'grib ltar snang yang /
NK050(wi)001:2540: des nam mkha' 'dus byas dang mi rtag par sgrib mi nus pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:2541: de lta bu'i chos nyid dam ye shes rang gi ngo bo la /
NK050(wi)001:2542: ye nas nyes pa'i rdul gyis ma gos pas gtsang ba /
NK050(wi)001:2543: rang bzhin 'pho 'gyur med pas rtag pa /
NK050(wi)001:2544: nam yang sdug bsngal gyis zil gyis mi non pas bde bas /
NK050(wi)001:2545: 'khor 'das kun la khyab cing bdag bdag med kyi
NK050(wi)001:2546: spros pa nye bar zhi bas dam pa'i bdag ste
NK050(wi)001:2547: / tshur mthong byis blo'i yul las pha rol bskal
NK050(wi)001:2548: don du gyur pa'i yon tan gyi chos bzhi dang
NK050(wi)001:2549: / ldan te / mgon po byams pas rgyud bla mar /
NK050(wi)001:2550: gtsang bdag bde ba rtag nyid phyir /
NK050(wi)001:2551: yon tan pha rol phyin pa 'bras /
NK050(wi)001:2554: rang bzhin gyis dag dag pa'i bdag /
NK050(wi)001:2555: thog ma med nas spros med bdag /
NK050(wi)001:2557: der ma zad chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK050(wi)001:2558: dag pa'i dbang gis de las shar ba'i chos can
NK050(wi)001:2559: phung khams skye mched kyis bsdus pa'i phyi nang gi
NK050(wi)001:2561: gnas tshul mthar thug pa'i dbang du byas na sku
NK050(wi)001:2562: dang ye shes kyi ngo bor ye nas sangs rgyas
NK050(wi)001:2563: pa'i rang bzhin mnyam pa nyid las mi g.yos te
NK050(wi)001:2564: / mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi spyan sgrib pa thams cad dang bral bas de ltar gzigs pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:2566: gang zhig bdag dang sems can rnams //
NK050(wi)001:2567: rang bzhin mnyam par rab gnas shing //
NK050(wi)001:2568: mi gnas len pa med pa de //
NK050(wi)001:2569: de dag bde bar gshegs pa'i gsungs //
NK050(wi)001:2570: gzugs dang tshor ba 'du shes dang //
NK050(wi)001:2571: rnam par shes dang sems dpa' dag /
NK050(wi)001:2572: grangs med de bzhin gshegs pa rnams //
NK050(wi)001:2573: de dag thub pa chen por 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:2576: mdor na phung po lnga rnams ni /
NK050(wi)001:2577: sangs rgyas lnga ni rab tu grags //
NK050(wi)001:2578: rdo rje'i skye mched rnam nyid ni //
NK050(wi)001:2579: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK050(wi)001:2582: 'gro ba 'di kun sangs rgyas lnga'i bdag nyid //
NK050(wi)001:2585: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas yin te sangs rgyas
NK050(wi)001:2586: chen po gzhan 'dir 'jig rten khams na yod ma
NK050(wi)001:2589: e ma ho phyogs bcu stong khams ye nas dben //
NK050(wi)001:2590: srid pa gsum ni dag pa'i zhing //
NK050(wi)001:2591: snyigs ma lnga nyid bde ldan gnas //
NK050(wi)001:2592: phung po lnga nyid rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK050(wi)001:2593: thams cad mchog gi snying po bas //
NK050(wi)001:2594: gzhan du rgyal bas chos mi btsal //
NK050(wi)001:2595: nyid las gzhan zhes bya ba'i chos //
NK050(wi)001:2596: btsal yang rgyal bas mi brnyes so //
NK050(wi)001:2598: 'o na sangs rgyas kyis phung sogs sdug kun gyi mtshan gzhir yang ma gsungs sam snyam na /
NK050(wi)001:2599: de ni dgos pa'i dbang gis te /
NK050(wi)001:2601: bdag go zhes kyang bstan gyur la //
NK050(wi)001:2602: bdag med ces kyang bstan par gyur //
NK050(wi)001:2603: rgyal ba rnams kyis dag dang ni //
NK050(wi)001:2604: bdag med 'ga' med ces kyang bstan //
NK050(wi)001:2606: sangs rgyas la bdag rtog med kyang nga dang nga
NK050(wi)001:2607: yir gsungs pa 'jig rten mthun 'jug yin pa dang
NK050(wi)001:2608: / nga bdag med kyang byis pa'i ngor yod pa
NK050(wi)001:2609: ltar gzigs pa mi 'gal ba theg chen spyi la
NK050(wi)001:2611: snang srid sku dang ye shes su gzigs kyang /
NK050(wi)001:2612: sems can ma dag pa'i 'khrul ngor sdug kun ltar
NK050(wi)001:2613: snang ba mi khegs pas de ltar gzigs nas tshul
NK050(wi)001:2614: de bzhin bstan pa mi 'gal lo //
NK050(wi)001:2615: de bzhin du sems can sangs rgyas yin na sems
NK050(wi)001:2616: can dmyal bar sdug bsngal tshe sangs rgyas la sdug
NK050(wi)001:2617: bsngal yod pa thal ba sogs kyang mi 'grub ste
NK050(wi)001:2618: / don dam par 'khor ba ma grub /
NK050(wi)001:2619: kun rdzob snang tshul du der skyes pa de sgrib pa dag zin gyi sangs rgyas ma yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:2620: rang rgyud ldan gyi sgrib pa'i dbang gis 'khrul snang
NK050(wi)001:2621: rmi lam lta bur myong ba yin pa'i phyir skyon
NK050(wi)001:2622: med la / gnas tshul du sdug bsngal sogs ma grub ste /
NK050(wi)001:2624: yang dag shes pa'i rang rig blo med na //
NK050(wi)001:2625: bde gshegs zhing yang ngan song gnas su mthong //
NK050(wi)001:2626: theg mchog mnyam pa'i don nyid rtogs pa ni //
NK050(wi)001:2627: ngan song gnas nyid 'og min dga' ldan gnas //
NK050(wi)001:2629: des na ma dag 'khor ba'i snang ba thams cad
NK050(wi)001:2630: 'khrul snang yin pas de'i ngor snang ba ltar min
NK050(wi)001:2631: la / dag pa myang 'das kyi sku dang ye
NK050(wi)001:2632: shes sogs kyi snang ba thams cad ma 'khrul pa
NK050(wi)001:2633: la / yin pas / 'di gnyis kho nas tha snyad tshad ma'i sgrub tshul shes par bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:2634: de yang dmyal sogs ma dag pa'i 'khor ba'i snang
NK050(wi)001:2635: ba 'di thams cad sems sdig pa can gyi dbang
NK050(wi)001:2636: gis rang rang gi 'khrul ngor snang ba ni /
NK050(wi)001:2638: lcags bsreg sa gzhi su yis byas //
NK050(wi)001:2639: me tshogs 'di dag ci las byung //
NK050(wi)001:2640: de phyir de dag thams cad ni //
NK050(wi)001:2641: sdigs sems yin par thub pas gsungs //
NK050(wi)001:2643: dag pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing sku'i bkod pa sogs
NK050(wi)001:2644: ni rang sems dag pa'i dbang gis snang ba yin
NK050(wi)001:2645: par mdo rgyud dgongs pa mthun zhing /
NK050(wi)001:2646: tshangs pa ral pa can dang sh+aa ri'i bu gnyis
NK050(wi)001:2647: zhing 'di dag ma dag tu rtsod pas kyang shes
NK050(wi)001:2648: nus la / khyad par sngags bla med kyi rgyud
NK050(wi)001:2649: sde rnams su nang gi rtsa rlung gi thig le'i
NK050(wi)001:2650: khams dang sems nyid dag ma dag gis byung bar
NK050(wi)001:2652: des na chos thams cad rang sems kyi rtog pas
NK050(wi)001:2653: phar btags pa tsam las don la grub pa med
NK050(wi)001:2654: kyang / rtog btags kyi yul de nyid rang rang
NK050(wi)001:2655: gi blo ngor gnas skabs rten 'byung gis dbang gi
NK050(wi)001:2656: snang ba bslu med nyid la tha snyad tshad grub
NK050(wi)001:2657: kyang / ces bya ste / las mthun par bsags
NK050(wi)001:2658: shing bag chags mthun par sad pa'i da lta rang
NK050(wi)001:2659: re mi lta bu la me nyid tsha bar snang
NK050(wi)001:2660: ba 'di tshad mas grub pas sus kyang me tsha
NK050(wi)001:2661: ba min zhes smyon du med la /
NK050(wi)001:2662: de bzhin dge sdig sogs kyang 'dra /
NK050(wi)001:2663: don dam par de ltar mtha' gcig tu chad pa ni med de /
NK050(wi)001:2664: ri dwags me yi gtsang sbra can sogs la me tsha bar mi snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK050(wi)001:2665: dbang thob pa rnams kyis dngos po sprul bsgyur sna tshogs par ston nus pas shes la /
NK050(wi)001:2667: dngos gcig yid ni tha dad phyir //
NK050(wi)001:2668: don ma grub par snang ba yin //
NK050(wi)001:2670: rang gi lus gcig pu 'di la'ang /
NK050(wi)001:2672: phyi rol gyi bya rgod dang /
NK050(wi)001:2675: rang gzhan dgra gnyen sogs du mas bltas na /
NK050(wi)001:2684: bar ma sogs mthong tshul dang 'dzin tshul tha dad pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2685: 'phags pa rnams kyis gzigs na lus rang bzhin gyis grub pa med pa sogs dang /
NK050(wi)001:2686: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sar gzugs phung dag pa
NK050(wi)001:2687: rnam snang gi ngo bor gsungs pa rnams de ltar
NK050(wi)001:2688: smyon med du grub pa yin zhing /
NK050(wi)001:2689: de yang legs par brtags na lus zhes pa'ang btsal
NK050(wi)001:2690: na mi dmigs shing rdul phra rab tsam du'ang grub
NK050(wi)001:2691: pa med pa ni da ltar yang dpyad pa gnad
NK050(wi)001:2692: du song bas shes nus pa 'di'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:2693: de nyid gzhan gyi lus sogs phyi nang gi chos
NK050(wi)001:2694: thams cad la sbyar bas rang bzhin med par gtan
NK050(wi)001:2696: don dam par de thams cad kyang rang bzhin gyis
NK050(wi)001:2697: dbye bsal med par chos nyid mnyam pa chen pos
NK050(wi)001:2698: shes dgos kyang / tha snyad du ni da lta
NK050(wi)001:2699: sems can phal pa la snang ba ni ma dag
NK050(wi)001:2700: 'khrul pa'i snang ba yin pas de'i ngor snang ba
NK050(wi)001:2702: lam byang sems kyi snang ba'ang da dung gong nas
NK050(wi)001:2703: gong du mthong ba rnam par dag rgya yod pa'i
NK050(wi)001:2704: phyir de'i ngor dbang btsan du min la /
NK050(wi)001:2705: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sa'i gzigs pa las gong
NK050(wi)001:2706: du bogs dbyung du med pa'i phyir gnas tshul mthar
NK050(wi)001:2707: thug par grub pas de ltar nges par bya ste
NK050(wi)001:2708: / mdor na brjod mtha' brjod bral /
NK050(wi)001:2710: rnam shes kyi mtha' ye shes /
NK050(wi)001:2711: chos can gyi mtha' chos nyid la thug pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:2712: rtogs tshogs lhar dag ye shes su dag /
NK050(wi)001:2713: ye shes ni gzung 'dzin mtshan ma'i spyod yul las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:2714: rang bzhin gnyug pa'am sgrib bral gyi phung khams skye
NK050(wi)001:2715: mched rnams ni gdod ma nas chos kyi dbyings dang
NK050(wi)001:2716: tha mi dad pa'i phyir rang bzhin rnam dag chen
NK050(wi)001:2718: 'o na lam sgom pa la don med do snyam na ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:2719: sems can rnams kyis de ltar ma rtogs pa'i dbang
NK050(wi)001:2720: gis 'khrul snang rmi lam lta bu 'di glo bur
NK050(wi)001:2721: du byung zhing de ltar zhen pa'i 'khrul rtog gi
NK050(wi)001:2722: bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir bskyed rdzogs sogs kyi lam
NK050(wi)001:2723: bsgom pa ste / des na lam dang 'bras bu'i
NK050(wi)001:2724: chos rnams la bden par zhen pas ni ma yin
NK050(wi)001:2725: bsgom pa ste / te / sgyu ma mkhan gyis
NK050(wi)001:2726: sprul pa'i dmag gis lam gyi 'jigs pa sel bar
NK050(wi)001:2727: byed pa'am bad kan can gyi mig nad sbyong ba
NK050(wi)001:2728: bsgom pa ste / te / bzhin no // de'i
NK050(wi)001:2729: phyir rtogs bya mthar thug pa'i dbang du byas na
NK050(wi)001:2730: bsgom pa ste / te / bzhin no // /
NK050(wi)001:2731: kun rdzob dang don dam gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK050(wi)001:2732: cad rang bzhin dbyer med par ye nas sangs rgyas
NK050(wi)001:2733: pa'i rang bzhin spros bral dag mnyam chen por gtan
NK050(wi)001:2735: tshur mthong gi byis blos phyogs rer gzhal ba'i yod
NK050(wi)001:2736: med snang stong dag ma dag sogs gnyis chos kyi
NK050(wi)001:2737: spros pa gang gi phyogs su'ang zhen cing lhung bar
NK050(wi)001:2740: gang zag la mi rton chos la rton /
NK050(wi)001:2741: tshig la mi rton don la rton /
NK050(wi)001:2742: drang don la mi rton nges don la rton /
NK050(wi)001:2743: rnam shes la mi rton ye shes la rton par gsungs pa bzhin /
NK050(wi)001:2744: shes bya bden gnyis kyi tshul la phyin ci ma
NK050(wi)001:2745: log par lung rigs man ngag tshad mas gzhal 'bras
NK050(wi)001:2748: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab mdo rgyud kyi dgongs
NK050(wi)001:2749: pa mtha' dag snying po gcig tu bsdu shes dgos
NK050(wi)001:2750: pas / mtshan nyid rgyu'i theg pa'i grub mtha'i rtse mo ni /
NK050(wi)001:2751: bka' 'khor bar tha gnyis ka'i nges don gyi bcud
NK050(wi)001:2752: bsdus pa rgyud bla sogs byams gzhung dang 'phags pa
NK050(wi)001:2753: klus bstod tshogs sogs nas bstan don theg mchog dbu
NK050(wi)001:2754: ma chen po nyid yin la /
NK050(wi)001:2755: 'bras bu sngags kyi skyel so mthar thug 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:2756: de gnyis don gyi dgongs pa gnad gcig tu 'babs pa'i tshul yang /
NK050(wi)001:2758: chos lnga rang bzhin gsum dang ni //
NK050(wi)001:2759: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad dang //
NK050(wi)001:2760: bdag med don ni rnam gnyis por //
NK050(wi)001:2761: theg chen mtha' dag bsdus pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:2765: yongs su brtags pa'i gzugs gang yin pa de ni rdzas med par blta'o //
NK050(wi)001:2766: rnam par brtags pa'i gzugs gang yin pa de rnam
NK050(wi)001:2767: par rtogs pa'i rdzas yod par blta yi rang dbang
NK050(wi)001:2768: du 'jug pa ni ma yin no //
NK050(wi)001:2769: chos nyid kyi gzugs gang yin pa de ni rdzas med pa'ang ma yin /
NK050(wi)001:2771: don dam pas rab tu phye ba yin par blta bar bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:2773: chos thams cad rang bzhin gsum du gtan la phabs pa las /
NK050(wi)001:2774: yongs grub chos dbyings 'gyur med bde gshegs snying po'i rang bzhin /
NK050(wi)001:2777: mkhyen cha stobs sogs sangs rgyas kyi chos gang+g+aa'i klung
NK050(wi)001:2778: gi bye ma'i grangs las 'das pa dang rnam dbyer
NK050(wi)001:2780: rdzogs chen gyi ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum
NK050(wi)001:2781: dbyer med pa'i gzhi gnas kyi ye shes sku gsum
NK050(wi)001:2782: rang chas su yod par gsungs pa dang don gcig
NK050(wi)001:2783: / dag ma dag gi rten 'byung gzhan dbang sgyu ma lta bu ni /
NK050(wi)001:2784: gzhi snang lhun grub kyi rtsal las grol 'khrul gyi
NK050(wi)001:2785: sgo gnyis gsungs pa'i shin tu phra ba'i rten 'byung
NK050(wi)001:2786: gi rtsa bar don gyi gnad thug /
NK050(wi)001:2787: yang dag pa ma yin pa'i kun rtog rtsa ba
NK050(wi)001:2788: bdag gnyis su 'dzin pa dang des bskyed pa'i 'khrul
NK050(wi)001:2789: snang 'khrul 'dzin dang bcas pa ma dag gzhan dbang
NK050(wi)001:2790: 'khor ba'i chos rnams ni skra shad dang zla ba
NK050(wi)001:2791: gnyis snang bzhin gzhi rtsa med pas don la yod
NK050(wi)001:2792: ma myong bas mtshan nyid chad pa'am med pa yin
NK050(wi)001:2793: la / de lta bu'i 'khrul gzhi 'khrul 'dzin dang
NK050(wi)001:2794: bcas dbyings su dag pa'i stong gzhi rnam kun mchog
NK050(wi)001:2795: ldan gyi rang rtsal dag pa gzhan dbang sku dang
NK050(wi)001:2796: ye shes sogs gdod ma gzhi yi gnas lugs chos
NK050(wi)001:2797: nyid mnyam pa chen po las tha mi dad pa'i
NK050(wi)001:2798: phyir mthar thug ka dag gi grol sa dngos yin
NK050(wi)001:2799: la / pa dang / lam nyams su len tshul yang /
NK050(wi)001:2800: yang dag pa'i gnas lugs bsal bzhag 'ching grol las
NK050(wi)001:2801: 'das pa'i don gnyis gtan la phab nas de'i ngang
NK050(wi)001:2802: goms par byed pa la mthun pa yin te /
NK050(wi)001:2803: rgyal ba'i sras po gzhan phan mtha' yas kyis //
NK050(wi)001:2804: byon dang 'byon gyur rgyal kun kyis //
NK050(wi)001:2805: bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam yin phyir //
NK050(wi)001:2806: rgyal sras thu bo mchog rnams kyang //
NK050(wi)001:2807: gcig tu brtson pas rang gir mdzad //
NK050(wi)001:2808: des na bdag gzhan mnyam barje yi //
NK050(wi)001:2809: rim par smon 'jug sems sbyangs nas //
NK050(wi)001:2810: myur lam sngags kyi man ngag la //
NK050(wi)001:2811: brten nas nyams su len pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:2812: khyad par don dam byang chub sems //
NK050(wi)001:2813: sgom pa'i rim pa sems phyogs kyi //
NK050(wi)001:2814: tan+t+ra rnams su thub dbang gis //
NK050(wi)001:2815: ji ltar gsungs bzhin bsgom par bya //
NK050(wi)001:2816: 'di yi nges pa'ang sems kyi gsang //
NK050(wi)001:2817: rang bzhin gyis ni 'od gsal ba //
NK050(wi)001:2818: gang la snang stong phyogs gnyis kyis //
NK050(wi)001:2819: ka dag lhun grub ces brjod yin //
NK050(wi)001:2820: der yang chos can chos nyid dang //
NK050(wi)001:2821: zung du 'jug pa'i dbye ba yis //
NK050(wi)001:2822: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje zhes //
NK050(wi)001:2823: gzhi gnas ye shes gsum dang ni //
NK050(wi)001:2824: de dag re rer ngo bo dang //
NK050(wi)001:2825: gdangs dang rtsal nas rnam dbye ba'i //
NK050(wi)001:2826: sku gsum ngo sprod der yang ni //
NK050(wi)001:2827: gzhi lam 'bras dus gsum gyis dbye //
NK050(wi)001:2828: de las ye gzhi chos kyi dbyings //
NK050(wi)001:2829: spros dang bral ba'i ka dag yin //
NK050(wi)001:2830: spyi gzhi rten 'byung sgyu ma la //
NK050(wi)001:2831: gzhi snang chen por ngo sprod mdzad //
NK050(wi)001:2832: gang la rnal 'byor spyod gzhung las //
NK050(wi)001:2833: ngo bo nyid rnam 'byed pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:2834: sdug dang mi sdug rnam 'byed pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:2836: tshul 'di legs par shes gyur na //
NK050(wi)001:2837: phar phyin theg pa'i zab gnad kun //
NK050(wi)001:2839: nang 'gal spros pa kun chod gyur //
NK050(wi)001:2840: de phyir kun brtag gzhan dbang dang //
NK050(wi)001:2841: yongs su grub par gang brjod pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:2842: mtshan nyid gsum gyi rnam bzhag der //
NK050(wi)001:2843: phan tshun sbyor bas don 'di rtogs //
NK050(wi)001:2844: gang phyir dbu ma'i gzhung las kyang //
NK050(wi)001:2845: tha snyad la ni ma brten par //
NK050(wi)001:2846: dam pa'i don ni rtogs min zhes //
NK050(wi)001:2847: de yi sgrub pa'ang gsungs bar mdzad //
NK050(wi)001:2848: 'di las mtshan nyid gsum gyi gnad //
NK050(wi)001:2849: mtha' dag rgyal tshab ma pham pas //
NK050(wi)001:2850: legs par bshad dang mthun pa ru //
NK050(wi)001:2851: gsungs las rnam bzhag log pa med //
NK050(wi)001:2852: de yang rgyal ba'i yum nyid las //
NK050(wi)001:2853: gzugs sogs chos rnams mtha' dag la //
NK050(wi)001:2854: chos nyid dang ni kun brtag dang //
NK050(wi)001:2855: rnam par brtags pas gsum gsum du //
NK050(wi)001:2856: dbye ba'i don 'di nyid yin phyir //
NK050(wi)001:2857: yum don tshad mar 'dzin rnams kyang //
NK050(wi)001:2858: tha snyad rnam bzhag 'di las gzhan //
NK050(wi)001:2859: byas na don las ring bar 'gyur /
NK050(wi)001:2860: 'on te bden pa'i rnam bzhag la //
NK050(wi)001:2861: phyi ma nyid ni phyi ma dang //
NK050(wi)001:2862: gzhan gnyis gzhan du bzhag pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:2863: skabs 'di'i tshul la phal cher rtsod //
NK050(wi)001:2864: de phyir dbu ma pa rnams la //
NK050(wi)001:2865: kun rdzob 'jog tshul mtshungs min las //
NK050(wi)001:2866: don dam bden pa spros bral du //
NK050(wi)001:2867: 'chad la rnam dbye yod ma yin //
NK050(wi)001:2868: gal te don dam spros bral las //
NK050(wi)001:2869: gzhan yod na ni ltos bzhag phyir //
NK050(wi)001:2870: gcig de dbu ma'i nyid yin na //
NK050(wi)001:2871: de tshe gzhan de mthar ltar 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:2872: mdor na thub pa'i gsungs rabs kun //
NK050(wi)001:2873: snga ma'i sbas don phyi ma yis //
NK050(wi)001:2874: gsal bar bshad pa nyid yin pas //
NK050(wi)001:2875: gsal bar bshad pa nyid yin pas //
NK050(wi)001:2876: theg pa mtho dman ji snyed kyang //
NK050(wi)001:2877: gzhung dang man ngag sbas don gyi //
NK050(wi)001:2878: rnam par bzhag las gzhan med phyir //
NK050(wi)001:2879: dngos bstan don la khyad che yang //
NK050(wi)001:2880: mthar thug don la khyad yod min //
NK050(wi)001:2881: de slad 'phags yul mkhas pa'i gzhung //
NK050(wi)001:2882: la lar khyad cher gsungs pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:2883: gzhan du khyad par med bshad pa //
NK050(wi)001:2884: kun gyi dgongs gzhi 'di yin yang //
NK050(wi)001:2886: rnam dbye legs par ma phyed bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:2887: rang phyogs bsgrub cing gzhan gyis phyogs //
NK050(wi)001:2888: dgag la khyad chos yin par rloms //
NK050(wi)001:2889: de bzhin bde dang grub mtha' dang //
NK050(wi)001:2890: sngags kyi rim gnyis dbye bsdu sogs //
NK050(wi)001:2891: legs par khong du ma chud bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:2892: dgag sgrub bgyis pa du ma mthong //
NK050(wi)001:2893: des na tshig la mi rton par //
NK050(wi)001:2894: don la rton pa'i man ngag gis //
NK050(wi)001:2895: thub gsungs mtha' dag 'gal med du //
NK050(wi)001:2896: sgrub pa'i tshul 'di mkhyen par mdzod //
NK050(wi)001:2897: ces rje nyid kyi rigs kyi bdag po gcig pu
NK050(wi)001:2898: grub dbang byang chub rdo rje'i yang srid rin po
NK050(wi)001:2899: cher mdo rgyud dgongs pa'i zab gnad tha dag snying
NK050(wi)001:2900: por bsdus te thugs bcud gsang ba zab mo nyid
NK050(wi)001:2901: gdams par mdzad pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:2902: de ltar legs par gtan la phebs nas gnas tshul dang mthun par lam nyams su len pa la'ang /
