NK050(wi)001:2904: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa chen por sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rgyu tsam du bzung nas /
NK050(wi)001:2905: 'bras bu sangs rgyas nyid gdod thob par bya ba'i slad du /
NK050(wi)001:2906: rigs dang bshes gnyen gyi stobs las /
NK050(wi)001:2908: mos bsngo yi rang sogs thabs la mkhas pas phar
NK050(wi)001:2909: phyin drug sogs tshogs gnyis zung 'brel gyi lam la
NK050(wi)001:2910: slob par byed pa yin la /
NK050(wi)001:2911: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg par ni /
NK050(wi)001:2912: sems nyid da lta nas sangs rgyas kyi ngo bor gnas pa nyid dbang gis smin par byas te /
NK050(wi)001:2913: dam tshig rnam par dag pas rgyud bsdams nas /
NK050(wi)001:2914: gnas tshul yang dag dang mthun par bskyed rdzogs kyi lam bsgom pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:2916: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa yis //
NK050(wi)001:2917: sems can sangs rgyas rgyu ru shes //
NK050(wi)001:2918: 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa yis //
NK050(wi)001:2919: sems nyid sangs rgyas nyid du bsgom //
NK050(wi)001:2921: sngags la'ang bya spyod sogs phyi rgyud rnams su /
NK050(wi)001:2922: sngar mdo las bshad pa'i bden gnyis dbyer med la nges shes cher song bas /
NK050(wi)001:2923: don dam par bdag dang lha gnyis tha dad du ma grub kyang /
NK050(wi)001:2924: kun rdzob tu yongs su dag pa'i lha dang gnyis rje khol lam spun grogs sogs su bltas te /
NK050(wi)001:2925: sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma ci rig pa yid la byed cing sgrub pas /
NK050(wi)001:2926: bdag gi rgyud byin gyis rlob cing dngos grub gnyis
NK050(wi)001:2927: thob par byed pa'i nges shes khyad par can gyi
NK050(wi)001:2928: lta ba la brten pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:2929: de yang kun gzigs rong pas phyag na rdo rje
NK050(wi)001:2930: dbang bskur ba'i tan+t+ra las ji skad bstan pa'i don
NK050(wi)001:2931: / gsang sngags kyi skabs 'dir tha mal gyi mngon rjes las 'das pa'i /
NK050(wi)001:2932: yid ches pa'i lung dang man ngag dam pa la
NK050(wi)001:2933: brten te skyes pa'i so sor rtog pa'i shes rab
NK050(wi)001:2935: phan tshun la ltos pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:2937: chos nyid kyi rigs pa rnams dang mi 'gal ba'i kun mkhyen gyi tshad ma gsum gsungs te /
NK050(wi)001:2938: de yang chos nyid rtogs par bya ba'i phyir thabs
NK050(wi)001:2939: kyi mtshan ma sna tshogs su brtags pa rnams la
NK050(wi)001:2940: ni rnam par smin pa'i lha zhes bya /
NK050(wi)001:2941: chos nyid rtogs pa ni 'bras bu'i ngo bo'i lha zhes bya ste /
NK050(wi)001:2942: chos nyid dang chos nyid thob par byed pa la
NK050(wi)001:2943: mi bslu ba thams cad ni tshad mar grub pas
NK050(wi)001:2944: / sku gsung thugs su sbyor ba'i dam tshig gis /
NK050(wi)001:2945: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub grub par byed pa
NK050(wi)001:2946: 'di yang rten cing 'brel te 'byung ba yin pa'i
NK050(wi)001:2947: phyir chos nyid kyi chos nyid ston par byed pa
NK050(wi)001:2948: yin no // de ltar nges par byas nas /
NK050(wi)001:2949: 'jug pa'i sgo chu dbang sogs kyis smin par byas te /
NK050(wi)001:2950: spyod pa khrus dang gtsang sbrar gnas shing /
NK050(wi)001:2954: bsam gtan gyi de kho na nyid sogs la brten te /
NK050(wi)001:2955: bdag gi sgo gsum dag pa la /
NK050(wi)001:2956: dag pa lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan mas rgyas btab ste bsgoms shing sgrub pas /
NK050(wi)001:2957: thun mong gi grub pa 'dod gzugs kyi rig 'dzin sogs dang /
NK050(wi)001:2958: thun mong ma yin pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK050(wi)001:2959: mi tshe bcu drug gam bdun sogs nas lcags la
NK050(wi)001:2960: gser 'gyur gyi rtsis thebs pa bzhin du /
NK050(wi)001:2961: rigs gsum rigs bzhi sogs rigs kyi gtso bo gang
NK050(wi)001:2962: yin pa dang gnyis su med par byang chub par
NK050(wi)001:2963: byed pa ni rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i dbang
NK050(wi)001:2965: dper na rtsub bstan brten nas su //
NK050(wi)001:2966: gtsub shing tsub par byed gyur na //
NK050(wi)001:2967: mi yi rtsol ba byed rgyu las //
NK050(wi)001:2968: stobs dang ldan pa'i me 'byung ngo //
NK050(wi)001:2969: de bzhin sngags dang phyag rgya lta //
NK050(wi)001:2970: gsum ni 'dus par gyur pa las //
NK050(wi)001:2972: byung bas yid la gang bsam pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:2973: las rnams byed par 'gyur ba yin //
NK050(wi)001:2975: 'di la mthar phyin 'bras bu'i ye shes nyid kyi
NK050(wi)001:2976: tshul du shar ba ci rigs pa lam du byed
NK050(wi)001:2977: pa'i cha nas 'bras bu lam byed kyi tshul yod
NK050(wi)001:2978: pas mdo lam las 'phags shing myur lam yin no
NK050(wi)001:2979: // thabs kyi theg pa'am sngags bla med nang rgyud sde gsum du ni /
NK050(wi)001:2980: de las kyang mnyam pa chen po'i don la nges shes khyad par du gyur pas /
NK050(wi)001:2981: don dam du ma zad kun rdzub tu'ang mi gnyis pa'i bsam spyod dang ldan pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:2982: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dag mnyam bden pa
NK050(wi)001:2983: dbyer med blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa'i lhag pa'i
NK050(wi)001:2984: chos sku chen por ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang
NK050(wi)001:2985: bzhin du lta bas gtan la phabs nas /
NK050(wi)001:2987: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas pas /
NK050(wi)001:2988: gnas skabs bzhi'i 'khrul pa dag byed kyi lam bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug tu bsgoms shing /
NK050(wi)001:2989: spyod pa gang la'ang gtsang dme blang dor dgag sgrub dang bral bar lam du khyer ba ste /
NK050(wi)001:2990: mdor na mnyam pa chen po'i dgongs spyod kyis lam
NK050(wi)001:2991: dang 'bras bu'i chos kun la bzlas pas mthar 'bras
NK050(wi)001:2992: la tshe 'adi'am bar do sogs su sbyong bar byed
NK050(wi)001:2993: pa yin te / sgyu 'phrul lam rim las /
NK050(wi)001:2994: bla med theg pa'i nang du ni //
NK050(wi)001:2995: don dam du ni dbyer med la //
NK050(wi)001:2996: kun rdzob tu ni thams cad la //
NK050(wi)001:2997: dag dang ma dag gnyis kar 'dzin //
NK050(wi)001:2998: thabs kyi theg pa chen por ni //
NK050(wi)001:2999: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK050(wi)001:3000: kun rdzob tu'ang dbyer med de //
NK050(wi)001:3001: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK050(wi)001:3003: rdo rje gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK050(wi)001:3004: bla med sngags kyi dngos grub gang //
NK050(wi)001:3005: shin tu brtson pas gang sgrub pa //
NK050(wi)001:3006: tshe 'di nyid la sangs rgyas te //
NK050(wi)001:3007: gdul bya'i zhing du mdzad pa ston //
NK050(wi)001:3008: grangs med rdo rje 'chang rnams kyi //
NK050(wi)001:3009: zab mo'i lam mthar thug pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:3010: zhes sogs gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:3011: de la'ang bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gsum gyi //
NK050(wi)001:3012: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga pas ni /
NK050(wi)001:3013: sems nyid dbyings dang ye shes dang sku gsung thugs
NK050(wi)001:3014: yon tan phrin las te don dam dkor bdun ngo
NK050(wi)001:3015: bo nyid du lhun gyis grub par mnyam pa dang
NK050(wi)001:3016: / de las shar ba'i kun rdzob phung khams skye
NK050(wi)001:3017: mched sogs gsum yongs rdzogs lha yi 'khor lo dang
NK050(wi)001:3018: sku dang ye shes su ye nas rnam par dag
NK050(wi)001:3019: pas bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral bar
NK050(wi)001:3021: de yang nges don gyi mdo sde zab mo rnams
NK050(wi)001:3022: su ye shes kyis brgyan pa'i chos dbyings spros bral
NK050(wi)001:3024: de nyid thos bsam gyis don spyi gtan la 'bebs
NK050(wi)001:3025: pa tsam las da lta nas mngon du byar med
NK050(wi)001:3026: la / sngags su dbang dang rim pa gnyis kyi
NK050(wi)001:3027: mthu las skyes pa'i so so rang rig pa'i ye
NK050(wi)001:3028: shes sems byung sems pa'i mtshan nyid las 'das pa'i
NK050(wi)001:3029: yul can zab mos mngon sum rang thog tu 'bebs
NK050(wi)001:3030: pas khyad par shin tu che'o //
NK050(wi)001:3031: de'i tshul yang sgyu 'phrul rtsa rgyud las /
NK050(wi)001:3033: dag pa gsum mnyam pa bzhi /
NK050(wi)001:3034: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshig rnams su gsungs te /
NK050(wi)001:3036: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems dang ye shes
NK050(wi)001:3037: kyi rang snang tsam ste don dam par rtsa ba
NK050(wi)001:3038: rang byung gi ye shes su rgyu gcig pa dang
NK050(wi)001:3039: / de las shar ba'i kun rdzob kyi chos rnams kyang de'i ngang tshul las ma 'das pas /
NK050(wi)001:3040: dpe yig 'bru'i tshul gyis sku dang ye shes su snang ba dang //
NK050(wi)001:3041: bden pa de gnyis ngo bo dbyer med par phan
NK050(wi)001:3042: tshun gcig gi gcig byin gyis brlabs te ngo bo
NK050(wi)001:3043: tha mi dad par gnas pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:3044: de lta'i gnas lugs zab mo de tha snyad kyi
NK050(wi)001:3045: blos spyod yul dang bral bar rang rig pa'i ye
NK050(wi)001:3046: shes kyis mngon du byed pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:3048: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK050(wi)001:3049: byin gyis brlabs dang mngon sum pa //
NK050(wi)001:3050: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis //
NK050(wi)001:3051: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal por che //
NK050(wi)001:3055: bcud phung po lnga bde gshegs rigs la /
NK050(wi)001:3056: rgyud rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar ye nas rnam par dag pa yin te /
NK050(wi)001:3057: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing /
NK050(wi)001:3060: spros pa phyogs re chod pa rnam grangs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:3061: mtha' dag chod pa rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don
NK050(wi)001:3062: dam gnyis ka rang bzhin ma grub tsam gyis phye
NK050(wi)001:3063: bas don dam gnyis ka rang bzhin ma grub tsam
NK050(wi)001:3064: gyis phye bas don dam tsam du mnyam pa dang
NK050(wi)001:3065: / snang la don byed nus pa yang dag dang
NK050(wi)001:3066: don byed mi nus pa log pa'i kun rdzob gnyis
NK050(wi)001:3067: ka ngo bo snang tsam la brtags na dbyen pa'i
NK050(wi)001:3068: phyir kun rdzob tu mnyam pa ni thun mong gi
NK050(wi)001:3070: ye nas dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i gnas lugs yin pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:3071: rnam grangs pa dang rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don
NK050(wi)001:3072: dam gnyis ka'ang lhag pa'i don dam dkor bdun ngo
NK050(wi)001:3073: bo nyid du lhun gyis grub par mnyam pa dang
NK050(wi)001:3074: / yang dag dang log pa'i kun rdzob gnyis ka'ang
NK050(wi)001:3075: gnas tshul du ye nas dag pa'i phyir lhag pa'i
NK050(wi)001:3076: kun rdzob sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bor mnyam
NK050(wi)001:3077: pa ni lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis bcas bzhi ste
NK050(wi)001:3078: / / mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK050(wi)001:3079: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK050(wi)001:3082: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams snang lugs nas du mar snang yang /
NK050(wi)001:3083: gnas lugs bdag nyid chen po rang byung gi ye shes nyag gcig tu nges te /
NK050(wi)001:3084: mthar thug dpyod rigs kyis de ltar grub pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:3085: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang /
NK050(wi)001:3087: de ltar gnas tshul la dag pa rab 'byams lha yi 'khor lor ye gdod ma nas gnas kyang /
NK050(wi)001:3088: snang tshul 'khrul pa can la de ltar snang ma nus pas /
NK050(wi)001:3089: ji ltar mig nad can gyi mig gi skyon sbyong ba bzhin du /
NK050(wi)001:3090: 'khrul pa de sbyong bar byed pa'i thabs gtso bor
NK050(wi)001:3091: bskyed rim yan lag dang bcas pa sgom pa ni
NK050(wi)001:3092: rnal 'byor chen po'am ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs te
NK050(wi)001:3093: / de yang bsgom bya'i lha rdo rje sems dpa' lta bu de ni /
NK050(wi)001:3094: rdo rje stong pa nyid dang /
NK050(wi)001:3095: sems dpa' ye shes chen po zung du 'jug pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:3096: gong du smos pa'i gzhi 'bras ro gcig pa'am dbyer
NK050(wi)001:3097: med pa'i dbyings ye snang stong zung du 'jug pa'i
NK050(wi)001:3098: gnyug ma'i sems chos nyid mnyam pa nyid chen po
NK050(wi)001:3100: de ni rigs dang dkyil 'khor kun gyi spro gzhi ste /
NK050(wi)001:3101: de'i snang cha zag med kyi yon tan rnams su
NK050(wi)001:3102: gang 'dul mtshan ma rtags kyi phyag rgya rten dang
NK050(wi)001:3103: brten pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lor ye nas shar
NK050(wi)001:3105: de ltar rtogs pa'i nges shes kyi lta bas zin pas /
NK050(wi)001:3106: mar 'chi bar skye gsum gyi rtog pa dag cing /
NK050(wi)001:3107: yar sku gsum gyi 'bras bu gzhi la rdzogs pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:3108: lam gong ma'i smin byed du'ang 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:3109: gnas tshul yang dag pa'i don dang mthun par /
NK050(wi)001:3111: sgyu lus snying rje sgyu ma /
NK050(wi)001:3112: zung 'jug phyag rgya gcig spros sogs /
NK050(wi)001:3113: gsal brtan dag gsum tshang ba'i bskyed rim yan lag dang bcas pa la bslab pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:3114: 'di la bskyed rim gtso bor smos kyang gong smos
NK050(wi)001:3115: ltar lta dgongs thabs shes zab mos khyad par byas
NK050(wi)001:3116: pa'i phyir bskyed rdzogs zhes rim pa gnyis kyi zlas
NK050(wi)001:3117: drangs pa'i bskyed rim tsam ni ma yin te ngo
NK050(wi)001:3118: bo zung 'jug gi lha skur grub pa'i phyir don
NK050(wi)001:3119: la bskyed rdzogs dbyer med rdzogs rim gyi lha skur
NK050(wi)001:3120: 'gyur bas / 'di lta bu'i lam nges rdzogs mthar
NK050(wi)001:3121: phyin pa las zag med la dngos su sbyor nus
NK050(wi)001:3122: par rigs pa'i gnod byed med de ngo bo zung
NK050(wi)001:3123: 'jug gi lam du grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK050(wi)001:3124: 'dis sbyang bya tha mal 'khrul 'dzin gyi zhen rtog bag chags dang bcas dang sbyang nas /
NK050(wi)001:3125: sbyangs 'bras sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku rdo rje
NK050(wi)001:3126: dang mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes mngon du byed
NK050(wi)001:3127: pa yin te / sgyu 'phrul rngams glong las /
NK050(wi)001:3128: srid gsum ye nas dag pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK050(wi)001:3129: bdag tu rtog pa'i srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs kyis //
NK050(wi)001:3130: yun ring dus nas 'khyams pa'i 'gro ba rnams //
NK050(wi)001:3131: ye nas don gyi sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK050(wi)001:3132: rmongs pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba'i 'khor lor 'khyams //
NK050(wi)001:3133: log rtog nyid nas dngos med byang chub sems //
NK050(wi)001:3134: 'khrul 'khor nyid kyang mi zad rgyan du che /
NK050(wi)001:3135: snyig ma lnga nyid bde ldan gnas su dag /
NK050(wi)001:3136: phung po lnga nyid mngon par rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK050(wi)001:3137: srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs byang chub snying por gnas //
NK050(wi)001:3138: phyi nang snod bcud yab yum ngang du gsal //
NK050(wi)001:3141: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK050(wi)001:3142: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK050(wi)001:3143: skye mched khams rnams mang po kun //
NK050(wi)001:3144: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK050(wi)001:3145: sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma k+ai //
NK050(wi)001:3146: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK050(wi)001:3147: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK050(wi)001:3148: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK050(wi)001:3149: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK050(wi)001:3150: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i chos //
NK050(wi)001:3151: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi brnyes so //
NK050(wi)001:3153: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK050(wi)001:3154: thos bsam bsgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK050(wi)001:3155: rang byung kun dam lhun gyis grub //
NK050(wi)001:3156: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK050(wi)001:3157: 'da' bar mi mdzad dam tshig mchog /
NK050(wi)001:3158: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK050(wi)001:3159: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK050(wi)001:3160: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad du //
NK050(wi)001:3161: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:3162: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:3163: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK050(wi)001:3164: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas shing //
NK050(wi)001:3165: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK050(wi)001:3167: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK050(wi)001:3168: 'das dang da ltar byung ba yi //
NK050(wi)001:3169: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'a khor ma lus pa //
NK050(wi)001:3170: bsnyen nas sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK050(wi)001:3173: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK050(wi)001:3174: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:3175: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK050(wi)001:3176: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK050(wi)001:3177: btsal yang rgyal bas mi brnyes so //
NK050(wi)001:3178: zhes gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin nyid /
NK050(wi)001:3179: lam thos bsam bsgom gsum gyis gtan la phab nas
NK050(wi)001:3180: mnyam pa nyid kyi don la rtogs goms kyi sbyor
NK050(wi)001:3181: bas mthar 'bras la dngos su sbyor ba la mi
NK050(wi)001:3182: bslu ba'i gtan tshig phan yon dgos ched sogs gsal
NK050(wi)001:3184: rdzogs pa a nu yo gas ni /
NK050(wi)001:3185: dbyings stong nyid kun tu bzang mo'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK050(wi)001:3186: thabs bde ba kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor gnyis
NK050(wi)001:3187: dbyer med pa ni sras bde chen byang chub sems
NK050(wi)001:3189: de nyid rigs dang dkyil 'khor gyi khyab bdag tu nges pa'i bde stong gi lta ba zhes /
NK050(wi)001:3190: don la rang byung zag med bde ba chen po
NK050(wi)001:3191: zhes pa ye nas bde stong 'du 'bral spang pa'i
NK050(wi)001:3192: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyid yin la de
NK050(wi)001:3193: nyid kyis chos thams cad la khyab cing rjes su
NK050(wi)001:3194: song bas snang srid ye nas sangs rgyas par gtan
NK050(wi)001:3195: la phabs nas / gtso bor shes rab rdzogs pa'i
NK050(wi)001:3196: rim pa khams 'ju 'dul sogs kyi thabs la brten
NK050(wi)001:3197: la phabs nas / nas / thabs byung rnam kun
NK050(wi)001:3198: mchog ldan gyi stong pa dang mchog tu mi 'gyur
NK050(wi)001:3199: ba'i bde ba zung du 'jug pa'i ye shes 'od
NK050(wi)001:3200: gsal nam mkha'i gzugs bsam mi khyab pa nyid lam
NK050(wi)001:3202: de yang dbyings ye gnyis med bde chen byang chub
NK050(wi)001:3203: kyi sems ngo bo rdul dang skad cig ma'i chos
NK050(wi)001:3204: las 'das pa'i ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs can mkha'
NK050(wi)001:3205: khyab mkha' yi rdo rje can gyis /
NK050(wi)001:3206: brtan g.yo 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la khyab
NK050(wi)001:3207: cing thams cad de'i rang bzhin las ma 'das pa
NK050(wi)001:3209: gang du bde chen zhes bya gcig pu nyid //
NK050(wi)001:3210: gcig pu'i nyams kyis du ma'i gar byed do //
NK050(wi)001:3213: sangs rgyas ma yin sems can ni //
NK050(wi)001:3214: gcig kyang yod pa mi yin no //
NK050(wi)001:3215: dmyal ba yi dwags byol song dang //
NK050(wi)001:3216: lha dang lha min mi rnams dang //
NK050(wi)001:3217: bshang ba'i srin bu sogs kyis kyang //
NK050(wi)001:3218: bde ba gang phyir mi shes pa //
NK050(wi)001:3219: rtag tu rang bzhin bde ba can //
NK050(wi)001:3220: 'jig rten khams ni gang du yang //
NK050(wi)001:3221: sangs rgyas gzhan du rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:3222: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyid //
NK050(wi)001:3223: sangs rgyas gzhan du bstan pa med //
NK050(wi)001:3225: khyad par mi yi rten can khams drug ldan gyi
NK050(wi)001:3226: rdo rje lus kyi rtsa thig rlung gsum la khyab
NK050(wi)001:3227: byed chos nyid kyi tshul du til la mar gyis
NK050(wi)001:3230: lus la ye shes chen po khyab //
NK050(wi)001:3231: til 'bru la ni mar bzhin du //
NK050(wi)001:3232: lus kyi bkrag mdangs gzi brjid rnams //
NK050(wi)001:3233: ye shes brlan gyis khyab par byed //
NK050(wi)001:3235: 'di la ye shes kyi dbu ma dang //
NK050(wi)001:3237: ye shes kyi thig le zhes phra ba'i sgo gsum rdo rje gsum du sgrub pa'i gzhi ste /
NK050(wi)001:3238: gang la gnad du bsnun bya'i gzhi ni /
NK050(wi)001:3239: 'od gsal gnyug ma'i chos nyid 'gyur med bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyid yin te /
NK050(wi)001:3241: lus can snying la gang gnas pa /
NK050(wi)001:3242: rang byung ye shes zag med gzugs //
NK050(wi)001:3243: mi shigs thig le bde chen po //
NK050(wi)001:3244: nam mkha' lta bur kun la khyab //
NK050(wi)001:3245: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK050(wi)001:3248: mi shigs thig le ye shes ni //
NK050(wi)001:3249: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK050(wi)001:3250: gcig dang du ma rnams spangs pa //
NK050(wi)001:3251: sna tshogs snang la mtshon du med //
NK050(wi)001:3254: rtag tu snying la gnas pa yi //
NK050(wi)001:3255: thig le gcig la 'gyur ba med //
NK050(wi)001:3256: de sgom byed pa'i skyes bu la //
NK050(wi)001:3257: nges par ye shes skye bar 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:3260: lus la ye shes chen po gnas //
NK050(wi)001:3261: rtogs pa thams cad yang dag spangs //
NK050(wi)001:3262: dngos po kun la khyab pa po //
NK050(wi)001:3263: lus gnas lus las ma skyes pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:3265: de yang chos rnams la stong nyid kyis khyab cing //
NK050(wi)001:3266: kun rdzob la brten nas don dam stong nyid gtan la 'bebs kyang /
NK050(wi)001:3267: stong nyid 'dus byas su mi 'gyur ba bzhin /
NK050(wi)001:3268: lhan skyes bde ba chen po'i ye shes kyis dngos po kun la khyab cing /
NK050(wi)001:3269: lus thams ldan gyi lam sogs kyis mngon du byed rung kyang /
NK050(wi)001:3270: ye shes de nyid de las gsar du skyes pa ni min no //
NK050(wi)001:3271: 'di la rgyud sde gong 'og sogs kyi khyad par
NK050(wi)001:3272: gyis sku dang thig le sogs sna tshogs bshad pa
NK050(wi)001:3273: yod kyang don la gnad gcig ste zag med rang
NK050(wi)001:3274: byung gi ye shes 'ba' zhig yin /
NK050(wi)001:3275: bde ba chen po zhes pa'ang 'gyur bcas kyi zug
NK050(wi)001:3276: ngu dang bral ba'i rang byung zag med kyi bde
NK050(wi)001:3277: ba dang stong zung du 'jug pa'i ye shes brjod
NK050(wi)001:3278: bral lhan cig skyes 'dus ma byas chen nyid la
NK050(wi)001:3279: brjod kyi tshor bde 'gyur ba can ni min te
NK050(wi)001:3281: dbang po gnyis sbyor bde ba ni //
NK050(wi)001:3282: de nyid yin zhes skye ngan smra //
NK050(wi)001:3283: de ni bde chen de nyid du //
NK050(wi)001:3284: rgyal ba mchog gis ma gsungs so //
NK050(wi)001:3286: bde chen mi rtag ma yin te //
NK050(wi)001:3287: bde ba chen po rtag tu rtag /
NK050(wi)001:3289: des na don dam byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen po dang /
NK050(wi)001:3290: kun rdzob mtshan ma'i rtsa thig rlung gsum rten brten
NK050(wi)001:3291: pa'am chos can dang chos nyid kyi tshul du 'brel
NK050(wi)001:3292: ba'i dbang gis / phyi'i bskyed rim spros rtsol sogs la ma ltos par /
NK050(wi)001:3293: nang rdo rje'i lus kyi rtsa rlung gi byed bcing
NK050(wi)001:3294: sogs rang lus thabs ldan dang gzhan lus pho nya'i
NK050(wi)001:3295: lam gang rung la brten nas gnad du bsnun pas
NK050(wi)001:3296: / rlung sems 'jug pa gcig pa'i gnad kyis rlung
NK050(wi)001:3297: dbu mar thim pas sems 'gag pa'i ye shes dpe
NK050(wi)001:3298: don gyis 'od gsal mngon du byed pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:3299: de'i tshe rang bzhin brgyad bcu'i kun rtog bzhon pa
NK050(wi)001:3300: dang bcas pa mtha' dag thim pa'i 'od gsal ba'i
NK050(wi)001:3301: dbyings rig gdangs ma 'gags pa'i bdag nyid can ni
NK050(wi)001:3302: / sems dang ye shes kyi zlas phye bas ye shes yin gyi sems ma yin la /
NK050(wi)001:3303: ye shes de nyid la yang yang goms pas nang gi sa lam bgrod de /
NK050(wi)001:3304: mthar ma dag rlung sems kyi cha dkar dmar rlung
NK050(wi)001:3305: gi byed pa snang gsum 'pho sgrib phra ba bcas
NK050(wi)001:3306: 'dod chags chen po'i lam gyis sbyang nas /
NK050(wi)001:3307: thog mar gang las byung ba'i gzhi 'gyur med bde ba chen po'i dbyings su dag pa'am thim nas /
NK050(wi)001:3308: 'bras bu gsung rdo rje dang gnyis su med pa'i
NK050(wi)001:3309: ye shes chen po nyid mngon du byed pa yin
NK050(wi)001:3311: gang du 'jig rten gsum po mtha' dag snang 'gyur
NK050(wi)001:3312: mi yi bdag po slar yang gang du thim pa'o
NK050(wi)001:3315: phyi nang bye brag ji snyed pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:3316: chos rnams thams cad byang chub sems //
NK050(wi)001:3317: ji bzhin ngang du ye gnas pas //
NK050(wi)001:3318: shes par bya ba rgyud don yin //
NK050(wi)001:3320: thig le mchog gi rgyud las /
NK050(wi)001:3321: 'od gsal ba yi sems nyid ni //
NK050(wi)001:3322: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med par //
NK050(wi)001:3323: bde bar che de sus sgom pa //
NK050(wi)001:3326: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo gas ni /
NK050(wi)001:3327: bya bral lhun rdzogs kyi lta ba zhes //
NK050(wi)001:3328: gshis gang du'ang ma grub la /
NK050(wi)001:3329: gang ltar yang 'char ba'i gzhi ma 'gags pa'i rig pa /
NK050(wi)001:3332: thugs rje'i rtsal ma 'gag pa'i chos nyid /
NK050(wi)001:3333: ye sangs rgyas pa'i mgon po rang chas su ye ldan pa ste /
NK050(wi)001:3336: dag ma dag sogs gnyis chos kyi spros pa'i mtha'
NK050(wi)001:3337: kun dang bral bas mtha' bral tsam du'ang bzhag tu
NK050(wi)001:3338: med la / rang bzhin gyi ngos nas sku dang
NK050(wi)001:3339: ye shes sogs yod pa'i tha snyad du ma dang
NK050(wi)001:3340: med la / ldan pa / thugs rje'i ngos nas
NK050(wi)001:3341: rig rtsal sna tshogs kyi 'char gzhi dang sgo 'byed
NK050(wi)001:3342: med la / ldan pa / pa / de dag
NK050(wi)001:3343: kyang gcig tha dad sogs grub mtha'i zhen rtog gi
NK050(wi)001:3344: spyod yul las 'das pa'i rang bzhin mtha' grol klong
NK050(wi)001:3345: yangs chen por ye nas gnas so //
NK050(wi)001:3346: de yang ma dag 'khrul pa'i snang ba rnams ni rmi lam dang 'dra bas /
NK050(wi)001:3347: ngo bo med pa rten med pa /
NK050(wi)001:3348: gdod nas yod ma myong la /
NK050(wi)001:3349: ma 'khrul ba'i ye shes sam bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ni /
NK050(wi)001:3352: dri ma ye nas sangs shing yon tan ye nas rgyas pa'i 'dus ma byas lhun grub chen po /
NK050(wi)001:3353: tshu rol mthong ba'i blos bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK050(wi)001:3354: dpe nyi mkha' lta bu ste /
NK050(wi)001:3355: de ltar rtogs na mngal gyi grong khyer rgyun bcad
NK050(wi)001:3356: nas khams gsum du mi ldog pas grong khyer rgyun
NK050(wi)001:3357: gcod kyi lta ba zhes gsungs te /
NK050(wi)001:3358: don la gong smos rang byung zag med kyi ye
NK050(wi)001:3359: shes ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum dbyer med
NK050(wi)001:3360: pa ye nas sku gsum gyi ngo bor lhun gyis
NK050(wi)001:3361: grub pas / de'i rtsal las shar ba'i rol pa
NK050(wi)001:3362: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye nas
NK050(wi)001:3363: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin nam
NK050(wi)001:3364: dkyil 'khor las ma 'das pa yin te /
NK050(wi)001:3366: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po yis //
NK050(wi)001:3367: snying po sku yi dkyil 'khor bkod pa ni //
NK050(wi)001:3368: ji ltar snang zhing gnas pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK050(wi)001:3369: skye ba med pa'i chos dbyings ngang la bkod //
NK050(wi)001:3370: ji ltar grags shing gnas pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK050(wi)001:3371: skye med dbyings las tshig gi gsung du bkod //
NK050(wi)001:3372: snying po brjod du med pa'i gsung la 'dus //
NK050(wi)001:3373: de yang kun byed rgyal po'i bkod pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:3374: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po yis //
NK050(wi)001:3375: snying po rig pa'i dkyil 'khor bkod pa ni //
NK050(wi)001:3376: ji ltar dran rig rtog pa thams cad kun //
NK050(wi)001:3377: ma skyes kun byed nyid kyi don du rig /
NK050(wi)001:3378: kun byed nga yi sku gsung thugs nyid ni //
NK050(wi)001:3379: ma bcos rnal du bzhag pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK050(wi)001:3380: ma bkod dus gcig rdzogs pa'i don rtogs pas //
NK050(wi)001:3381: lhun grub snying po'i don la 'jug par byed //
NK050(wi)001:3383: des na da lta'i rig pa rang gnas kyi bsam
NK050(wi)001:3384: gtan skyon yon grub bsal las 'das pa'i chos nyid
NK050(wi)001:3386: blos byas dang yid dpyod du ma song bar /
NK050(wi)001:3389: gdams ngag gi zab khyad la brten nas mngon sum du ngo 'phrod par byas te /
NK050(wi)001:3390: de nyid kun bzang chos sku'i dgongs par thag bcad rang grol spangs gnyen dang bral bar gdengs bcas /
NK050(wi)001:3391: tshogs drug gi yul snang gang la'ang dgag sgrub spang gnyen dang bral bar lam du khyer bas /
NK050(wi)001:3392: phyi chos can la bltas pas 'khrul snang rten med
NK050(wi)001:3393: du snang ba sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad du rtogs nas
NK050(wi)001:3395: nang chos nyid la bltas pas ro mnyam grub bsal
NK050(wi)001:3396: med pa nam mkha' ltar rtogs nas spros bral chos
NK050(wi)001:3397: zad kyi ngang du re dogs kyi 'dzin pa zhig
NK050(wi)001:3398: / gsang ba rig pa la bltas pas stong gsal
NK050(wi)001:3399: 'gag med chen po chos sku lhun grub tu rtogs
NK050(wi)001:3400: nas rtsol sgrub bcos bslad dang bral te /
NK050(wi)001:3401: de'i tshe theg pa gzhan gyis mi mthong ba'i don mthong bas /
NK050(wi)001:3402: dpe ri rab kyi rtser phyin pas gling bzhi dus
NK050(wi)001:3403: gcig la mthong ba dang 'dra ba'i phyir ri bo
NK050(wi)001:3404: cog bzhag gi sgom pa zhes bya ste /
NK050(wi)001:3407: nga ni kun byed rgyal po byang chub sems //
NK050(wi)001:3408: nga la sgro skur bya ba'i yul med pas //
NK050(wi)001:3409: gang la'ang sems par ma byed sgom ma byed //
NK050(wi)001:3410: sgo gsum ma bcos ji bzhin lhug par zhog /
NK050(wi)001:3411: ji ltar shar yang rang bzhin ngang gis grol //
NK050(wi)001:3412: skye med nam mkha' lta bur phyogs 'das pas //
NK050(wi)001:3413: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen por shes par gyis //
NK050(wi)001:3415: ma bcos rnal ma kun gyi chos nyid yin //
NK050(wi)001:3416: chos nyid las ni sangs rgyas gud na med //
NK050(wi)001:3417: sangs rgyas ming du btags pa bla dwags yin //
NK050(wi)001:3418: chos nyid bya ba gzhan med rang sems te //
NK050(wi)001:3419: rang sems ma bcos chos kyi sku ru bshad //
NK050(wi)001:3420: ma bcos pa la ye nas skye med pas //
NK050(wi)001:3421: skye med don la btsal zhing sgrub tu med //
NK050(wi)001:3422: btsal zhing sgrub pas byar med 'grub mi 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:3425: rang bzhin dag pa chen po'i mtha' //
NK050(wi)001:3426: chos rnams rang sar bzhag pa ste //
NK050(wi)001:3427: snang shes chos nyid zung 'jug pas //
NK050(wi)001:3428: ye grol cog bzhag nyid la thug /
NK050(wi)001:3429: dgongs pa blo las 'das pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:3430: mtshan bcas rang sar dag pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:3431: stong dang dngos po'i mtha' grol dang //
NK050(wi)001:3432: 'byung zad rtog pa med pa dang //
NK050(wi)001:3435: thabs des grub pa'i dgongs pa ni khams gsum yongs grol zhes bya ste /
NK050(wi)001:3436: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas bltas na /
NK050(wi)001:3437: snang srid 'khor 'das thams cad la ma grol ba gcig kyang med de /
NK050(wi)001:3439: da lta 'khrul ba gzhi la mi gnas /
NK050(wi)001:3440: tha ma 'khrul mi srid pa'i phyir de skad ces bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:3441: de ltar rtogs thog tu bzhag pas /
NK050(wi)001:3442: dgag sgrub dang re dogs spang gnyen gzung 'dzin gyis bsdus pa'i mtshan rtog rang sar deng nas /
NK050(wi)001:3443: chos zad ye grol gyi dgongs par gnas te /
NK050(wi)001:3444: de'i tshe 'khrul pa don la med par rtogs pas 'khor ba spang du med pas blo bde /
NK050(wi)001:3445: chos la phyogs ris med pas grub mtha'i 'khrul pa
NK050(wi)001:3446: zhig ste chos su 'dzin zhen med pas blo bde
NK050(wi)001:3447: / tshig gis don thog tu mi phebs pas yid
NK050(wi)001:3448: dpyod tshig phyir 'brangs kyang sangs mi rgya bar shes
NK050(wi)001:3449: / te / tha snyad tshig la gdeng du mi
NK050(wi)001:3450: 'dzin pas blo bde ba gsum khongs nas 'char ba
NK050(wi)001:3451: / te / yin te / mdor na kun byed las /
NK050(wi)001:3452: byar med 'di la gang gnas pa //
NK050(wi)001:3453: lus ni gang zag lha mi yang //
NK050(wi)001:3454: dgongs pa chos nyid sangs rgyas yin //
NK050(wi)001:3456: de ltar bzhag pas ma dag rlung sems kyi 'gyu
NK050(wi)001:3457: ba mtha' dag rang 'gags su song nas ye grol
NK050(wi)001:3458: bde gshegs snying po'i rang bzhin chos zad ming med
NK050(wi)001:3459: chen po ka dag blo 'das rig stong thugs rdo
NK050(wi)001:3460: rje chos sku'i dgongs pa mngon du gyur te da
NK050(wi)001:3461: lta nyid nas lhun mnyam bde ba chen po'i sa
NK050(wi)001:3462: la phyin par byed pa gnad kyi me btsa' lta
NK050(wi)001:3464: de phyir sems dpa' rdo rje khyod kyis kyang //
NK050(wi)001:3465: sgra la ma dga' don nyid rtogs par gyis //
NK050(wi)001:3466: gang gis de la rtogs pa skyes ma thag /
NK050(wi)001:3467: kun byed rgyal po'i dron la dbang 'byor 'gyur //
NK050(wi)001:3469: de yang thabs lam pa ltar rtsa rlung gi byed
NK050(wi)001:3470: bcing sogs la brten nas rags rlung dbu mar bstim
NK050(wi)001:3471: ste / rang bzhin brgyad cu'i kun rtog 'gog pa sogs kyi rtsol ba la lam ltos par /
NK050(wi)001:3472: grol lam bla ma'i man ngag gis rang gnas kyi
NK050(wi)001:3473: ye shes da lta nas mngon sum du ngo sprod
NK050(wi)001:3474: du yod pa ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK050(wi)001:3476: zhib par sems dang rig pa /
NK050(wi)001:3477: kun gzhi dang chos sku'i dbye ba sogs rdzogs pa
NK050(wi)001:3478: chen po'i rgyud gzhung rnams dang khyad par kun mkhyen
NK050(wi)001:3479: chen po'i gsung rab las rtogs par bya zhing /
NK050(wi)001:3480: don la rdzogs chen gyi rig ngo 'khyug med 'phrod
NK050(wi)001:3481: na sngags lam gyi dpe yi 'od gsal skyes pa
NK050(wi)001:3482: yin / 'di nyid mngon sum yin phyir don gyi ye shes dngos su bzhed pa yod kyang /
NK050(wi)001:3483: rang lugs kun mkhyen chen po ni /
NK050(wi)001:3484: don gyi ye shes dngos mthong lam yin pas de
NK050(wi)001:3485: la yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis mngon du gyur
NK050(wi)001:3487: 'dir mngon sum gyis mthong ba yin yang da dung
NK050(wi)001:3488: mthong spang gi dri ma'i sbub las ma grol ba'i
NK050(wi)001:3489: phyir don gyi 'od gsal dngos ma yin la /
NK050(wi)001:3491: de nyid la goms pas don gyi ye shes btsan
NK050(wi)001:3492: thabs su 'dren pas zung 'jug 'phags pa'i sa la
NK050(wi)001:3494: de yang snang tshul du ma dag rlung sems kyi g.yo ba stobs su gyur te /
NK050(wi)001:3495: rig pa rang gnas kyi ye shes bzhon pa dang
NK050(wi)001:3496: bcas pa bag la zha ba'i tshul gyis mngon du
NK050(wi)001:3497: ma gyur pa'i gzhi sems can dang /
NK050(wi)001:3498: gnyen po ye shes nyid ngos zin te rnam shes
NK050(wi)001:3499: dang ye shes kyi byed pa 'dres pa'i skabs su
NK050(wi)001:3501: ma dag rlung sems kyi 'gyu cha mtha' dag dang
NK050(wi)001:3502: bral te ye shes dang ye rlung gi byed pa
NK050(wi)001:3503: 'ba' zhig tu gyur pa ni 'bras bu sangs rgyas
NK050(wi)001:3504: kyi sa'i rnam par bzhag ste /
NK050(wi)001:3509: tha snyad du gcig ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:3513: thugs rje'i 'char tshul ma 'gags pa'i rig pa byang chub kyi sems yin la /
NK050(wi)001:3514: de'i rtsal ye shes su shar du /
NK050(wi)001:3515: de las rol pa sangs rgyas kyi sku dang zhing khams sogs dang /
NK050(wi)001:3516: rtsal ma rig 'khrul sems su shar dus /
NK050(wi)001:3517: de las rol pa sems can gyi phung khams skye
NK050(wi)001:3518: mched sogs 'khor ba'i chos rnams snang ba yin pas
NK050(wi)001:3519: / de lta na snang ba dang snang yul /
NK050(wi)001:3522: gzhi lam 'bras gsum sogs so sor phyes te tha snyad kyi rnam bzhag rnams zhib mor byed dgos /
NK050(wi)001:3523: don dam par tha dad du ma yin te /
NK050(wi)001:3524: rol pa ni med snang stong gzugs sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad lta bu don la yod ma myong la /
NK050(wi)001:3525: rtsal ni shar grol rjes med ngo bo ngos bzung dang bral ba nam mkha'i bya rjes lta bu /
NK050(wi)001:3526: chos nyid byang chub kyi sems ni ngo bo bsam
NK050(wi)001:3527: brjod las 'das pa'i mtha' zad ming med spros bral
NK050(wi)001:3528: mnyam pa chen po yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:3529: gcig tha dad du dbye ba'i gzhi med do //
NK050(wi)001:3530: des na snang sems ro mnyam gdod nas ka dag
NK050(wi)001:3531: ye grol chen por shes par bya ste grub mtha'
NK050(wi)001:3532: 'og ma'i zhe 'dod dang bsre bar mi bya ste
NK050(wi)001:3534: thog ma nyid kyi ka dag la //
NK050(wi)001:3535: 'khrul zhes tsam du brjod du med //
NK050(wi)001:3537: de phyir 'khrul pa gdod nas dag /
NK050(wi)001:3540: rang sems grol ba zhes bya ba /
NK050(wi)001:3541: gcig nas gcig tu song ba med //
NK050(wi)001:3542: gang gis bkrol ba med pa'i sems //
NK050(wi)001:3544: brtags pas ma rnyed rgyu mtshan med //
NK050(wi)001:3545: gzhi rtsa med pa'i stong gsal gnas //
NK050(wi)001:3546: rang gsal gnas pa'i sems de ni //
NK050(wi)001:3547: gnad kyis grol bas phyogs ris med //
NK050(wi)001:3548: dus kyis grol bas ltos gzhi med //
NK050(wi)001:3550: gdeng gis grol bas 'bad rtsol med //
NK050(wi)001:3551: de la gdeng gis grol ba bshad //
NK050(wi)001:3552: ye nas grol bas bskyar gzhi med //
NK050(wi)001:3553: ngang gis grol bas gnyen po med //
NK050(wi)001:3554: cer gyis grol bas mthong sar yal //
NK050(wi)001:3555: yongs su grol bas 'bad med pa'o //
NK050(wi)001:3558: lta ba ye grol du rtogs kyang sgom pa yin
NK050(wi)001:3559: thog tu ma bzhag na gzung 'dzin gyi 'khrul pa
NK050(wi)001:3560: mi choms shing ma bsgoms par sangs rgyas pa'i lam
NK050(wi)001:3561: ni rdo rje 'chang gis kyang ma bstan par gsungs
NK050(wi)001:3562: pa bzhin / las dang po pas dben pa brten
NK050(wi)001:3563: te rtse gcig tu nyams su len par bya ba
NK050(wi)001:3564: pa bzhin / gal che / gnas lugs rtogs ma
NK050(wi)001:3565: rtogs kyi tshad 'dzin pa yod med du gsungs pa
NK050(wi)001:3566: bzhin zhen med 'dzin med gang shar spang blang dang
NK050(wi)001:3568: dad mos snying rje bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug pas
NK050(wi)001:3569: 'khrul pa ye shes su dag pa'i lam gnad du
NK050(wi)001:3570: gang 'gro la brtson par bya dgos so //
NK050(wi)001:3571: 'di la'ang gzhi ka dag gi nyams len sems klong sogs su /
NK050(wi)001:3572: rang byung zag med kyi dbyings kyi yon tan sku
NK050(wi)001:3573: dang ye shes sogs bltar mi mngon pa'i chos nyid
NK050(wi)001:3574: kyi tshul du bzhugs pa'i rig stong chos zad rjen
NK050(wi)001:3575: pa'i gshis lugs 'ching grol las 'das pa nyid lam
NK050(wi)001:3576: du byed kyi / da lta nas chos nyid 'od
NK050(wi)001:3577: gsal ba'i rtags snang rnams mngon sum lam du byed
NK050(wi)001:3578: du byed kyi / pa min pas / gang zag
NK050(wi)001:3579: blo chung ba kha cig la yid dpyod dang gshis
NK050(wi)001:3580: shor gyi gol sa 'byung ba'i nyen yod la /
NK050(wi)001:3581: lhun grub thod rgal gyi nyams len yang gsang man
NK050(wi)001:3582: ngag snying thig gi dgongs pa sgo yul rlung rig
NK050(wi)001:3583: sogs kyi gnad zab mo la brten nas /
NK050(wi)001:3584: ye shes rin po che'i gsang mdzod phyes te chos nyid yid dpyod du ma song bar /
NK050(wi)001:3585: mngon sum 'od gsal gyi rtags snang bzhi'i ye shes lam du byas pas /
NK050(wi)001:3586: dbang rnon skal pa mchog dang ldan pa rnams zla
NK050(wi)001:3587: drug sogs kyis rang snang longs sku'i zhing khams gtan
NK050(wi)001:3588: la phebs shing mthar phyin gzhon du bum skur grol
NK050(wi)001:3589: te mi slob pa'i zung 'jug mngon du byed par
NK050(wi)001:3590: gsungs pas na / rigs khams chos nyid 'od gsal
NK050(wi)001:3591: ba'i ye shes nges pa ji tsam skyes pa de
NK050(wi)001:3592: gsungs pas na / tsam du / de nyid mngon
NK050(wi)001:3593: du byed pa'i lam mam thabs ji zab tu song
NK050(wi)001:3594: ba yin te mthar phyin pa ni rang bzhin rdzogs
NK050(wi)001:3595: pa chen po'i lam 'ba' zhig yin pas 'di ni
NK050(wi)001:3596: rdzogs rim kun gyi mthar thug pa'am bla mar gyur
NK050(wi)001:3597: gsungs pas na / tsam du / pa yin no // mdor na /
NK050(wi)001:3598: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dag mnyam bden pa
NK050(wi)001:3599: dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por ye nas
NK050(wi)001:3600: sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du rtogs pa ni lta
NK050(wi)001:3601: ba / rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK050(wi)001:3602: 'khor chen por ye nas lhun gyis grub par gnas
NK050(wi)001:3603: pa'i don la blo ma bcos par 'jog pa ni
NK050(wi)001:3604: ba / sgom pa / lta sgom zung du 'brel
NK050(wi)001:3605: ba'i sgo nas snang grags kyi chos thams cad sku
NK050(wi)001:3606: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor chen por longs spyod
NK050(wi)001:3608: sgo gsum rdo rje gsum gyi rang bzhin du shes te de las mi 'da' ba ni dam tshig /
NK050(wi)001:3609: de mngon du gyur pa ni 'bras bu yin pas na /
NK050(wi)001:3610: de ltar lta sgom spyod 'bras sogs kyi chos rnams
NK050(wi)001:3611: don la dbyer mi phyed par nyams su len pa
NK050(wi)001:3612: ni 'bras bu lam du byed pa zhes gsang sngags
NK050(wi)001:3613: nang rgyud bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gsum gyi bstan bya'i
NK050(wi)001:3615: de yang dag pa mya ngan las 'das pa sangs rgyas kyi sku dang zhing khams nas /
NK050(wi)001:3616: ma dag pa 'khor ba'i snod bcud phung khams skye mched sogs dang /
NK050(wi)001:3617: bar ma rnal 'byor pa'i nyams kyi snang bas bsdus
NK050(wi)001:3618: pa ji ltar snang ba'i chos 'di thams cad la
NK050(wi)001:3619: / don dam dpyod byed kyi tshad mas gzhal na /
NK050(wi)001:3620: rgyu rkyen las ma skyes pa'i phyir dang /
NK050(wi)001:3621: dus glo bur du ma byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK050(wi)001:3622: byed pos ma byas pa'i phyir dang /
NK050(wi)001:3623: skyes pa'i dngos po 'di 'dra zhes ma dmigs pa'i phyir don dam skye bar med par mnyam zhing /
NK050(wi)001:3624: tha snyad dpyod byed kyi tshad mas gzhal na /
NK050(wi)001:3625: kun rdzob snang tsam po 'di las mthun par bsags
NK050(wi)001:3626: pa'i 'gro ba rnams la mthun snang du grub pa'i
NK050(wi)001:3627: phyir dang / snang tsam po 'di med na don
NK050(wi)001:3628: dam shes byed kyang med kyang med pa'i skyon du
NK050(wi)001:3630: snang ba 'di thams cad mkhyen pa'i phyag gis kyang ma khegs par snang 'dug pa'i phyir dang /
NK050(wi)001:3631: rang rig pa'i rtsal thams cad du ma 'gags par
NK050(wi)001:3632: rang snang ba'i phyi rol ba 'gags pa med par
NK050(wi)001:3633: mnyam la / mthar thug bden gnyis dbyer med du dpyod pa'i tshad mas gzhal na /
NK050(wi)001:3634: de gnyis la rang bzhin bzang ngan med pa'i phyir dang /
NK050(wi)001:3635: ngo bo dbyer med pa'i phyir dang /
NK050(wi)001:3636: 'dug sa tha mi dad pa'i phyir dang /
NK050(wi)001:3637: dus snga phyi med pa'i phyir dbyer med bsam yul las 'das par mnyam pas na /
NK050(wi)001:3638: dag ma dag sogs gnyis chos kyi spros pa thams cad blos btags pa tsam las /
NK050(wi)001:3639: yul rang gi ngos nas grub pa cung zad kyang med pas /
NK050(wi)001:3644: thams cad spros bral mnyam pa chen po las mi
NK050(wi)001:3645: 'da' bas gang la'ang dgag sgrub zhen 'dzin med par
NK050(wi)001:3646: rang sar bzhag pas gang snang ye shes kyi rol
NK050(wi)001:3647: par 'char ba'i gnad de yin pas /
NK050(wi)001:3648: de ltar ma shes par gzung 'dzin gyi blos dgag
NK050(wi)001:3649: sgrub tu zhen na gang gis kyang 'khrul gzhi byed
NK050(wi)001:3650: de thog ma'i 'od gsal chen po'i rtsal la bdag
NK050(wi)001:3651: tu zhen pas sems can rnams 'khrul pa bzhin no
NK050(wi)001:3652: // de bzhin du ya ki sangs rgyas kyi gsung nas /
NK050(wi)001:3653: ma ki 'gro drug gi brjod pa'i bar /
NK050(wi)001:3654: yang dag pa'i don dang ldan pa'i chos dang /
NK050(wi)001:3655: phyin ci log grub mtha' ngan pa'i gtam dang /
NK050(wi)001:3656: bar ma lung ma bstan gyi rigs sogs ji ltar grags pa 'di thams cad kyang /
NK050(wi)001:3657: don dam par brag ca'i sgra bzhin phyi nang gang
NK050(wi)001:3658: du'ang btsal na mi rnyed de rang bzhin skye ba
NK050(wi)001:3659: med par mnyam la kun rdzob tu ming tshig yi
NK050(wi)001:3660: ge sogs kyi rnam par shar zhing brda' sprod pa
NK050(wi)001:3661: sogs kyi nus pa ma 'gags par yang mnyam la
NK050(wi)001:3662: / de ltar grags pa'i dus nyid na'ang rang bzhin gyis skye ba med la /
NK050(wi)001:3663: skye ba med bzhin ming tshig brjod pa'i ngo bo snang bas na /
NK050(wi)001:3664: log par brtags na sgra thams cad grags stong brjod
NK050(wi)001:3665: med yi ge'i rang bzhin las ma 'das pas de
NK050(wi)001:3666: ltar shes na gang gis kyang mi 'ching zhing sgra
NK050(wi)001:3667: grags brjod pa thams cad sngags kyi bzlas pa las
NK050(wi)001:3668: mi 'da' 'o // de ltar ma shes par rang mtshan du zhen na gang gis kyang 'ching ste /
NK050(wi)001:3669: dper na drag sngags rang mtshan par bzlas pas log par gol ba'i tshul gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:3670: de bzhin du yid kyi yul du /
NK050(wi)001:3671: dag pa lha sku'i gsal snang sogs bskyed rdzogs kyi sems 'dzin dang /
NK050(wi)001:3672: ma dag pa nyon mongs dug lnga dug gsum rtsa ba bdag tu 'dzin pa sogs te /
NK050(wi)001:3673: bar ma dge mi dge lung ma bstan gyi 'gyu
NK050(wi)001:3674: dran gyi rtog pa ci dang ci shar yang rtsa
NK050(wi)001:3675: ba sems nyid gcig pu'i rang rtsal las ma 'das
NK050(wi)001:3676: shing sems ni dang po 'byung bas stong /
NK050(wi)001:3679: dus gsum skye 'gags sogs kyi spros pa'i mtshan ma
NK050(wi)001:3680: thams cad dang bral ba'i chos nyid mnyam pa chen
NK050(wi)001:3681: po yin la / spros bral stong nyid de'i rang rtsal las ma 'gags par shar ba'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:3682: shar ba'i dus na mnyam shar /
NK050(wi)001:3683: gnas pa'i dus na mnyam gnas /
NK050(wi)001:3684: grol ba'i dus na mnyam grol te /
NK050(wi)001:3685: thams cad bzang ngan med par chos nyid mnyam pa
NK050(wi)001:3686: chen po'i klong du rang grol bas gshis la 'pho
NK050(wi)001:3687: 'gyur dang bri gang bsal bzhag bral ba'i gnad kyis
NK050(wi)001:3688: / gang shar yang spang blang dgag sgrub bral bar
NK050(wi)001:3689: rang sar bzhag pas gnyen po gzhan mi dgos par
NK050(wi)001:3690: rang gis rang grol te kun kyang ye shes chen
NK050(wi)001:3692: de ltar ma shes par gang la'ang mtshan mar zhen na 'ching bar 'gyur te /
NK050(wi)001:3693: bskyed rim rang rgyud par bzung bas ru tra sogs su gol ba dang /
NK050(wi)001:3694: thabs lam rang mtshan par zhen pas mngal gyi srin
NK050(wi)001:3695: bur skye ba sogs rgyud sde rnams nas gsungs pa
NK050(wi)001:3696: bzhin no // des na snang grags rtog tshogs kyis
NK050(wi)001:3697: bsdus pa'i chos gang la'ang spang blang dgag sgrub dang
NK050(wi)001:3698: bral bar chos nyid mnyam pa'i don la gdeng bcas
NK050(wi)001:3699: te de'i ngang las mi g.yo bar bya ba ni
NK050(wi)001:3700: mnyam bzhag tu la bzla ba'i tshul yin la /
NK050(wi)001:3701: rjes thob spyod pas shan 'byed pa'i skabs su ni /
NK050(wi)001:3702: ji srid gzung 'dzin gyi 'khrul rtog dbyings su ma dag pa'i bar du /
NK050(wi)001:3703: kun rdzob las dang las kyi 'bras bu sogs bslu med du yod pas /
NK050(wi)001:3704: 'dzin med sgyu ma lta bu'i rtsis zin pa'i ngang
NK050(wi)001:3705: nas thabs shes zung du 'jug pa'i lam chen gyi
NK050(wi)001:3706: dge rtsa dam pa gsum ldan du sgrub pa sogs
NK050(wi)001:3707: blang dor tshul bzhin bya ba las stong sta had
NK050(wi)001:3708: pos khyad du mi gsod pa ni cis kyang gal
NK050(wi)001:3709: che ste o rgyan dus gsum mkhyen pas kyang rjes
NK050(wi)001:3710: su gdams par mdzad pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:3711: de'i ngor ni sangs rgyas kyi sku gzugs rtsig ngos
NK050(wi)001:3712: la bris pa tshun chad sems can dman pa dud
NK050(wi)001:3713: 'gro yan gang gi mig lam du snang ba dang
NK050(wi)001:3714: / gzungs sngags khyad par can dang sangs rgyas kyi mtshan sogs rna bar lan gcig thos pa dang /
NK050(wi)001:3715: dkon mchog gsum la dwangs ba'i sems skad cig ma skyes te /
NK050(wi)001:3717: thal mo ya gcig gdeng ba'am /
NK050(wi)001:3718: me tog gcig nam mkhar 'thor ba yan chod rnam
NK050(wi)001:3719: grol gyi 'bras bu las phyir mi ldog par mdo
NK050(wi)001:3720: rgyud bstan bcos tshad ma'i lung las 'byung ba bzhin
NK050(wi)001:3721: kun la dag snang sbyang zhing nges shes bskyed /
NK050(wi)001:3722: chos nyid bsam mi khyab pa'i don dran pa'i ngang
NK050(wi)001:3723: nas chos dang gang zag la skur pa mi gdab
NK050(wi)001:3724: gtso bor rang rgyud kyi ma dag 'khrul pa'i snang
NK050(wi)001:3725: ba 'di sbyong ba'i thabs la brtson par bya'o //
NK050(wi)001:3726: des na rang bzhin rdzogs rigs gdod ma'i 'od gsal
NK050(wi)001:3727: chen po 'ching grol las 'das pa ni bral gzhi
NK050(wi)001:3728: / de'i steng gi sgrib byed kyi dri ma med snang blo bur ba rnams ni bral bya /
NK050(wi)001:3729: de sel byed gnyen po lam bden gyi char gtogs 'khor dang bcas pa ni bral rgyu'am bral byed /
NK050(wi)001:3730: mthar thug sgrib pa mtha' dag dang bral nas gzhi
NK050(wi)001:3731: la gnas pa'i yon tan tha dad mngon sum du
NK050(wi)001:3732: gyur te dag pa gnyis ldan mthar thug pa sangs
NK050(wi)001:3733: rgyas rang snang gi sku gsum zhing khams mdzad pa
NK050(wi)001:3734: phrin las dang bcas pa ye shes kyi rol pa
NK050(wi)001:3735: tshad med pa ni bral ba'i 'bras bu ste /
NK050(wi)001:3736: 'di'i skabs su kun gzhi tshogs brgyad dang bcas pa
NK050(wi)001:3737: dbyings su dag pas slob lam gyi thob pa chad
NK050(wi)001:3739: rang bzhin 'od gsal sgrib bral gyi sems chen po'am
NK050(wi)001:3740: zag pa med pa'i ye shes mthar thug pa mngon
NK050(wi)001:3741: du gyur pas yul yul can tha dad du 'dzin
NK050(wi)001:3742: pa'i zhen rtog phra mo tsam yang mi mnga' mod
NK050(wi)001:3743: kyi / mnyam nyid phyogs lhung bral ba'i mkhyen pa'i ye shes skad cig ma gcig gis /
NK050(wi)001:3744: dus gsum gyi shes bya mtha' dag cig car du gzigs shing /
NK050(wi)001:3745: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje chen po rgyun chad
NK050(wi)001:3746: med pas ji srid 'khor ba'i mtha' ma rdzogs kyi
NK050(wi)001:3747: bar du / rtag khyab lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin
NK050(wi)001:3748: las gdul bya'i yul la rtsol med du 'jug pas
NK050(wi)001:3749: lus can mtha' dag gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi
NK050(wi)001:3750: phan bde'i dpal la 'god par mdzad pa ni gnas
NK050(wi)001:3751: gyur mtha' thug pa thob pa'i dbang gis so //
NK050(wi)001:3753: sgrib byed mtha' dag dang bral ba'i ye shes zag
NK050(wi)001:3754: pa med pa nyid ji bzhin par mngon du gyur
NK050(wi)001:3755: pa'i cha tsam la brjod kyi /
NK050(wi)001:3756: theg pa 'go ma pa rnams 'dod pa'i gnas gyur mtshan nyid pa ni min te /
NK050(wi)001:3757: dus gsum 'pho 'gyur dang bral ba'i chos nyid bsam
NK050(wi)001:3758: mi khyab pa'i rang bzhin rang byung bsam med kyi
NK050(wi)001:3759: ye shes 'dus ma byas kyis khyad par du byas
NK050(wi)001:3760: pa'i phyir / des na sangs rgyas kyi mkhyen brtse
NK050(wi)001:3761: nus gsum sogs ye shes bsam mi khyab pa ni
NK050(wi)001:3762: chos kyi dbyings dang tha mi dad par dbyer med
NK050(wi)001:3763: ro mnyam pas nam yang rgyun chad pa mi srid
NK050(wi)001:3764: pa'i phyir / la / mkhyen brtse nus gsum gyi
NK050(wi)001:3765: phrin las gang la 'jug pa'i yul gdul bya sems
NK050(wi)001:3766: can gyi khams la'ang mtha' med pa'i phyir /
NK050(wi)001:3767: de ma zad kyi bar du gang 'dul zhing sku'i
NK050(wi)001:3768: bkod pa dang ye shes yon tan mdzad pa phrin
NK050(wi)001:3769: las kyi mtha' rdzogs par mi 'gyur bas na mtha'i
NK050(wi)001:3770: tshad dang rnam pa'i grangs dang dus sam yun 'di
NK050(wi)001:3771: tsam zhes sus kyang tshad bzung du med de chos
NK050(wi)001:3772: kyi dbyings dang sems can gyi khams ji tsam gnas
NK050(wi)001:3775: zhi sku dpag bsam shing ltar gsal gyur cing //
NK050(wi)001:3776: yid bzhin nor bu bzhin du rnam mi rtog /
NK050(wi)001:3777: 'gro sgrol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /
NK050(wi)001:3778: 'di ni spros dang bral la snang ba yin //
NK050(wi)001:3780: rdo rje'i gnas 'di ni phal gyi bsam gyis mi
NK050(wi)001:3781: khyab cing rtogs dka' ba'i gnas sangs rgyas rang nyid
NK050(wi)001:3782: kyis mkhyen pa'i spyod yul te /
NK050(wi)001:3784: sangs rgyas khams dang sangs rgyas byang chub dang //
NK050(wi)001:3785: sangs rgyas yon tan sangs rgyas phrin las te //
NK050(wi)001:3786: dag pa'i sems can gyis kyang bsam bya min //
NK050(wi)001:3787: 'di ni 'dren pa rnams kyi spyod yul lo //
NK050(wi)001:3789: des na sangs rgyas dang sems can /
NK050(wi)001:3791: dag ma dag la sogs pa'i gnyis chos kyi spros
NK050(wi)001:3792: pa mtha' yas shing mu med par snang ba 'di
NK050(wi)001:3793: thams cad / don la chos dbyings mnyam pa chen po'i klong las nam yang ma g.yos /
NK050(wi)001:3796: gang la'ang dgag sgrub spang blang re dogs zhen 'dzin sogs kyis bslad mi gzhug par /
NK050(wi)001:3797: rang byung gdod ma'i gshis lugs /
NK050(wi)001:3798: ye nas 'ching grol las 'das pa'i don la yid ches /
NK050(wi)001:3800: brtan pa thob par bya ba ni /
NK050(wi)001:3801: nges don gyi mdo rgyud man ngag kun gyi bstan don zab gnad snying po gcig tu dril te /
NK050(wi)001:3802: klong rab 'byams rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK050(wi)001:3804: mnyam pa'i don las g.yos pa med //
NK050(wi)001:3805: thams cad kun tu bzang por gcig /
NK050(wi)001:3808: ji ltar snang ba de bzhin nyid du gcig /
NK050(wi)001:3809: 'di la sus kyang bcos par ma byed cig /
NK050(wi)001:3810: ma bcos mnyam pa'i rgyal po de la ni //
NK050(wi)001:3811: mi rtog chos sku'i dgongs pa lhun gyis grub //
NK050(wi)001:3814: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK050(wi)001:3815: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK050(wi)001:3816: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK050(wi)001:3817: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK050(wi)001:3819: skye med rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK050(wi)001:3820: gar yang ma gtogs cir yang ma bsams shig /
NK050(wi)001:3821: bcas bcos ma byed rang bzhin lhug par zhog /
NK050(wi)001:3822: ma bcos pa ni skye med rin chen mdzod //
NK050(wi)001:3823: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa yin //
NK050(wi)001:3825: de ltar rtogs pa'i dgos ched dam phan yon yang /
NK050(wi)001:3826: yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK050(wi)001:3827: yang zab lta ba'i mthar thug 'di shes pas //
NK050(wi)001:3828: gol grib las grol rtag chad kun dang bral //
NK050(wi)001:3829: bsgrub pa don yod myur du 'tshang rgya zhing //
NK050(wi)001:3830: mdo rgyud kun la lta ba'i mig dang ldan //
NK050(wi)001:3831: de phyir gnas lugs 'od gsal mkhyen par mdzod //
NK050(wi)001:3832: ces rjes su gdams par mdzad pa bzhin no //
NK050(wi)001:3834: gdod ma'i 'od gsal bde gshegs snying po ni //
NK050(wi)001:3835: ngo bo stong pas rtag pa'i mtha' las grol //
NK050(wi)001:3836: rang bzhin 'od gsal chad pa'i mu dang bral //
NK050(wi)001:3837: gang la'ang mi gnas gnyis med mnyam pa nyid //
NK050(wi)001:3838: de yi ngang las 'khor 'das bkod pa'i sprin //
NK050(wi)001:3839: bsam gyis mi khyab mkha' yi mu mnyam yang //
NK050(wi)001:3840: don la gnyis med mnyam nyid chos skur grub //
NK050(wi)001:3841: chos sku'i klong du dgag sgrub spang len ci //
NK050(wi)001:3842: 'khor ba ming med 'khrul gzhi ka nas dag /
NK050(wi)001:3843: ye shes rang gsal dus gsum 'gyur ba med //
NK050(wi)001:3844: srid zhi ro mnyam bsal bzhag bri gang bral //
NK050(wi)001:3845: de tshul shes rnams theg pa mchog la sbyor //
NK050(wi)001:3846: de phyir rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i man ngag bzhin //
NK050(wi)001:3847: don gnas snying po mdo tsam brjod par byas //
NK050(wi)001:3848: 'di la nongs gyur gang mchis 'phags la bshags //
NK050(wi)001:3849: dge bas rang gnas ye shes mngon byed shog /
NK050(wi)001:3850: 'di ltar smra ba'ang bla ma'i drin yin pas //
NK050(wi)001:3851: skye kun bla ma mchog dang mi 'bral bar //
NK050(wi)001:3852: de'i gsung zab rgyas chos mdzod kun 'dzin zhing //
NK050(wi)001:3853: gzhan la ston pa'i skal bzang thob gyur cig /
NK050(wi)001:3854: rgyal ba rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i bden byin gyis //
NK050(wi)001:3855: nges gsang bstan mchog srid mthar cher rgyas shing //
NK050(wi)001:3856: 'gro kun theg mchog lam bzang 'dir zhugs te //
NK050(wi)001:3857: kun kyang rnam mkhyen grong khyer mdzes byed shog /
NK050(wi)001:3858: bkra shis gang zhig lhan skyes bde ba che //
NK050(wi)001:3859: shes rab rang byung sgron me 'jam pa'i dpal //
NK050(wi)001:3860: lus can kun gyi snying la rtag gnas pa'i //
NK050(wi)001:3861: bden pa de yis dus kun shis gyur cig //
NK050(wi)001:3862: ces pa'ang nges pa don gyi thams cad mkhyen pa
NK050(wi)001:3863: 'jam mgon rnam gsum gyi zhabs kyi chu skyes spyi
NK050(wi)001:3864: bor len pa'i zhe chen ban rgan 'gyur med pad+ma
NK050(wi)001:3865: rnam rgyal lam 'jam dbyangs blo gros rgya mtshos rang
NK050(wi)001:3866: lo nga bzhi pa shing byi gnam lo gsar 'char
NK050(wi)001:3867: gyi dus tshes dge bar bde mchog bkra shis dge
NK050(wi)001:3868: 'phel du lhag pa'i lha'i bsnyen mtshams la gnas pa'i
NK050(wi)001:3869: thun gseng du bris pa ste /
